rcontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEieuy6NbnoX2N8iVER-AB8Nr-X0xoDoiRBhF53tsj63z9l8rBM94mQ4mgVVV-N9xgE3Y-Rj8aVGg4ksyZKdXhHfPUHhj7puSKKjelt_VjEIwlLpDtuZ9p-GL60_Bv41FfByPt9LN5XIQCVscvVVv2NUkSQVt8jMvutHtVUXzPrMZY0NLfYAMRyglDnuxhI/s600/DSC05337.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲牌架四個，可以堆疊起來收納很方便</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgZ0DICoiDPLfb040Q-wfeU2JgGbL2Jx6sRHt1us24_m1SWQnpvBYDDIMMFKJXI8N1D0672MgvMAxJRdWqBeTUzndR8xcqBdlezDLdHZtqTm8lrWRY7YMQF0b-rZa0ZHp3CcYyJXfkqBBfeq0cpiYk_2ijdEEv6Dd60x9E-dn-g5jsezXCjnT7_R1AaiQU/s4420/DSC05338.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgZ0DICoiDPLfb040Q-wfeU2JgGbL2Jx6sRHt1us24_m1SWQnpvBYDDIMMFKJXI8N1D0672MgvMAxJRdWqBeTUzndR8xcqBdlezDLdHZtqTm8lrWRY7YMQF0b-rZa0ZHp3CcYyJXfkqBBfeq0cpiYk_2ijdEEv6Dd60x9E-dn-g5jsezXCjnT7_R1AaiQU/s600/DSC05338.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲卡片有三種</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhkq0G-DF-vDtLrx9LKMRWva4-qYicxSogey_jgra0CzoRI_eYT5uvg45vkfHHS0oO_ioKFfohL-PcKcT3E2RLm8rOZ6H0wYNzr9b24EzlNokBUn0-360EJtdZ7x4v7jyfU-ctuhkfFAFE2w9FOq4rIEFWvAMHGD-SDWPKgeWRaVBelDTKRqWSS5m3PY6w/s3840/DSC05339.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhkq0G-DF-vDtLrx9LKMRWva4-qYicxSogey_jgra0CzoRI_eYT5uvg45vkfHHS0oO_ioKFfohL-PcKcT3E2RLm8rOZ6H0wYNzr9b24EzlNokBUn0-360EJtdZ7x4v7jyfU-ctuhkfFAFE2w9FOq4rIEFWvAMHGD-SDWPKgeWRaVBelDTKRqWSS5m3PY6w/s600/DSC05339.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲第一種是關卡卡片，裡面有每一關的規則與細節</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhGNG9zXc_n0Zv7hvK3Ofk_ksTHKLIEr15oSy9cui_sDCetaOjWBojtTrOIWbUWCB9lzMbHLl_0O04IeZUFUMmUQWRKrg84zie3tEA9KLXx6MnuWP_fnKxD_gXmhOy-GYi0qw6jjWpSuoXkWOBDKjtOVd3baeydC3Up739HogUwLYsfFSpT2LELWg67LpQ/s2960/DSC05340.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhGNG9zXc_n0Zv7hvK3Ofk_ksTHKLIEr15oSy9cui_sDCetaOjWBojtTrOIWbUWCB9lzMbHLl_0O04IeZUFUMmUQWRKrg84zie3tEA9KLXx6MnuWP_fnKxD_gXmhOy-GYi0qw6jjWpSuoXkWOBDKjtOVd3baeydC3Up739HogUwLYsfFSpT2LELWg67LpQ/s600/DSC05340.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲第二種是隊員卡，每個隊員都會有個人裝備</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">（也可以用來抽誰是隊長）</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgcsUIE52rE_8jI4Lh6O5Pnz3Njvzx7EvLV2WzGNxeupxilw8UiHhPicKu6J2jGulWdy1e2_c5pjpvYrXSOtgKhhHIVfkRSh1TMaNAKG03Hgvzm77ie-esHJbYTr6Q5qXZRvhZ71wJuMCPHFJM25QdcPYyYvjS6K0ItwgLaHuji__nfXTJJP7qJ34FX6IE/s3308/DSC05341.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgcsUIE52rE_8jI4Lh6O5Pnz3Njvzx7EvLV2WzGNxeupxilw8UiHhPicKu6J2jGulWdy1e2_c5pjpvYrXSOtgKhhHIVfkRSh1TMaNAKG03Hgvzm77ie-esHJbYTr6Q5qXZRvhZ71wJuMCPHFJM25QdcPYyYvjS6K0ItwgLaHuji__nfXTJJP7qJ34FX6IE/s600/DSC05341.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲第三種是工具卡，分別對應１－１２的數字</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhovjIZtCaARcF18u6gkiw23y-dGdjGNreHa3Ni4bT8CtFZ610R9Dtj-ooSFqrpnYaL8hdSMlMuzRQSU8EMrwc8S0rUMcG32lLzTLc1mxzNrybEb1w05FfiK9SVyq2jDxnA1dfZQsd7IeR1HCVvK81CbRCXewIR4KT-wzMohsv8CbVXjJRuBaZGWrRnxIA/s4272/DSC05342.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhovjIZtCaARcF18u6gkiw23y-dGdjGNreHa3Ni4bT8CtFZ610R9Dtj-ooSFqrpnYaL8hdSMlMuzRQSU8EMrwc8S0rUMcG32lLzTLc1mxzNrybEb1w05FfiK9SVyq2jDxnA1dfZQsd7IeR1HCVvK81CbRCXewIR4KT-wzMohsv8CbVXjJRuBaZGWrRnxIA/s600/DSC05342.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">▲盒子裡面還有更多盒子，聰明的你應該知道了，這些就是後面的關卡，裡面的東西要等到達進度之後才能打開來看喔～話說每個盒子上的美術也都好可愛～（這裡面的東西我就不暴雷了）</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEim8agiKf1cLDEfwHv9iMDhsoyNWELINrupSro6oV6V7ETDoZ-L0RAXQTKW3iDYo4huuSWLPiFWlyBuPjrHpFDMDWCjiYfGQCkqjQv1l0YpdZh8UZxjb8ZRJ3CIUsTXtf0zY8z29LDaaJDdAC4vky4wovoHushC09vQ1_t5Ow3inRAott1PjfFV4meks2E\"></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲遊戲的基本規則不難，我這邊先放官方影片給大家看～</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">遊戲設置的時候，玩家們會隨機獲得導線，裡面有普通導線，還有黃色跟紅色的導線～（玩家們會知道每個黃色跟紅色的導線各自落哪兩個數字中間）拿到導線之後，將所有的導線由左至右由小到大排列在自己面前的牌架上，接著每位玩家可以放一個提示，來給其他隊友們線索。</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">每次輪到玩家的時候可以從兩種拆彈行動二選一：</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">（一）雙人拆彈</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">玩家指定自己的一片導線，與另一位玩家的導線，並宣稱兩片相同。如果是，成功拆彈，將兩面導線都面朝上擺在各自前面；如果不是，起爆器前進一格，前進到底就會導致任務失敗。黃色的導線也可以用此方式拆除，而且不用管上面的數字，只要兩片都是黃色就可以拆掉。但，任何時候如果你指定到紅色導線，那遊戲就會直接失敗～</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">（二）單人拆彈</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">玩家可以將自己牌架上的四片相同數字的導線，或是某數字的最後兩片導線（前兩片已經被拆掉）拆掉。這個行動是不可能失敗的，因為數字對你來說都是公開資訊，只是要符合條件才能拆。</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">遊戲就這樣不斷進行，直到玩家們拆到紅色導線（失敗）、起爆器引爆（失敗），或是一直拆到所有人的牌架上最後只剩一根紅色導線（成功）為止！</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEiYbh5ZNhgL3QWxTiO9ZKf4jv95tgiXvjsaqGl30jCUqgwJyk5onnPX739IRgNXS69jmtVDTGwDWXaylhxyYz2shhCchboJrExzfnllNXFseSKo2uc14FU7HKZ3gx9uF0HoIQgkny2zOFODXOOC4lD2Wx7Fdlqg2SPdgwHqkSh97Sb61LhZFVTUuHq0aVI\"></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>情境十足</strong></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">這遊戲在情境感上配合得相當不錯，從一開始的模擬訓練，到實地訓練。然後就是一關又一關的關卡，隨著盒子一個一個打開，一些新的變化會讓你驚呼『哇！居然還有這招！』～我不想劇透，但後面有個立體的傢伙很有趣～遊戲當中也有需要使用到QR code的設計，也都是讓情境感再往上堆疊～玩起來真的很有自己就是拆彈小隊一員的感受！</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">但，豐富的關卡其實就是個雙面刃。大家應該也知道，現今遊戲大爆炸的年代，誰還會一盒遊戲玩６６次！？我自己當然也是，要老實跟大家說，我從教學關卡就開始跳關了，實在是沒辦法一關一關玩下去～但即使是這樣，就算你每個階段只玩最後一關，還是有六個關卡可以玩！（但不建議大家跳得太誇張，因為中間有一些關卡還是會讓你學到一些技巧跟經驗～）</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">此外還有一個缺點要提，雖然遊戲人數支援２－５人，但我跟吉姆進行過一場兩人局，遊戲體驗實在是不好～主要的缺點是難度太低，有點不知道在幹嘛就已經過關了。但抱歉，我們沒有繼續往後嘗試其他關卡的兩人局。我很少建議大家不要嘗試，但這款遊戲如果你是打算買來當雙人桌遊的，我會勸你再想想～</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">我其實有點懷疑，設計師是不是在打麻將的過程中發想出這款遊戲。只是從原本打麻將的爾虞我詐，要去猜測對方有什麼牌，變成了大家合作，一起把炸彈給拆掉～這款遊戲目前體驗下來，最推薦大家玩四人局。我會推薦給：喜歡合作遊戲的玩家，喜歡有多重關卡遊戲的玩家，想找四到五人遊戲的玩家～最後容我再說一句，Dom 2D的美術我真的太喜歡，希望能趕快看到他的下一部作品～</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEi48OhfBQ5_wHhRYYrKAYhFKbHX0sRi0wX7XzAL7m5eJad7s1wY3SG-X7GBU0izVhKpGSi9wRfB706ToYH4ONFnj39Qbkgu0JmsRhAWpGlQk69HfHi0kyGKbHlqwf-uS9L0iMAQrw3-_P0OrzzjcCn3UAIRqUqiLHN8EQZyQxd9dXQbnghOE7nZ_VBWM-E/s4300/DSC05343.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEi48OhfBQ5_wHhRYYrKAYhFKbHX0sRi0wX7XzAL7m5eJad7s1wY3SG-X7GBU0izVhKpGSi9wRfB706ToYH4ONFnj39Qbkgu0JmsRhAWpGlQk69HfHi0kyGKbHlqwf-uS9L0iMAQrw3-_P0OrzzjcCn3UAIRqUqiLHN8EQZyQxd9dXQbnghOE7nZ_VBWM-E/s600/DSC05343.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲遊戲收納照～</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgxLiU2IEBW9ubjI2I5269EypYknG_ncf1HIwK9-tlO7D7fBqOEifTAP33c8feWRRq4sDRmHePmLr9gHqLpqVQ8ieGkC0KmvFlwwF4W6wO2VKabWf1nwJpUxqhwPfS6QislEc5EquBkAKdMNWpxgPrrG51vP36uVFp-HOOd8FTebzfAMPZE4gH10M2ma6E/s5356/DSC05344.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgxLiU2IEBW9ubjI2I5269EypYknG_ncf1HIwK9-tlO7D7fBqOEifTAP33c8feWRRq4sDRmHePmLr9gHqLpqVQ8ieGkC0KmvFlwwF4W6wO2VKabWf1nwJpUxqhwPfS6QislEc5EquBkAKdMNWpxgPrrG51vP36uVFp-HOOd8FTebzfAMPZE4gH10M2ma6E/s600/DSC05344.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲盒子的內側有很可愛的小獎盃圖，這些都是有用途的喔～</p><p><br></p>', '2024-11-18 09:39:50', '2024-11-18 09:39:50', 1, 'forum-1731893990911-952762360.jpg'),
(6, 1, '【桌遊開箱報】Treat or cheat 寵物擠診室 開箱+介紹', '<h3><br></h3><p><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEg5hhpO0uV4ERGMmdUUXz-RkYSajOhWyHJwf7PtPU6TDJ8neNlNpyN7BgHsT6TVFBV0cP3vJaq1nUthH4JlMzswYYEazyysHehQqmUhAkOtUauqEKWIE4zxSh5VHBqlG-r2TLno-ej3G_xAtQXgekqop-r7mtW3oDzaDiQG59xPTD_tZFnwqFpAkcowSwY/s2152/DSC05315.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEg5hhpO0uV4ERGMmdUUXz-RkYSajOhWyHJwf7PtPU6TDJ8neNlNpyN7BgHsT6TVFBV0cP3vJaq1nUthH4JlMzswYYEazyysHehQqmUhAkOtUauqEKWIE4zxSh5VHBqlG-r2TLno-ej3G_xAtQXgekqop-r7mtW3oDzaDiQG59xPTD_tZFnwqFpAkcowSwY/w445-h640/DSC05315.JPG\"></a></p><p><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEgu4VqSuEiPzEkSQ4m49YB0PFJkkII16UPk9wnj93y_6APHsLuXw9JVo9-jCS1HhorNPElcWpXQGq7YqVRQs67ubJPB78Yv3F0mwT0Vgu-5DsiXIHsluU7vi3yFejWdReiT8210brKgaiRIknfro9tC-K6TTObaeY_k3K-7s7W8mdFoL2BUWXMiBCG6Py4\"></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">不知道大家有沒有去過急診室的經驗，無論是自己或是家人，相信在急診室的經驗都不會是個快樂的回憶。不過跟很多國家比起來，我們的急診室已經是SSR等級的！無論是速度、品質，還有價格，絕對都是世界一等一的水準！但即使是這樣的急診室，可能還是沒有辦法同時滿足所有人的需求，套句鯛民常說的：『我來急診耶！為什麼還要等！』既然，你也急，我也急，他也急！那就大家一起來『擠診室』吧！！！</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEh4k4vF8_6OaIXoWDX2uMflZtcp1Csa4sdq7OZpqlgDr5WVvqtFif0jJrFDTPhAxUGJiFtOALCd7Ed-Y-XyW_b78vP582EJEfkzfPdALAqwoO-irtnm3ordBJXEFJW4ESvS1QFDuKVBebvAfzfIizrDOAqE4v_ELfIivvW9GclB53gx3JW6RGbVJMWxpb0\"></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEg5hhpO0uV4ERGMmdUUXz-RkYSajOhWyHJwf7PtPU6TDJ8neNlNpyN7BgHsT6TVFBV0cP3vJaq1nUthH4JlMzswYYEazyysHehQqmUhAkOtUauqEKWIE4zxSh5VHBqlG-r2TLno-ej3G_xAtQXgekqop-r7mtW3oDzaDiQG59xPTD_tZFnwqFpAkcowSwY/s2152/DSC05315.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEg5hhpO0uV4ERGMmdUUXz-RkYSajOhWyHJwf7PtPU6TDJ8neNlNpyN7BgHsT6TVFBV0cP3vJaq1nUthH4JlMzswYYEazyysHehQqmUhAkOtUauqEKWIE4zxSh5VHBqlG-r2TLno-ej3G_xAtQXgekqop-r7mtW3oDzaDiQG59xPTD_tZFnwqFpAkcowSwY/s600/DSC05315.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲封面超可愛～</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">動物們：「醫生啊～你救救他～」</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">獅子醫生（怕.jpg）</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjriM2LgjFQx7vSmzmyJbffuPO_xWEvrCX7xWfTqtv4w4Oqxmk0t40RLpYGmAbr860mmEqTjnGhyphenhyphenLpIUC0_JYlO-AL-B953j59B_k2-0nYZejbyre3rRpRF4m8wzzkQSMvCcOdPDIhbk4FF-Ia1OhDPxrRtyRCYYurLnRimlhNo2wf092GEmQsbbu7p05A/s4012/DSC05316.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjriM2LgjFQx7vSmzmyJbffuPO_xWEvrCX7xWfTqtv4w4Oqxmk0t40RLpYGmAbr860mmEqTjnGhyphenhyphenLpIUC0_JYlO-AL-B953j59B_k2-0nYZejbyre3rRpRF4m8wzzkQSMvCcOdPDIhbk4FF-Ia1OhDPxrRtyRCYYurLnRimlhNo2wf092GEmQsbbu7p05A/s600/DSC05316.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲遊戲人數：3-5人　建議年齡：8+　遊戲時間：20mins</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjDMn6zQlSPjAITSPr4E7sqjNjS-GCaoiTOWL4BU8OWx6a2ebnnplKLEjwnMQ-chrjyQZom6LyV0LbyAKJZXtFrqKqProfWHVEg5hCMlCBc1As8Dy7OQELP9iiQe0XjQvfS7x6VxQMOQxvS8x-DDcuATzcy4dtSqbHxnkf1D5Mn2nTjkzTEbwuYPyuO6qc/s2452/DSC05317.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjDMn6zQlSPjAITSPr4E7sqjNjS-GCaoiTOWL4BU8OWx6a2ebnnplKLEjwnMQ-chrjyQZom6LyV0LbyAKJZXtFrqKqProfWHVEg5hCMlCBc1As8Dy7OQELP9iiQe0XjQvfS7x6VxQMOQxvS8x-DDcuATzcy4dtSqbHxnkf1D5Mn2nTjkzTEbwuYPyuO6qc/s600/DSC05317.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲盒底有遊玩時的概況圖</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhhyphenhyphenNpxKCndp6rpMPEB13Izidqi0TdeS9oFuIpdW_w9-MbqVcSWE2bg7TqxO8KQZ7cnzRTnusYLeefe7cmP1El1FVSDVKDLz69Qg7PFdr_-JzK9BxO5fy5zhPwCMC6mrnbyt6LlzuV8LqgpfwRI_KpYpVfbgKLElGaKDQx6_2vs4_fIzzHf0Ahq22BiLEc/s3960/DSC05318.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhhyphenhyphenNpxKCndp6rpMPEB13Izidqi0TdeS9oFuIpdW_w9-MbqVcSWE2bg7TqxO8KQZ7cnzRTnusYLeefe7cmP1El1FVSDVKDLz69Qg7PFdr_-JzK9BxO5fy5zhPwCMC6mrnbyt6LlzuV8LqgpfwRI_KpYpVfbgKLElGaKDQx6_2vs4_fIzzHf0Ahq22BiLEc/s600/DSC05318.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲內容物一覽，主要是卡片</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgX53cZeExqKH3LuOm9UCr-Z6lCLV2KQgCL8fH3ST-_1CYNSA1FkH_SGrSSgmQMxZkblSyW32zaG7YfLXnHtfqpC4xUV3xEAOH1V6ewb73tBQOoSBjBoxtkg8A5jL3e414jti4xKtyvOIgvBGdvGXk-khYWU4mAxRw80CdiIQ3OTvY-n1TsNeKexB3E6ek/s4696/DSC05319.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgX53cZeExqKH3LuOm9UCr-Z6lCLV2KQgCL8fH3ST-_1CYNSA1FkH_SGrSSgmQMxZkblSyW32zaG7YfLXnHtfqpC4xUV3xEAOH1V6ewb73tBQOoSBjBoxtkg8A5jL3e414jti4xKtyvOIgvBGdvGXk-khYWU4mAxRw80CdiIQ3OTvY-n1TsNeKexB3E6ek/w640-h456/DSC05319.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲卡片總覽：有三張醫院卡、五種家族的寵物卡、檢傷幫助卡、與轉診獎勵卡</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">底下我們來看看五種家族的寵物卡</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjn3bGb6DxmHup46-pzOYYjOd21NPc1Z9H7lKlj80AOIeU658a4RGKQ_FyIXte-qApJxZEAkvn_BGo9skrdm8z2gn_J-w2v1SBtPbBv2QCdgidLm-hGpFr7Kl97g-WL9nnn02DCf75sigC5UNFaQupDX90qsbn00uvbU_8JtEehzNEUp3AGPKRJlP3e3JE/s3480/DSC05320.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjn3bGb6DxmHup46-pzOYYjOd21NPc1Z9H7lKlj80AOIeU658a4RGKQ_FyIXte-qApJxZEAkvn_BGo9skrdm8z2gn_J-w2v1SBtPbBv2QCdgidLm-hGpFr7Kl97g-WL9nnn02DCf75sigC5UNFaQupDX90qsbn00uvbU_8JtEehzNEUp3AGPKRJlP3e3JE/w640-h640/DSC05320.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲首先是貓貓家族，病人有分輕症、中症跟重症，還有四張家屬～</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">檢傷卡有兩張，一張是單面，另一張是雙面的～</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgkWYKR1YVaB1qYiUn-FdR52xpXMTdYqZGhi4xyblZhzz8YCLiFNTo86StX9B6R1sRlCQWhGXXT5jQ75i0ImPFaWU8ztg6HwXJTYpsmDRVQo5hyPnudX__5d2_kXA_nNc5hHQ_Cul4ELiiwt6Sx_VTSFZZhD0sCsivs4-GDxqHnSOm8iv7PyKfEN2i8IVE/s3526/DSC05321.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgkWYKR1YVaB1qYiUn-FdR52xpXMTdYqZGhi4xyblZhzz8YCLiFNTo86StX9B6R1sRlCQWhGXXT5jQ75i0ImPFaWU8ztg6HwXJTYpsmDRVQo5hyPnudX__5d2_kXA_nNc5hHQ_Cul4ELiiwt6Sx_VTSFZZhD0sCsivs4-GDxqHnSOm8iv7PyKfEN2i8IVE/w465-h640/DSC05321.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲接著是兔兔家族，八字鬍的兔老爹意外的有點萌～</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEh5EOgtI1Ejgo9QMd2sAMgN-UwpnofrLG6PjVNShqG09wLAf1e1kjM_DF0UCf43aDSbEeQJ1YGDWWqf6JURDft9Qjtcm0R27lm0CdmjlH12Z98tkcJ4UwiuPUpcoOAoHhw-quRCvyRW7O2ijx7W0srqZFKifxN0MrtcuTP8n5VRNrJF5ck4QQkCyJUIlrU/s3464/DSC05322.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEh5EOgtI1Ejgo9QMd2sAMgN-UwpnofrLG6PjVNShqG09wLAf1e1kjM_DF0UCf43aDSbEeQJ1YGDWWqf6JURDft9Qjtcm0R27lm0CdmjlH12Z98tkcJ4UwiuPUpcoOAoHhw-quRCvyRW7O2ijx7W0srqZFKifxN0MrtcuTP8n5VRNrJF5ck4QQkCyJUIlrU/w456-h640/DSC05322.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲熊熊家族，全家都有種呆萌的可愛</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">（而且是台灣黑熊！）</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiLpdwTNzwaZZC735g426Y9zRXX-LGQTX6Y9mYCMzmeZkgDHfiL4Y3gwcgKK0TcSKBlVSC7G4NfXf5TirlaVt51211BP2P7wYWFg8NpSgTpIv9YBJJUtvla2WGnioy3_fn9U34-gXhneB468NrPAOK5cioMIvbjx1hboA-qTWTSZ3KtZnv23VGrA47Fof0/s3324/DSC05323.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiLpdwTNzwaZZC735g426Y9zRXX-LGQTX6Y9mYCMzmeZkgDHfiL4Y3gwcgKK0TcSKBlVSC7G4NfXf5TirlaVt51211BP2P7wYWFg8NpSgTpIv9YBJJUtvla2WGnioy3_fn9U34-gXhneB468NrPAOK5cioMIvbjx1hboA-qTWTSZ3KtZnv23VGrA47Fof0/s600/DSC05323.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲豬豬家族，豬媽媽與三隻小豬都到齊了！</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiJo9K6Tr2Ho0j968CFtV-VcIXrgXxNMXCsNJ2nNZSPOB2L4ZHjSMJW1NAKbS7u6jW0YrS8jV1CbtyUUmVZsUK1LfY0LAHJ1KAL0JGeO4ZB2M6bbA6visgoLe7iK5d4UaJGP4oDRpI4hftxJ4YUoo4kWjQj10Ouyl2wlmAVwNMuviJLQwFVqHVNYbsX05A/s3362/DSC05324.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiJo9K6Tr2Ho0j968CFtV-VcIXrgXxNMXCsNJ2nNZSPOB2L4ZHjSMJW1NAKbS7u6jW0YrS8jV1CbtyUUmVZsUK1LfY0LAHJ1KAL0JGeO4ZB2M6bbA6visgoLe7iK5d4UaJGP4oDRpI4hftxJ4YUoo4kWjQj10Ouyl2wlmAVwNMuviJLQwFVqHVNYbsX05A/s600/DSC05324.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲鬥牛犬家族有異常的堅持，即使都已經重症了，還是要戴著墨鏡～</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhFOh1Jy4clSBcXdcsjOkpZBwTX94EZZgP7DTu5V3q-9l6tGZuWvlRi36zYe8rqf3ov5Ew2PcZf6ucQXktS8f4SEXP8UB58e0H2_68KseApyS0UKZItFmkXQkzVna-2-ryVf1jwjyyqH2CN3_qgk3ubqP9tV0K3Qyd-AXbyukxXdm-D1IPqOI-WpPkFBNI/s1864/DSC05325.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhFOh1Jy4clSBcXdcsjOkpZBwTX94EZZgP7DTu5V3q-9l6tGZuWvlRi36zYe8rqf3ov5Ew2PcZf6ucQXktS8f4SEXP8UB58e0H2_68KseApyS0UKZItFmkXQkzVna-2-ryVf1jwjyyqH2CN3_qgk3ubqP9tV0K3Qyd-AXbyukxXdm-D1IPqOI-WpPkFBNI/s600/DSC05325.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲檢傷提示卡一張，讓大家不用記住檢傷流程</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjDIOyyVC_Zq6ALt9Jcfk2X12vGSJe5DU6K_7NnnC5AZOPxmx_tdzdZqWBinZ7oY-Z3kyTp-XafD4CM9c8ZNGmK4usRFi7_OJqo5Ydcmbt4aDjuKwQSajTEB2DYhR02O_KnMHI__dAZ5T_Lz3savBfyZYrmkCtePg4dTuCin7ecN5BO98vg1TBSpXFFcKs/s4408/DSC05326.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjDIOyyVC_Zq6ALt9Jcfk2X12vGSJe5DU6K_7NnnC5AZOPxmx_tdzdZqWBinZ7oY-Z3kyTp-XafD4CM9c8ZNGmK4usRFi7_OJqo5Ydcmbt4aDjuKwQSajTEB2DYhR02O_KnMHI__dAZ5T_Lz3savBfyZYrmkCtePg4dTuCin7ecN5BO98vg1TBSpXFFcKs/w640-h324/DSC05326.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲轉診獎勵好多張</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEj9FMpIhT_Ec8KMCoY5vPC1Uc5AELqp9IYJ826ljxP1oVswXlna_kcbWYNoYYA_aASqV_MEvYg1RgBL5C1-7VGiZOXS7RPK8qBwNkqpd-iPEoEzUwtYoLQT7mBivZ8pWunDEC9e4EV6EApbRbnnemIv5m-O7wBlwAD_cveCnL3k7l2qG1NeIHA8pHPoMVE/s3332/DSC05327.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEj9FMpIhT_Ec8KMCoY5vPC1Uc5AELqp9IYJ826ljxP1oVswXlna_kcbWYNoYYA_aASqV_MEvYg1RgBL5C1-7VGiZOXS7RPK8qBwNkqpd-iPEoEzUwtYoLQT7mBivZ8pWunDEC9e4EV6EApbRbnnemIv5m-O7wBlwAD_cveCnL3k7l2qG1NeIHA8pHPoMVE/w640-h307/DSC05327.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲三種層級的醫院各一張（另外一面是英文版）</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEim8agiKf1cLDEfwHv9iMDhsoyNWELINrupSro6oV6V7ETDoZ-L0RAXQTKW3iDYo4huuSWLPiFWlyBuPjrHpFDMDWCjiYfGQCkqjQv1l0YpdZh8UZxjb8ZRJ3CIUsTXtf0zY8z29LDaaJDdAC4vky4wovoHushC09vQ1_t5Ow3inRAott1PjfFV4meks2E\"></p><p><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲XIAN有詳盡的教學說明～</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">遊戲的進行步調很快，基本的流程就是打一抽二，想辦法將自己的病患往更高層級的醫院擠，如果能被收住院是再好不過，收住院的當下如果能『順便』多帶幾個家屬進去，那就更棒了！</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">每次輪到我們的時候就是打一張卡片，共有三種選擇：</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">（１）正面朝上打出一張動物卡，並放入其中一間醫院的隊伍中，接著按照【排隊規則】來整理隊伍</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">（２）打出一張檢傷卡，按照【檢傷規則】開始檢傷，並收病人入院</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">（３）面朝下打出一張動物卡，無視【排隊規則】將該動物卡插隊，塞到其中一間醫院的任何一個位置，並且將【插隊計數器】減１</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">＊（１）跟（２）打完牌之後都會抽兩張牌，但（３）不會補牌</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEj9FMpIhT_Ec8KMCoY5vPC1Uc5AELqp9IYJ826ljxP1oVswXlna_kcbWYNoYYA_aASqV_MEvYg1RgBL5C1-7VGiZOXS7RPK8qBwNkqpd-iPEoEzUwtYoLQT7mBivZ8pWunDEC9e4EV6EApbRbnnemIv5m-O7wBlwAD_cveCnL3k7l2qG1NeIHA8pHPoMVE/s600/DSC05327.JPG\"></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">▲遊戲最後進行計分，有進入醫學中心的每張卡片（病患卡，家屬卡，轉診獎勵卡）得３分；區域醫院每張２分；地區診所每張１分。有個容易被忘掉的點，就是在地區診所擁有最多張卡片的玩家，還可以平分剩下的轉診獎勵卡～最後最高分的玩家獲勝！</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEiYbh5ZNhgL3QWxTiO9ZKf4jv95tgiXvjsaqGl30jCUqgwJyk5onnPX739IRgNXS69jmtVDTGwDWXaylhxyYz2shhCchboJrExzfnllNXFseSKo2uc14FU7HKZ3gx9uF0HoIQgkny2zOFODXOOC4lD2Wx7Fdlqg2SPdgwHqkSh97Sb61LhZFVTUuHq0aVI\"></p><p><br></p><p><strong>檢傷分類</strong></p><p><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">身為急診科醫師的設計師官官已經不是第一次在遊戲當中代入『檢傷分類』的概念。可見這些辛苦的急診科醫師們，除了要跟死神拔河之外，還要跟一大堆很急的鯛民們拔河，真的是非常辛苦～<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/erdrwei?__tn__=-UC*F\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">急診鋼鐵人Dr.魏</a>也有製作過一張檢傷分類的圖（正確版＋已歪版），下面我轉貼跟大家分享～希望大家能體會醫護人員們的辛苦，而不是我今天到急診我就急！我就是老大的這種心態。根據下面這張表其實大家可以知道，在急診最緊急的最需要立刻照護的，都是那種已經無法發出聲音，甚至無法動彈的；至於大聲吼叫，敲桌拍櫃台的，很明顯就是最不急的那一群～</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEheX1MQQjfh4mE-vtd000mCqxzu-JNU07KMYeRcRKN1kTgIJTrY-3vbs6tkBjKz0ZtmcOJtm1dTp10oKY0L01aIgKN3m73F8hevqXHTuaidMQMRNUYDlvJHEnG0fixG6yoRH5x4HrjS00N_qaFq6MKiamID-K13BZipnmPmIAwBdkY0B8cNUj5Ir5RikDw/s750/462362609_3759334580981592_7268722197737780058_n.png\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEheX1MQQjfh4mE-vtd000mCqxzu-JNU07KMYeRcRKN1kTgIJTrY-3vbs6tkBjKz0ZtmcOJtm1dTp10oKY0L01aIgKN3m73F8hevqXHTuaidMQMRNUYDlvJHEnG0fixG6yoRH5x4HrjS00N_qaFq6MKiamID-K13BZipnmPmIAwBdkY0B8cNUj5Ir5RikDw/w640-h472/462362609_3759334580981592_7268722197737780058_n.png\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/erdrwei?__tn__=-UC*F\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">急診鋼鐵人Dr.魏</a>製作的表格</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">回到遊戲本身，這次的遊戲是個很簡單的卡片遊戲，但卻有把三級醫院間的上轉下轉都做出來，也有把輕症、中症、還有重症三種病情代入～更厲害的是連三叔公，二嬸婆也都被做進遊戲中～每當檢傷的時候，如果有家屬卡跟著病患卡一起被收入院的時候，我彷彿看見三叔公的微笑，聽見二嬸婆爽朗的笑聲～情境感與規則的安排相當吻合～</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">插隊的設計也相當的巧妙，可以讓你的家屬成為醫學中心裡的影武者，躲到最後才現身；也可以不講道理硬是把別人家的病患直接往下擠到下一個層級的醫院去～更是把三叔公，二嬸婆常做的行為．．．（說過了說過了）</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">《Treat or cheat 寵物擠診室》是一款歡樂的排隊小品，雖然有想要宣傳檢傷分類的概念，但沒有沉重的說教環節，只有機車的插隊與心機的勾心鬥角。我會推薦給喜歡派對遊戲的玩家、想找３－５人小遊戲的玩家、喜歡可愛動物美術的玩家、還有喜歡插隊的玩家（咦！？）。謝謝官官又一次設計了一款好玩又有趣的遊戲！</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEi8xp6nPGkCAf1JHchIBrnfK8DsGP9gEoDS6w7bgxvTkrP9VpPYZPYC-a9pC7FJsd7Ny9b9HYnaKWCOFr5NSy0tfKlJpGRuOCqKNN0qRl-bHIPDgyruZYX8wkjrwn4HNvt_KTo9wNnk6M2DZCVVh8sdI4QaysQTEHgb2V6RmUxARlGEGdGfAVR5Vhw_Tv4/s3644/DSC05328.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEi8xp6nPGkCAf1JHchIBrnfK8DsGP9gEoDS6w7bgxvTkrP9VpPYZPYC-a9pC7FJsd7Ny9b9HYnaKWCOFr5NSy0tfKlJpGRuOCqKNN0qRl-bHIPDgyruZYX8wkjrwn4HNvt_KTo9wNnk6M2DZCVVh8sdI4QaysQTEHgb2V6RmUxARlGEGdGfAVR5Vhw_Tv4/s600/DSC05328.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲遊戲收納照</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEj56zxTTI5fnjtJTjsY96oZI-dRRyuJ6nwrdqO5oXflRmkhGgNC2VAwHkqtG8lJjM51JdQ62ldYGCXgOfynIw4-DisI4ibs_ZutvM7wP6KQj7RXFLL0xsiHuW6JGuaaiVKmJtIAGIBMFuV5OXNvBzsnLxoyQ2lrIe1Ro5Hax4zhuzv7bgxKdy1RiWZ4MSE/s4004/DSC05329.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEj56zxTTI5fnjtJTjsY96oZI-dRRyuJ6nwrdqO5oXflRmkhGgNC2VAwHkqtG8lJjM51JdQ62ldYGCXgOfynIw4-DisI4ibs_ZutvM7wP6KQj7RXFLL0xsiHuW6JGuaaiVKmJtIAGIBMFuV5OXNvBzsnLxoyQ2lrIe1Ro5Hax4zhuzv7bgxKdy1RiWZ4MSE/s600/DSC05329.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲內襯就是封面的美術，據說我是全球第一位收到正確內襯版本的人，一定要拍照留念一下！</p><p><br></p>', '2024-11-18 09:40:32', '2024-11-18 09:40:32', 1, 'forum-1731894032045-820891345.jpg');
INSERT INTO `forum_posts` (`id`, `user_id`, `title`, `content`, `created_at`, `updated_at`, `status`, `cover_image`) VALUES
(7, 1, '【桌遊開箱報】藥到病除 開箱+介紹', '<h3><br></h3><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjQtBCO_oqAI5_hUgeYECZG1POcU9Jk_qkdHL2QPKRvHgFvsZtyEF7NCOSJzVTshheUC9SK0dab9zUeRbHRRYoIk6mWsghM1M9dicDCPtsjzHGSNkpL4gLNLLf9_44I533jwE28q02fC5Jntn65ahi-sClT8nehfcs6yOLv-HEnArKLtVsuVSIQj7iFFUE/s2604/DSC05267.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjQtBCO_oqAI5_hUgeYECZG1POcU9Jk_qkdHL2QPKRvHgFvsZtyEF7NCOSJzVTshheUC9SK0dab9zUeRbHRRYoIk6mWsghM1M9dicDCPtsjzHGSNkpL4gLNLLf9_44I533jwE28q02fC5Jntn65ahi-sClT8nehfcs6yOLv-HEnArKLtVsuVSIQj7iFFUE/s600/DSC05267.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEjNKPKm-654-jp0wq0Vujj2Ml3JtKDwVxlEOWeLVCmFWZKH1BhrZhWg09b1n5TGoWLX4DF_64guWpfj9u4NF8qFEsnley3lURMOzvufCWn_uJbt4yQPqm88JvZrXlIdQUMXz4r94fufzrw-44gK0jjzbpFNPqOIcsPMwzJlrCVdvgJSLMwN9kfk2_-EawE\"></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">《藥到病除》是ＲＫ大師的舊遊戲，很多老玩家應該有聽過或是玩過它之前的版本。最早是由戰棋會出的《毒藥》，以及後來新天鵝堡出的《十三號星期五》。這次由嘴嘴桌遊代理的版本，則是代入了中藥的主題，美術一整個提升變成歷代最佳，而且直接不講武德加入了其他版本都沒有的擴充內容，真的是豐富又大碗～</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEh4k4vF8_6OaIXoWDX2uMflZtcp1Csa4sdq7OZpqlgDr5WVvqtFif0jJrFDTPhAxUGJiFtOALCd7Ed-Y-XyW_b78vP582EJEfkzfPdALAqwoO-irtnm3ordBJXEFJW4ESvS1QFDuKVBebvAfzfIizrDOAqE4v_ELfIivvW9GclB53gx3JW6RGbVJMWxpb0\"></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjQtBCO_oqAI5_hUgeYECZG1POcU9Jk_qkdHL2QPKRvHgFvsZtyEF7NCOSJzVTshheUC9SK0dab9zUeRbHRRYoIk6mWsghM1M9dicDCPtsjzHGSNkpL4gLNLLf9_44I533jwE28q02fC5Jntn65ahi-sClT8nehfcs6yOLv-HEnArKLtVsuVSIQj7iFFUE/s600/DSC05267.JPG\"></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲封面一整個非常復古，而且很有質感～</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEh5KywUrM8OFlmpU_5pQKlNB7iLG4ZEaPjGfbhNMLrh0gVJrdtOsLQXnuApes-KImf011D5bWNtE8GtmDT4cDh90UTlwdfWzjEMWOTQlXRWKZZesAQ-7i1e9_7iyraPfjKfwmcDJF9fnEq8ZirK1Di4hHo9f9eNMWriKbs9ICWBsogiXgVA2u-BN5Th6hg/s4436/DSC05268.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEh5KywUrM8OFlmpU_5pQKlNB7iLG4ZEaPjGfbhNMLrh0gVJrdtOsLQXnuApes-KImf011D5bWNtE8GtmDT4cDh90UTlwdfWzjEMWOTQlXRWKZZesAQ-7i1e9_7iyraPfjKfwmcDJF9fnEq8ZirK1Di4hHo9f9eNMWriKbs9ICWBsogiXgVA2u-BN5Th6hg/s600/DSC05268.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲遊戲人數：3-6人　建議年齡：10+　遊戲時間：30mins</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEj6p3tdXnaCCZ3_7mApuc4Flkx2bWUVapRay5bu2yHECmdZUdo0NZwo5BjZ1roZFKhPkLeabnSyMM09-8Dd6RKa_C3RTsoosZTQFy9yhqBKF_hwqL2gmCQ2zLnBpF9RmuVzlExwy8aQ2e0_5cZa0CGkMnEFU68UdSUoRVXnhQmBeJtvSPc1H7-CtIiN-O8/s2912/DSC05269.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEj6p3tdXnaCCZ3_7mApuc4Flkx2bWUVapRay5bu2yHECmdZUdo0NZwo5BjZ1roZFKhPkLeabnSyMM09-8Dd6RKa_C3RTsoosZTQFy9yhqBKF_hwqL2gmCQ2zLnBpF9RmuVzlExwy8aQ2e0_5cZa0CGkMnEFU68UdSUoRVXnhQmBeJtvSPc1H7-CtIiN-O8/s600/DSC05269.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲盒底可以看到有個很擬真的把手～</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">（不知道為什麼我都會把遊戲名稱唸成《藥到命除》）</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjkyjisCHulrUwDcht9uQZMKgrliQhf7jbS45Q2he7GfWDUVnM_o2kEMeh4yljVty5GlFZqPs3XJFPvUl5T36bNLEEzRUVPVzsnb0N1OsaHRAJ6hlvejoG7z7_l75weZGyVRoC2NnERKoReVdfJLlhE3tRGWlm3Tr_22OQLdKD096DtivEOm0hxYhymaBM/s3644/DSC05270.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjkyjisCHulrUwDcht9uQZMKgrliQhf7jbS45Q2he7GfWDUVnM_o2kEMeh4yljVty5GlFZqPs3XJFPvUl5T36bNLEEzRUVPVzsnb0N1OsaHRAJ6hlvejoG7z7_l75weZGyVRoC2NnERKoReVdfJLlhE3tRGWlm3Tr_22OQLdKD096DtivEOm0hxYhymaBM/s600/DSC05270.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲內容物一覽</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEj0KPRWZmvf6AlbqoZsUCDwaQOtvhwaiFqY9_lWQMnI2bZUpnBNbdp0A424P-pDbxNovo0E_5kIdPLTA9BonTl0sU3oi2BuXfNzn6Ihv55q1mbOO_MYFTKLsmAn3pgygtzn9n_OgQUvqKxNcCO3DfqHb6hFcFIaTTO7nJ48GMhyX29HbocfJzWtbWQ4jZY/s5382/DSC05271.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEj0KPRWZmvf6AlbqoZsUCDwaQOtvhwaiFqY9_lWQMnI2bZUpnBNbdp0A424P-pDbxNovo0E_5kIdPLTA9BonTl0sU3oi2BuXfNzn6Ihv55q1mbOO_MYFTKLsmAn3pgygtzn9n_OgQUvqKxNcCO3DfqHb6hFcFIaTTO7nJ48GMhyX29HbocfJzWtbWQ4jZY/s600/DSC05271.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲說明書有兩本，一本基本，另一本是擴充</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgM4nE2hB90sj-fupKkV_O_yxvrpfXHl_r9ctTtVY1LlM2hoKeaBNq4l_jCMZu5RLoFKeq3yjdm-1-m082sBHF4HpMcqSCez4RdFRfNUvK9AkY4SnQVzKUCkKXiWBds1w5UIINBLZlBWhEiBr0NeRZuVUNO4yvvNN02TGPTJYApIiSPgESHnSu4GrjEqaY/s5276/DSC05272.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgM4nE2hB90sj-fupKkV_O_yxvrpfXHl_r9ctTtVY1LlM2hoKeaBNq4l_jCMZu5RLoFKeq3yjdm-1-m082sBHF4HpMcqSCez4RdFRfNUvK9AkY4SnQVzKUCkKXiWBds1w5UIINBLZlBWhEiBr0NeRZuVUNO4yvvNN02TGPTJYApIiSPgESHnSu4GrjEqaY/s600/DSC05272.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲包藥紙三張</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjHoc_EvLOUOlmHOPr56f3PFjhdM8ShAwlhzlxcY1TdlXG9GyU3g6b5LCGkqWE4Ytsrr-zcPRmea26VqkSDO3FzMdpuzgpd1WsXBc6uvWCqBGN9Hd8IZv6u06qIGPqrKDbsRIJMjX62TX7GpoCgl1igOnusYcJDpNyB9r1HrMPhL7C_hElUhZNZfQw7sao/s4400/DSC05273.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjHoc_EvLOUOlmHOPr56f3PFjhdM8ShAwlhzlxcY1TdlXG9GyU3g6b5LCGkqWE4Ytsrr-zcPRmea26VqkSDO3FzMdpuzgpd1WsXBc6uvWCqBGN9Hd8IZv6u06qIGPqrKDbsRIJMjX62TX7GpoCgl1igOnusYcJDpNyB9r1HrMPhL7C_hElUhZNZfQw7sao/s600/DSC05273.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲卡片兩包</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjpovlae_rqqZbVO5QQPOaNFDlWTRWqXc1KXE5Z3FVA4c3q7fHw7vyIbhSkbqveGOzZ7UNlKOdc_QqSZ-UQl_K9KziksofOas5zZOShE1dg-8GnExnlhFUiLnen6AjdXhkwwly9prudAYr3QzJqqM0h3Fzmyei4WWXkRpE9taoZFnb3vood7Dv2iojkHQI/s4656/DSC05274.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjpovlae_rqqZbVO5QQPOaNFDlWTRWqXc1KXE5Z3FVA4c3q7fHw7vyIbhSkbqveGOzZ7UNlKOdc_QqSZ-UQl_K9KziksofOas5zZOShE1dg-8GnExnlhFUiLnen6AjdXhkwwly9prudAYr3QzJqqM0h3Fzmyei4WWXkRpE9taoZFnb3vood7Dv2iojkHQI/s600/DSC05274.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲第一包卡片就是這次的擴充，也就是以往其他版本沒有的角色能力卡</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEj9OFJ5L5QUDKotGaIXLJnu9JNdjF7PYXAbgbH1KlSM_WCvQOiHVXKe-HRcW-cP1vAFlSN5QTIaRzFSrgOLOI4IEpJWCffSidcX9IklkbxpdbVF8alx3TE6ch0yMFDAmq3KH3wtaavIyiGdpwZk4K8XrjQpYFNsjnk7_SgX9FM1Qja513W7ohCKZ_bczpY/s3392/DSC05275.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEj9OFJ5L5QUDKotGaIXLJnu9JNdjF7PYXAbgbH1KlSM_WCvQOiHVXKe-HRcW-cP1vAFlSN5QTIaRzFSrgOLOI4IEpJWCffSidcX9IklkbxpdbVF8alx3TE6ch0yMFDAmq3KH3wtaavIyiGdpwZk4K8XrjQpYFNsjnk7_SgX9FM1Qja513W7ohCKZ_bczpY/s600/DSC05275.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲角色的設計都很用心，也都有符合該人物在歷史上所代表的意義</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEh7lhL3oCQLq3BzCjHde3kb_5-VSy7Dni5gGpg1G3iZAi1HB4M9dNGMvI6locszZViZkzDFrTHlVhQ4c6y7i0TnnC3lumN3lEae4czcIAtLWbnO7okLgAZsu0Yqbz6y4YN9GTswkdVLxvku80seq5eGHchyphenhyphenCQ7ErW5GJz9ewHCiIdHOP8B92UMXWKEoR_c/s4384/DSC05276.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEh7lhL3oCQLq3BzCjHde3kb_5-VSy7Dni5gGpg1G3iZAi1HB4M9dNGMvI6locszZViZkzDFrTHlVhQ4c6y7i0TnnC3lumN3lEae4czcIAtLWbnO7okLgAZsu0Yqbz6y4YN9GTswkdVLxvku80seq5eGHchyphenhyphenCQ7ErW5GJz9ewHCiIdHOP8B92UMXWKEoR_c/s600/DSC05276.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲另一疊卡片則是所有的手牌，分別是毒藥還有紅藍黃三種藥物</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjh4fBBFllfYzDW6iWsitexBFLHVkr__FL5HR9JdSuhYWrO-LxOqwINFriu00b8QuecMO3kpfSfSzbmAp9UoCNMPcDAXTQu6cQ6KDBofZ4epCjWEi_b9R-5EFXyxm683qlJmHtXrgIvqXEDLYOrD2ZHfsh7GoeBKWtlhk8fYGs9_sUQYCIPGfWACXb96sk/s4084/DSC05277.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjh4fBBFllfYzDW6iWsitexBFLHVkr__FL5HR9JdSuhYWrO-LxOqwINFriu00b8QuecMO3kpfSfSzbmAp9UoCNMPcDAXTQu6cQ6KDBofZ4epCjWEi_b9R-5EFXyxm683qlJmHtXrgIvqXEDLYOrD2ZHfsh7GoeBKWtlhk8fYGs9_sUQYCIPGfWACXb96sk/s600/DSC05277.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">▲遊戲中只會用到８張毒藥，但直接給了你１６張，而且每一張的美術都不同～每次遊戲可以很奢華的隨意選８張出來使用～（卡片能力沒有不同）</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgBd-0CFko5Da4K7sVqgeZmq9o8cAZRSgrl1hDJP4sfG1rDR1CJnquV_8khEFvl1uJJZYZHKitaMOcXfeLsVzwIaCs5S5hVqKMhNFK-635i1W3zQMVtQRwJ7rxOqd2xa5-3zybfwjNMwu-MnzAMd9Qc1G9w8WT5nZ0EYc6yqmLf25cgXxTjAUbQCivbe1g/s3940/DSC05278.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgBd-0CFko5Da4K7sVqgeZmq9o8cAZRSgrl1hDJP4sfG1rDR1CJnquV_8khEFvl1uJJZYZHKitaMOcXfeLsVzwIaCs5S5hVqKMhNFK-635i1W3zQMVtQRwJ7rxOqd2xa5-3zybfwjNMwu-MnzAMd9Qc1G9w8WT5nZ0EYc6yqmLf25cgXxTjAUbQCivbe1g/s600/DSC05278.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">▲黃色（平性）藥物如照片，遊戲中藥物卡片的數字分別為：１、２、４、５、７。但可以看到即使是相同數值的卡片，還是堅持使用不同的美術，卡片真的漂亮到不行～</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjNSCBfKT1bAxL_XZUs4maPMdh-OuNAJEdVLtCiym3BrfGNIO-9UB7ug188xmh2Vtd0RSCArN5IivcRDXtaDrOCKffEWuUKDU6B79T8PdT2SnhoX1Z_JC9gPZ1wwsgdnh3B6S6y8FS9umZTOaX3DxFOURjMwmnCNxEnbnkiu_70GEf9WL0B0cQg22oihEg/s4120/DSC05279.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjNSCBfKT1bAxL_XZUs4maPMdh-OuNAJEdVLtCiym3BrfGNIO-9UB7ug188xmh2Vtd0RSCArN5IivcRDXtaDrOCKffEWuUKDU6B79T8PdT2SnhoX1Z_JC9gPZ1wwsgdnh3B6S6y8FS9umZTOaX3DxFOURjMwmnCNxEnbnkiu_70GEf9WL0B0cQg22oihEg/s600/DSC05279.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲藍色（寒涼）藥物的卡片，數字的組成是完全相同的，當然，每一張的美術都完全不同～</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjIN2-NupUFZ7QzlDSGSoxI6a0imcOGvv5w0YdRq4rLIVFa1SjEZxanLGXYyngg1Rjci2ViGYeFvT-JkHYmW1JfgU2HixCYKF3kzaVbNrPFmuCk5YsQk8TIz2oqSvik2aKF8J3ar0UzCLT0zLuSFNlphNpEE988tJXJWhSCLoZZuXVrvdJMx-FjkGzRE64/s3956/DSC05280.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjIN2-NupUFZ7QzlDSGSoxI6a0imcOGvv5w0YdRq4rLIVFa1SjEZxanLGXYyngg1Rjci2ViGYeFvT-JkHYmW1JfgU2HixCYKF3kzaVbNrPFmuCk5YsQk8TIz2oqSvik2aKF8J3ar0UzCLT0zLuSFNlphNpEE988tJXJWhSCLoZZuXVrvdJMx-FjkGzRE64/s600/DSC05280.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲最後則是紅色（溫熱）的卡片，同樣也是誠意滿滿～</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEim8agiKf1cLDEfwHv9iMDhsoyNWELINrupSro6oV6V7ETDoZ-L0RAXQTKW3iDYo4huuSWLPiFWlyBuPjrHpFDMDWCjiYfGQCkqjQv1l0YpdZh8UZxjb8ZRJ3CIUsTXtf0zY8z29LDaaJDdAC4vky4wovoHushC09vQ1_t5Ow3inRAott1PjfFV4meks2E\"></p><p>這這這，超經典遊戲規則我就不教了～派我的好朋友超級美少女Vicky來教大家～</p><p><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲Vicky的教學影片，做得相當棒！</p><p><br></p><p><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEiYbh5ZNhgL3QWxTiO9ZKf4jv95tgiXvjsaqGl30jCUqgwJyk5onnPX739IRgNXS69jmtVDTGwDWXaylhxyYz2shhCchboJrExzfnllNXFseSKo2uc14FU7HKZ3gx9uF0HoIQgkny2zOFODXOOC4lD2Wx7Fdlqg2SPdgwHqkSh97Sb61LhZFVTUuHq0aVI\"></p><p><strong>誠意滿滿</strong></p><p><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">雖然是老遊戲新製，但這次加入的角色卡的確讓遊戲有了許多新的變化，角色能力的設計也是相當的用心～因此在所有版本裡面，目前絕對是最值得推薦的版本～除此之外，美術的進化也是肉眼可見的誠意滿滿～相同數值的卡片明明功能就一樣，但還是做出了不同的美術，甚至連文字的介紹也都不馬虎～可以感受到製作組的用心～</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">有一點我一定要單獨提出來說的是，美術真的有夠漂亮～除了很有誠意的每張都不同之外，每個藥材的圖畫真的都好美～下面我會另外再給大家看更清楚的卡片照片～美到直接出明信片應該都會有人想要買的程度～</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiK9doXvktXj72uQEoknQ_YqSAn7rr7YzUM0VOJ7KtSCmFXkYebyjdGGZhssclktF-ceZy4Lwlhe17pd00bK3mVvd_-YS3bVlLboArPUyc6BRjun9gmssyWL6F-W2x2c-rJAHTl4A9xKV3vf2XPK_RBfxAOG214rO1JzPGVpufOonvWR1pSqHJH0xJG-V0/w640-h444/DSC05279.png\"></p><p><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEimMEUcYRvmV7DcO5JCdz_aOzxwOuhknnFmlrO63P8IoqDBLtrLw1M5ofG1vUmx4Iu2N91yDGSMO3gk_ddig7JqNP0kh5oSxuWg3kUnX4D9T6s9mLqtZhTonYA5InLyThKGpuB9LI3J9hgLb7q1BWuztVQVeduCtFBi-vaphJ8P4AQG0fobRrR_axkujoc/w640-h504/DSC05280.png\"></p><p><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEg_Zgjl9PS-Z18l8d7MyCNgO2-pQmiHtdWFUreTl0_KubnqoIXHGaMla6aLaGXKBX1YF4rRtV1CJrtv0V7YRa0taJDBvjmH_tqpXAiSWebpDVUtwhPG6fMfBLLYDnz-N4o7EIdMgXHH8lQrfP0NVTmHf7_FM6T5O6xmcmDtSFOS1l_oan5i8IVvq4L7JS4/s3796/DSC05281.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEg_Zgjl9PS-Z18l8d7MyCNgO2-pQmiHtdWFUreTl0_KubnqoIXHGaMla6aLaGXKBX1YF4rRtV1CJrtv0V7YRa0taJDBvjmH_tqpXAiSWebpDVUtwhPG6fMfBLLYDnz-N4o7EIdMgXHH8lQrfP0NVTmHf7_FM6T5O6xmcmDtSFOS1l_oan5i8IVvq4L7JS4/s600/DSC05281.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲遊戲收納照～留下的空間上薄套應該是沒問題～</p><p><br></p>', '2024-11-18 09:41:04', '2024-11-18 09:41:04', 1, 'forum-1731894064622-624592870.jpg'),
(8, 1, '【桌遊開箱報】Quoridor PAC-MAN 步步為營 PAC-MAN版 開箱+介紹', '<h3><br></h3><p><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEi3p7Gx11lC5yfXFbRFlqBqRCbWsdFZvz_KylsyqXZ1J7x6BkRm93XP61IrqgZKvj6avn1-CwLIAnBy4W1VuLuTpzaAF4kpyO5Kb7Pr4CDZhQzDvbxOPYvz6nsTRinsUlc7XPPQs1gIOavjpwx7W0grn_4XZ3K5mLruFGDpZpXC2wxEKbkBWMyEodjdcCk/s3456/DSC05116.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEi3p7Gx11lC5yfXFbRFlqBqRCbWsdFZvz_KylsyqXZ1J7x6BkRm93XP61IrqgZKvj6avn1-CwLIAnBy4W1VuLuTpzaAF4kpyO5Kb7Pr4CDZhQzDvbxOPYvz6nsTRinsUlc7XPPQs1gIOavjpwx7W0grn_4XZ3K5mLruFGDpZpXC2wxEKbkBWMyEodjdcCk/s600/DSC05116.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEjNKPKm-654-jp0wq0Vujj2Ml3JtKDwVxlEOWeLVCmFWZKH1BhrZhWg09b1n5TGoWLX4DF_64guWpfj9u4NF8qFEsnley3lURMOzvufCWn_uJbt4yQPqm88JvZrXlIdQUMXz4r94fufzrw-44gK0jjzbpFNPqOIcsPMwzJlrCVdvgJSLMwN9kfk2_-EawE\"></p><p><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">沒想到真的來到這一刻，我反而有點不知道怎麼寫這段開頭～偷偷跟大家說，這是我的第六百篇部落格文章！我也不知道是怎麼做到的，但終於也來到了這一天～也謝謝大家這麼多年來的陪伴～對我來說不管是臉書的廢文或是快速的《小小戰報》，我大概都可以五到十分鐘之內搞定～但一篇部落格從拍照到寫完，通常前前後後至少要花我一個禮拜的時間～（而且還有越來越慢的趨勢）加上我也了解部落格這個媒體的性質，在當今各種影音與社群的夾擊下，其實生存的空間也越來越少了～對我來說，拍拍照片在臉書簡單寫寫，大概可以輕鬆個不只十倍～但這裡畢竟是我的起點，就當作是我任性吧～我還是不想輕易放棄部落格～</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">回到這次的《步步為營 PAC-MAN版》，我選擇讓它成為我的第六百篇文章，就知道我有多喜歡它了！《步步為營》本身就是一款很優秀的經典遊戲，這次與PAC-MAN強強聯手，打造出這款不管是在美術上、品質上、甚至是規則變化上都是水準之上的遊戲～總之，一起來看看這款遊戲吧～</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEh4k4vF8_6OaIXoWDX2uMflZtcp1Csa4sdq7OZpqlgDr5WVvqtFif0jJrFDTPhAxUGJiFtOALCd7Ed-Y-XyW_b78vP582EJEfkzfPdALAqwoO-irtnm3ordBJXEFJW4ESvS1QFDuKVBebvAfzfIizrDOAqE4v_ELfIivvW9GclB53gx3JW6RGbVJMWxpb0\"></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEi3p7Gx11lC5yfXFbRFlqBqRCbWsdFZvz_KylsyqXZ1J7x6BkRm93XP61IrqgZKvj6avn1-CwLIAnBy4W1VuLuTpzaAF4kpyO5Kb7Pr4CDZhQzDvbxOPYvz6nsTRinsUlc7XPPQs1gIOavjpwx7W0grn_4XZ3K5mLruFGDpZpXC2wxEKbkBWMyEodjdcCk/s600/DSC05116.JPG\"></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲封面直接不演啦，火力展示給你看！小精靈真的超級可愛！</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhlAIF968AsxBfe-X-h6EQ1nYs6anS6ZYqcjptUITwsk0-zhcZAzoUUpoZz4spnUZlyvdbbKgDnDQIP3a5PVfRXpkg_Tw2MgYNUA1ybMWMwbGwF1yeIrIlmsc9vDEuqAbcHSlXpiHjP0ZMTTiHK1karmelgILqhOLpQMbA0qCOWPo1X4cIyKcjQKOYpkmI/s3968/DSC05117.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhlAIF968AsxBfe-X-h6EQ1nYs6anS6ZYqcjptUITwsk0-zhcZAzoUUpoZz4spnUZlyvdbbKgDnDQIP3a5PVfRXpkg_Tw2MgYNUA1ybMWMwbGwF1yeIrIlmsc9vDEuqAbcHSlXpiHjP0ZMTTiHK1karmelgILqhOLpQMbA0qCOWPo1X4cIyKcjQKOYpkmI/s600/DSC05117.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲遊戲人數：2-5人　建議年齡：8+　遊戲時間：15mins</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">（但其實本質上還是雙人遊戲）</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjubxcXuYBet3BuFw6-ha38JU-e51xxGJgsz4a2DwHcposAAzAr1ZDZjjzM8VGfQGsBi9Rf86yfcMa4Lukg5WeFZumbo4W6TnNeD0Ef5RxM03Jk5Iz5zoyFLPpC4Do5jn0Rh75S0c_IMnIuhyphenhyphenZBD0UQ-bakfEVQRswM_wpMdAxkHGdREf5OSrYm_R3ZkJg/s3504/DSC05118.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjubxcXuYBet3BuFw6-ha38JU-e51xxGJgsz4a2DwHcposAAzAr1ZDZjjzM8VGfQGsBi9Rf86yfcMa4Lukg5WeFZumbo4W6TnNeD0Ef5RxM03Jk5Iz5zoyFLPpC4Do5jn0Rh75S0c_IMnIuhyphenhyphenZBD0UQ-bakfEVQRswM_wpMdAxkHGdREf5OSrYm_R3ZkJg/s600/DSC05118.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲盒底可以看到遊戲的立體樣貌，是不是很期待！</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjjsrlk48gHhH8BA_6JkQ7EbdcEtFixOlgtRrTRO5LNdPAhXTuCQqNKXjzUtnMCBvSsS3nAeBU7V46TlYpzKt5-YWOFRkCVoNJ7q1fOXhSMKsw7ydxT1rrwCEtP9Y8v8G9TtD7sjDTq7r0AWyv3NHdfvK1v3pKGacLO7OOz8kRocTKlNi9pjrNool94Xy4/s4944/DSC05119.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjjsrlk48gHhH8BA_6JkQ7EbdcEtFixOlgtRrTRO5LNdPAhXTuCQqNKXjzUtnMCBvSsS3nAeBU7V46TlYpzKt5-YWOFRkCVoNJ7q1fOXhSMKsw7ydxT1rrwCEtP9Y8v8G9TtD7sjDTq7r0AWyv3NHdfvK1v3pKGacLO7OOz8kRocTKlNi9pjrNool94Xy4/s600/DSC05119.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲內容物一覽</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEih682zzbVCSYEHbAI-kyaDmNa_17kVsKdtQncW58-kUGlJ-T5LNVqd239wTdtOJ0EuQIEY1E3-kGAVFrki3KrUCcwrB6w1Hd7VzE6-yAisAWlY2le8f9cNdmzjb7R7YtZnzBNmzfZMdIDm3W19R74vzp2fD1MipnjvUT6hYSOxECBwUxhoxoY6UvMN7Zs/s4072/DSC05120.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEih682zzbVCSYEHbAI-kyaDmNa_17kVsKdtQncW58-kUGlJ-T5LNVqd239wTdtOJ0EuQIEY1E3-kGAVFrki3KrUCcwrB6w1Hd7VzE6-yAisAWlY2le8f9cNdmzjb7R7YtZnzBNmzfZMdIDm3W19R74vzp2fD1MipnjvUT6hYSOxECBwUxhoxoY6UvMN7Zs/s600/DSC05120.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲遊戲的棋盤是木製的，很大很漂亮～</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjPk8rOTF5jImqaXen0cdfTCjAyJVQ-O31M1QyZt4Xk5Rlcd9Qst2mPqXcJABo4D3b1zFcF43R2QBYDmT69i8IGeN9BAN0FCeL2L2qYrc7DeoE9Il0FdMW5pgMSsbRTA2QSfBC4br4mIqitcCZXUlFEFxtWiKGSK8oUj900Yq9FgFlE7zHWAFbHcemyQwM/s5472/DSC05121.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjPk8rOTF5jImqaXen0cdfTCjAyJVQ-O31M1QyZt4Xk5Rlcd9Qst2mPqXcJABo4D3b1zFcF43R2QBYDmT69i8IGeN9BAN0FCeL2L2qYrc7DeoE9Il0FdMW5pgMSsbRTA2QSfBC4br4mIqitcCZXUlFEFxtWiKGSK8oUj900Yq9FgFlE7zHWAFbHcemyQwM/s600/DSC05121.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲棋盤的背面還有防滑墊，相當的貼心～</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjyuotVDKHCcVtzvVKNdKhg8xauKLi-1CEeRbAaPL-D59V28l-afp_DrPkGUntr8pMyCVDrF8rh8g5EXiC__ebskH9Mradqp-Kw2qI6vvQwRex0GzF2HT8w73QIRezXLUWgTIJMJslnrd7212s8oOQUh2oiccm6BE_YtkkOVS533g3bzJhFk0JYJ_SqU-U/s5192/DSC05122.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjyuotVDKHCcVtzvVKNdKhg8xauKLi-1CEeRbAaPL-D59V28l-afp_DrPkGUntr8pMyCVDrF8rh8g5EXiC__ebskH9Mradqp-Kw2qI6vvQwRex0GzF2HT8w73QIRezXLUWgTIJMJslnrd7212s8oOQUh2oiccm6BE_YtkkOVS533g3bzJhFk0JYJ_SqU-U/s600/DSC05122.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲但我其實不太會把棋盤拿出來玩，直接像這樣放在盒子裡面也不錯～</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEj4ZipKldxJIpXeS5LbFBw-aw0_FeT2h6lQyKsAr0jmzH4PGyljdRG4LEHfbWQVldiGxBPyvBKjjxfEnKLDkhXzf8yAqGVU926-b0W9vAB64mvRkLtVwPUvRa3iQydt0YaSz34n-f5D_elgAyibS8VFk2Q_qloxKiZebZvH6rKtd21XWUMfG4WNvgwAy2o/s5258/DSC05123.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEj4ZipKldxJIpXeS5LbFBw-aw0_FeT2h6lQyKsAr0jmzH4PGyljdRG4LEHfbWQVldiGxBPyvBKjjxfEnKLDkhXzf8yAqGVU926-b0W9vAB64mvRkLtVwPUvRa3iQydt0YaSz34n-f5D_elgAyibS8VFk2Q_qloxKiZebZvH6rKtd21XWUMfG4WNvgwAy2o/s600/DSC05123.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲木頭的立體配件都有設計相對應的收納空間</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEh8rA0G1HCp-LrQNH2MNLq27vpl7HIzBWlh9uDQ3Sg3WGBBL7VJU8xux8iG4r4g_NLQRs0rMYQC_AvdO2RpJykNKvDL436cybUoziY-5tO_05P55a0_IFwYoTd5Dg3or-84YwkYqGBjuIj7lyRSRcX6_DtnwXgbhV6EBg123wT76PdUGnngPN1BG8_4-TU/s4780/DSC05124.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEh8rA0G1HCp-LrQNH2MNLq27vpl7HIzBWlh9uDQ3Sg3WGBBL7VJU8xux8iG4r4g_NLQRs0rMYQC_AvdO2RpJykNKvDL436cybUoziY-5tO_05P55a0_IFwYoTd5Dg3or-84YwkYqGBjuIj7lyRSRcX6_DtnwXgbhV6EBg123wT76PdUGnngPN1BG8_4-TU/s600/DSC05124.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲可愛爆擊！！！！！！！</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiEYuunQQ_CFkUbpm8fDjYv3iVtunSD8ET4OR7sQ5YukVRGovugmkyGek74tItTP6OuQV1a6nfuZgUNixeu1Kgmt-cvtsuOXboNE-8mfNv85g12m1-4yO_0JZ06VONzv-3twVeEOlybJihl9KoAOBYz638q-vxDpWXLzJKZR0lRsdFal86-pTzNjw2ro-8/s5306/DSC05125.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiEYuunQQ_CFkUbpm8fDjYv3iVtunSD8ET4OR7sQ5YukVRGovugmkyGek74tItTP6OuQV1a6nfuZgUNixeu1Kgmt-cvtsuOXboNE-8mfNv85g12m1-4yO_0JZ06VONzv-3twVeEOlybJihl9KoAOBYz638q-vxDpWXLzJKZR0lRsdFal86-pTzNjw2ro-8/s600/DSC05125.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲可愛爆爆爆擊！！！！！</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEg1B1GJm_sNUrXuMlg9bYzjg5EnrZIRUko7PaHsfpr-3RcHH9Hw81MuBwmb5u6epuMeQYlzzrNK9NvoiNCkvx_65ImyBoLGafYFAp5ebhVsMoz8V9MS9AshTa2qOXihXs5Zd1bEtBPQRgUTfKvE0akVe74E7QcSNHz78BDURgp5mqza0RM4BuegJH5vRy8\">雖然這是特別版的遊戲，但要拿來玩基本的《步步為營》也是絕對沒有問題的～基本版的規則實在是太經典，我這裡就不特別著墨。至於特殊版的ＰＡＣＭＡＮ規則，則是先請逸馬來教大家～</p><p><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲逸馬的教學影片</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiyIIUk31KTHsUaJikltC8lGhaRLE3zM3s6sNtcZ9zbw9d_rB2VGJQ8E1DFTUEHaaFFfDkj75YlF7078AMRM4lsNap2f_bgfrSXs6HUbczzIhtfmablGNxO7q41aeFr4_cb1h-tQTheAqhLiotWwF1k1BM1OynSfUXnoiT1Qbs9sOTCvbjB2MVMQT0J-0c/s4933/DSC05127.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiyIIUk31KTHsUaJikltC8lGhaRLE3zM3s6sNtcZ9zbw9d_rB2VGJQ8E1DFTUEHaaFFfDkj75YlF7078AMRM4lsNap2f_bgfrSXs6HUbczzIhtfmablGNxO7q41aeFr4_cb1h-tQTheAqhLiotWwF1k1BM1OynSfUXnoiT1Qbs9sOTCvbjB2MVMQT0J-0c/s600/DSC05127.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">▲特殊模式的設置好之後會像這樣，分成兩個陣營來玩～遊戲由小精靈開始，他每次可以移動兩步～接著換四隻鬼魂各移動一步～但如果鬼魂移動前在視線內有看到小精靈的話，該鬼魂可以直接移動兩步～</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">遊戲不斷進行，若小精靈吃到能量球～他可以立刻再移動三步～如果在這三步當中有碰到鬼魂，就會將鬼魂吃掉～該鬼魂會被暫時移出遊戲～小精靈的目標是將場上四顆能量球都吃掉，吃完的當下他就獲勝了！</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">鬼魂碰到小精靈就可以將其吃掉，每次小精靈死亡之後，所有角色都會回到起始位置（包含先前死掉的鬼魂），然後重新開始～但小精靈只有三條命，如果三條命都用完，那鬼魂就獲勝了！</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEgk3Qm8u_N5Yv12ryA2x-ny_GCiK_Ukz5C4e1lNIOEcLZCTDzIfiHHj-vIQq63xhXAaK9YCZU7XfGbPUUxGijysXj1eSaIlmBxrZKlbaJKqyEYIkdMTp9qB07Xveb2cXT6GCEp9Wl9FvQ2eWOMJB7fYpiJ0MAqU2rb_SNF7cgUfGfFbMpmGtkShvdqyHDA\"></p><p><br></p><p><strong>顏值爆錶</strong></p><p><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">《PAC-MAN》雖然是一款很古早的電玩，而且也不像瑪利歐那樣一直有新的系列作誕生～但憑藉著超級可愛的形象，多年來一直都還是深植人心～甚至在2015年上映的《Pexels 世界大對戰》當中，外星人也選擇了PAC-MAN來跟人類對戰～</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">這次的《步步為營 PAC-MAN版》也不只是漂亮而已，整個遊戲的配件質感都很棒～甚至在眼睛看不到的地方，主圖板的底部防滑都做得很用心～整體呈現出來的結果，也讓我看到它第一眼就決定一定要把它放在我的第六百篇部落格中～</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">回頭講特殊模式，雖然逸馬的影片裡面是小精靈樂勝。但我玩的場次裡面，常常都是鬼魂勝利，就算是小精靈勝利，也常常至少要到第三條命才獲勝～不管是扮演哪一方都是相當有挑戰的遊戲，我覺得不管是在遊戲性上，或是原作的重現度上，都是表現相當好的改編～甚至可以毫不誇張的說，比起經典的《步步為營》規則，我更喜歡這次的PAC-MAN版本～</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">最後就不多囉嗦了，給大家看更多照片～這遊戲真的不怕你拍～只是會怕自己沒有拍好，沒辦法呈現出它有多可愛～</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjuirTIp-qc9rpv7-WAnzgRe2zpJBfI8A1hfLbdvoufM7wH7fuWX1MB1Zs6uV2aCS37AaYebaciA1OFyxpSLAoiJ7hMBry0iy6JYuaTSFrfntaZqdUeojvfSkJzq1yf2m5dH0V0pBKBJ2_DeOIMDuSr1RPMoJqf2hLanAym-wXY6x9n1QccJQq0YdPMyHE/s5222/DSC05128.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjuirTIp-qc9rpv7-WAnzgRe2zpJBfI8A1hfLbdvoufM7wH7fuWX1MB1Zs6uV2aCS37AaYebaciA1OFyxpSLAoiJ7hMBry0iy6JYuaTSFrfntaZqdUeojvfSkJzq1yf2m5dH0V0pBKBJ2_DeOIMDuSr1RPMoJqf2hLanAym-wXY6x9n1QccJQq0YdPMyHE/s600/DSC05128.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgkzmsqwS-i0XqclNclmhvBA8a9uJ31OtO9YUMJbXYsTvyAu6x8STzqVZnuwtCec5U_Jeagvpe0NHY9F_ZQj3il7Yku3xdJEcuJ-yPXLXGmiaQT6HQC4e3ttEJCDvefL2I5TCVIzXiJZFin30huo2gDT5NBvJpgXhP2VZnc-aW3j8wJbHeBR5NuDIMF-ko/s5472/DSC05129.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgkzmsqwS-i0XqclNclmhvBA8a9uJ31OtO9YUMJbXYsTvyAu6x8STzqVZnuwtCec5U_Jeagvpe0NHY9F_ZQj3il7Yku3xdJEcuJ-yPXLXGmiaQT6HQC4e3ttEJCDvefL2I5TCVIzXiJZFin30huo2gDT5NBvJpgXhP2VZnc-aW3j8wJbHeBR5NuDIMF-ko/s600/DSC05129.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhxTj5T5ERTKO8Ct1RgHB6cVSIy07kT14czhvLi9TtTU1H4N8m1lJsNaG9c7BtAfuDUV7JAHaZAOdkTn8MEDEh0_LEDcZVAggiflzsUhorqFjVXM2MZIIqLtdejFjNnDv9pcrr2QA5EdPKom-9pXepLf-XENacfKz-zQXxUQs7pHJis2M0zGerpFTks6WA/s5028/DSC05130.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhxTj5T5ERTKO8Ct1RgHB6cVSIy07kT14czhvLi9TtTU1H4N8m1lJsNaG9c7BtAfuDUV7JAHaZAOdkTn8MEDEh0_LEDcZVAggiflzsUhorqFjVXM2MZIIqLtdejFjNnDv9pcrr2QA5EdPKom-9pXepLf-XENacfKz-zQXxUQs7pHJis2M0zGerpFTks6WA/s600/DSC05130.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhm1uYYlNzLGlWe4KNnaUK0889ldjVOt_rwV7pNQ_7-COOlZDU1OkAHWOnwYxTcFMVcKfa3Dq2TMwQOkCb27y1C08GNjGmWuWwBe5Y7OFZEQXi655mISzkMpkYAx3f58xMX5I3YX6VYs0zZNHOg3b4Ssl7CSskwvym4xl5ScJqLRQ-Q-AMr0m-7izXybfA/s4316/DSC05131.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhm1uYYlNzLGlWe4KNnaUK0889ldjVOt_rwV7pNQ_7-COOlZDU1OkAHWOnwYxTcFMVcKfa3Dq2TMwQOkCb27y1C08GNjGmWuWwBe5Y7OFZEQXi655mISzkMpkYAx3f58xMX5I3YX6VYs0zZNHOg3b4Ssl7CSskwvym4xl5ScJqLRQ-Q-AMr0m-7izXybfA/s600/DSC05131.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲遊戲收納照～整款唯一可以嫌棄的地方，就是這個收納太緊，東西不是很好拿出來～</p><p><br></p>', '2024-11-18 09:42:04', '2024-11-18 09:42:04', 1, 'forum-1731894124680-503487444.jpg'),
