com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhR21i9Xzio5c2rUFBkhQ3fkYYEGWTQ-ZTlDWXXAddYjewLF0XPFYYee7lFQKyMbjyh9gd7qJq0ETYLsPWq0v_hZAxz-YXpfsrPR9OvNQaMINhdSMvrmKGE1A__e7BpC8ZA1RJyLtq6yCymZi90Gimjkj8wsijob5FVlTYTu1hf58gVVmX-xFavdz3-_ug/s600/DSC05245.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲內容物一覽</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjFkYhSPfshvPCleQY2EhP44FXr2yNSpDFKEglGH4n_506sv9-sH3gWoz54WTkG25onC6u2cdDa9s_LH8JI9b5kqM9trgliYPQD1qg8g9rfUYgCEht9NNd8ZZ3ahVk6OgNidd8uf6YdmxDn-GHD-ummvj2avz3uBkQ9t_BvVNZooFMgPeP8SzCXK5gdX28/s3900/DSC05246.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjFkYhSPfshvPCleQY2EhP44FXr2yNSpDFKEglGH4n_506sv9-sH3gWoz54WTkG25onC6u2cdDa9s_LH8JI9b5kqM9trgliYPQD1qg8g9rfUYgCEht9NNd8ZZ3ahVk6OgNidd8uf6YdmxDn-GHD-ummvj2avz3uBkQ9t_BvVNZooFMgPeP8SzCXK5gdX28/s600/DSC05246.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲說明書也超可愛</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiqvP9YQQ2AeRog6sCsDMipRG1CXHix6EWqRcjA6Z1903TmAFdbISQS9ZMQzDzKN5IQ_JVmrb_U_TJ2H-rZerfDElxvjFadgxrT2CsnTnFsn63UCZGlLiHU2ajvYSIuJNpW_E8sRfMziWEyUFGV2VumeAw_v9ywxs4awyoRDiha8bUFTGKodJWvqcG-3LE/s3920/DSC05247.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiqvP9YQQ2AeRog6sCsDMipRG1CXHix6EWqRcjA6Z1903TmAFdbISQS9ZMQzDzKN5IQ_JVmrb_U_TJ2H-rZerfDElxvjFadgxrT2CsnTnFsn63UCZGlLiHU2ajvYSIuJNpW_E8sRfMziWEyUFGV2VumeAw_v9ywxs4awyoRDiha8bUFTGKodJWvqcG-3LE/s600/DSC05247.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲內容都有圖例，很好理解</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhENgB-gbmtkpCPPT194ylkpSbjGKS9mNJwO2A_AUhgMIh0kXv4dlY3pwf5yI-roBqXP3JA51EKxxzsM9yazlxPda6XVvAFxr3WBbeJnSlUv8whFTdAaCBKT2XAPhencs1rPn83PCCArAVfvfcqHThsMu0x0b7vW1HUmmzRvN9Cz1S0N5lyaOtFiNIHMxk/s4156/DSC05248.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhENgB-gbmtkpCPPT194ylkpSbjGKS9mNJwO2A_AUhgMIh0kXv4dlY3pwf5yI-roBqXP3JA51EKxxzsM9yazlxPda6XVvAFxr3WBbeJnSlUv8whFTdAaCBKT2XAPhencs1rPn83PCCArAVfvfcqHThsMu0x0b7vW1HUmmzRvN9Cz1S0N5lyaOtFiNIHMxk/s600/DSC05248.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲卡片有好幾種</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiF-V25u9fsbeQJ5hNGvuLWawVKYFucc76p8FgFNyvbZor5yXFhJV-mGbMJ-sfa1Mf3GMoxlw52kZ6a6ESJinvnQUSr__-s8Mgw3OknZFy889W2Mb4s9kn_d_6LmUkKoS3HYxWZ2KyTWwln1Od4RkNkrS4tQrj-HbaTP5HUmsGbkC6_j2Ts_IOYPEWilz0/s4532/DSC05249.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiF-V25u9fsbeQJ5hNGvuLWawVKYFucc76p8FgFNyvbZor5yXFhJV-mGbMJ-sfa1Mf3GMoxlw52kZ6a6ESJinvnQUSr__-s8Mgw3OknZFy889W2Mb4s9kn_d_6LmUkKoS3HYxWZ2KyTWwln1Od4RkNkrS4tQrj-HbaTP5HUmsGbkC6_j2Ts_IOYPEWilz0/s600/DSC05249.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲第一種是罐罐卡，每位玩家都有一種顏色的罐罐卡～</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgIGORFLOZ0qC0E9YTI7Igny_WUheythCyuZx8y8-HMx2sjmvKwjc5WUz4Pq4Wq7HBS6i2EqH8ZQp2u69Us7sKV0BwOpM7qCv5YQQa6gSP4gsjJrcxGTkoMdehNNQbqac-LHW0-PbNoZLKV_PgOp4IT6R0_cIjpCC_ccfCi_F2aAIPRnnxeqW_13UJ3DaE/s4472/DSC05250.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgIGORFLOZ0qC0E9YTI7Igny_WUheythCyuZx8y8-HMx2sjmvKwjc5WUz4Pq4Wq7HBS6i2EqH8ZQp2u69Us7sKV0BwOpM7qCv5YQQa6gSP4gsjJrcxGTkoMdehNNQbqac-LHW0-PbNoZLKV_PgOp4IT6R0_cIjpCC_ccfCi_F2aAIPRnnxeqW_13UJ3DaE/s600/DSC05250.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲起始玩家卡一張</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhsbTTpmTniQNbf8W1stEhVPqVGduOH-vhofH8-tkO8_Bqc8OKdwEN3EIOaMLXjUPT-DBgsS-Cq6T6NzrBJsYbWdAUUZICQbr6c-y533e8WJq7X2FNjDqVkMvihyxSZP2H4rcc31GYvW1ZTLi1EkuH2XibiGKWFgZNkOTypvEcIYvK9C-snT8z9evzmPmI/s3840/DSC05252.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhsbTTpmTniQNbf8W1stEhVPqVGduOH-vhofH8-tkO8_Bqc8OKdwEN3EIOaMLXjUPT-DBgsS-Cq6T6NzrBJsYbWdAUUZICQbr6c-y533e8WJq7X2FNjDqVkMvihyxSZP2H4rcc31GYvW1ZTLi1EkuH2XibiGKWFgZNkOTypvEcIYvK9C-snT8z9evzmPmI/s600/DSC05252.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲情境卡，每張上面會有兩種情境</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEh0pAQNljpMOG20pYkyACkxIGfPCdeAGgmZLFcy51wjwDpV71idg_OhWALbD5LsDbhRSgUGglvt5A2OFik4rPe_aeqpDiK43xmvqiRWQjAt3uHCfdRZLa364WFcQHbO1ZsJNHCTwW9oL1X4_gaQgstOr1a5MwdNvRtZnWEB0rC5trk55zMb0x9Ps91pOs0/s4236/DSC05253.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEh0pAQNljpMOG20pYkyACkxIGfPCdeAGgmZLFcy51wjwDpV71idg_OhWALbD5LsDbhRSgUGglvt5A2OFik4rPe_aeqpDiK43xmvqiRWQjAt3uHCfdRZLa364WFcQHbO1ZsJNHCTwW9oL1X4_gaQgstOr1a5MwdNvRtZnWEB0rC5trk55zMb0x9Ps91pOs0/s600/DSC05253.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲貓格特質牌，上面的貓貓都好可愛～</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgZDfDEzhbqjkqRAkeh8YxktUW6i5U2IZEm26tDVGX-F9aLMeLbCjiZj3jpjC3PoVyqVz0vdYlFjdPmlPQKvTWPMdXQFLyRD9m09X341pf-Yqrv1mqGS-fDd4qR-yi9ebYabXaaEUDEgUvIKvp1ia2IhYHLl25MQjENQjSdzok9_c_z08s4ExiP4MjTWOI/s4940/DSC05254.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgZDfDEzhbqjkqRAkeh8YxktUW6i5U2IZEm26tDVGX-F9aLMeLbCjiZj3jpjC3PoVyqVz0vdYlFjdPmlPQKvTWPMdXQFLyRD9m09X341pf-Yqrv1mqGS-fDd4qR-yi9ebYabXaaEUDEgUvIKvp1ia2IhYHLl25MQjENQjSdzok9_c_z08s4ExiP4MjTWOI/s600/DSC05254.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲貓貓可愛到爆炸</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEim8agiKf1cLDEfwHv9iMDhsoyNWELINrupSro6oV6V7ETDoZ-L0RAXQTKW3iDYo4huuSWLPiFWlyBuPjrHpFDMDWCjiYfGQCkqjQv1l0YpdZh8UZxjb8ZRJ3CIUsTXtf0zY8z29LDaaJDdAC4vky4wovoHushC09vQ1_t5Ow3inRAott1PjfFV4meks2E\"></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhdy2ccZAffPfNhy0ERrWPOFrDgLNCxJJVunZIr3znsbTHmk4qGmnTtrFlbw5F2J_TqCYSkS16XNnfxpx-xJu4MbFfS5tdMj01U68qmpUzpbfhVRVNyjm5UnIc1NDsHnH2SIRBxkOulRR15lc4mdMX3AmxB_kJAZ6WUTdXEuxLk89lJ2-B1Ax5vYw7Yn4c/s600/DSC05260.JPG\"></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲先抽一張情境卡，然後大家一起決定要選擇哪個情境</p><p><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgZhDhnwu4N-DveNhEmYsWNDf8EjcZ34Ici1HCuyifgHTcJqWtgoDeA1xX6CI1TvVT_Vwfv0ZEzlP4UaZNnhLZSNXaUHddJCm7FvIISJXrM32YIDWjtVHR-AeTGv-BtgDhmOp3ktXaoLxYaz_entGUx9IlonZnZAvS8R3qmCcpea7487uM0S1aA9DgzK64/s4800/DSC05259.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgZhDhnwu4N-DveNhEmYsWNDf8EjcZ34Ici1HCuyifgHTcJqWtgoDeA1xX6CI1TvVT_Vwfv0ZEzlP4UaZNnhLZSNXaUHddJCm7FvIISJXrM32YIDWjtVHR-AeTGv-BtgDhmOp3ktXaoLxYaz_entGUx9IlonZnZAvS8R3qmCcpea7487uM0S1aA9DgzK64/s600/DSC05259.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲接著發給每位玩家一組罐罐卡（有些卡片上面有人數限制）</p><p><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjPyYvDUZOsNXu8eyHORkYfAZTRlp541DaTIEyT0Fm0ZZ2tXXi9GO2glkIArXai0dKh27WddCxiTE-IO-6PFw7pPfibussGpwHFsDAUpuplcOVjgIdPZgHH9_P7sgk_VZkqEAPI0v_ZubZ2brfTK6yk7P7ObdDiy4gjBRmIDyZwKo_Md1fZnwPPxMi-G6w/s5100/DSC05261.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjPyYvDUZOsNXu8eyHORkYfAZTRlp541DaTIEyT0Fm0ZZ2tXXi9GO2glkIArXai0dKh27WddCxiTE-IO-6PFw7pPfibussGpwHFsDAUpuplcOVjgIdPZgHH9_P7sgk_VZkqEAPI0v_ZubZ2brfTK6yk7P7ObdDiy4gjBRmIDyZwKo_Md1fZnwPPxMi-G6w/s600/DSC05261.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲翻開人數＋１的貓格特質牌</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEi8jDJ6xDrQVP0bPEmDRBpvp69Da41ZzrHfcxbItaJMzVYucUpivAwXLIfWAT7NQ7riHNvTOaWDvkOfLVQ8YfsofLwYmXTwZVHQRAj3IWe7s3G2GvfuATPpLGCuOzuT6fb-nSm5tgfxXfy3K0vAEs6QUTAl4njMwagJV4w_5fR7gm4skeH8WG386kf2RT8/s4940/DSC05262.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEi8jDJ6xDrQVP0bPEmDRBpvp69Da41ZzrHfcxbItaJMzVYucUpivAwXLIfWAT7NQ7riHNvTOaWDvkOfLVQ8YfsofLwYmXTwZVHQRAj3IWe7s3G2GvfuATPpLGCuOzuT6fb-nSm5tgfxXfy3K0vAEs6QUTAl4njMwagJV4w_5fR7gm4skeH8WG386kf2RT8/s600/DSC05262.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">▲由起始玩家開始，選擇一張貓格特質牌帶回家。接著大家輪流選，直到場上只剩一張貓格特質牌後再補到玩家＋１張～然後順時鐘換下一位玩家當起始玩家，大家繼續挑選好朋友的特質～</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjVFub2vLeDrYkkMKNEE4A3xTDUDrqjOgYpYMl9D_TIZd4kOma3bMYnvTBwXGAapn_aLQ8NC1PNfDG3jOaabiDs9cKR68L4iFi6EraMH8Ej1wyA2IEKs1sken-oB_yH1Cx0lz4vMt-Yha3uCSr4sTfnXYDOgYNcLly4HbK_BjWbS7BCjApjWd30DSrZYiw/s4264/DSC05263.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjVFub2vLeDrYkkMKNEE4A3xTDUDrqjOgYpYMl9D_TIZd4kOma3bMYnvTBwXGAapn_aLQ8NC1PNfDG3jOaabiDs9cKR68L4iFi6EraMH8Ej1wyA2IEKs1sken-oB_yH1Cx0lz4vMt-Yha3uCSr4sTfnXYDOgYNcLly4HbK_BjWbS7BCjApjWd30DSrZYiw/s600/DSC05263.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">▲直到所有人都拿到三張貓格特質牌之後，大家輪流解釋為什麼你會選擁有這三種貓格特質的朋友一起去面對那個情境～我這邊直接舉個例子～</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">這回合我們玩的是『一起成為屠龍勇者的時候』，為了成為欣梅爾勇者，一路上一定會遇到許多不同的冒險，遇到各式各樣的困難～因此我會需要我的朋友<strong><u>有條理</u></strong>，幫我們制定各種計畫，規劃我們冒險的路線～同時也需要朋友<strong><u>易怒</u></strong>，在冒險的旅途中遇到各式各樣的壞人才不會在氣勢上吃虧。當然，更需要這位朋友可以很有<strong><u>毅力</u></strong>，才能讓我們艱辛的旅程能夠順利到最後～</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">所有人都發表完之後，大家就會用手上的罐罐卡幫你打分數～</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhlQjo-QiCdO89lLAQOhuZJpa3Vt8P-ibvXZqRWBqETqWNQXcUH1hcmW_7P1ZruW4WIUSvvItuk7HhyphenhyphenmrIks9y0LCSsMTeDVQvAvdD0OwpH5AFDpj-5S_hQFAXOrvUGyIMOo606clgTwJMYy1dI0bT_x_ew1PCMsdn8xzp0rEq94qj40MvTLR-idlsjeJg/s3940/DSC05264.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhlQjo-QiCdO89lLAQOhuZJpa3Vt8P-ibvXZqRWBqETqWNQXcUH1hcmW_7P1ZruW4WIUSvvItuk7HhyphenhyphenmrIks9y0LCSsMTeDVQvAvdD0OwpH5AFDpj-5S_hQFAXOrvUGyIMOo606clgTwJMYy1dI0bT_x_ew1PCMsdn8xzp0rEq94qj40MvTLR-idlsjeJg/s600/DSC05264.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲如果我拿到這樣的罐罐卡，我就得６分！</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">（３＋２＋１）</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEiYbh5ZNhgL3QWxTiO9ZKf4jv95tgiXvjsaqGl30jCUqgwJyk5onnPX739IRgNXS69jmtVDTGwDWXaylhxyYz2shhCchboJrExzfnllNXFseSKo2uc14FU7HKZ3gx9uF0HoIQgkny2zOFODXOOC4lD2Wx7Fdlqg2SPdgwHqkSh97Sb61LhZFVTUuHq0aVI\"></p><p><br></p><p><strong>貓貓好可愛</strong></p><p><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">這遊戲除了規則本身就很可愛之外，貓貓們更是可愛到不像話！我本人是個狗派，但被這些貓弄到快要彎過去了～遊戲的規則很簡單也很輕鬆，就算是沒有玩過桌遊的人也能馬上上手，是一款很適合派對或是破冰的遊戲～如果是拿來在類似聯誼的場合，就可以更快打開大家的話匣子，也更容易去了解一位新朋友～</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">所有的好朋友卡除了有超可愛的貓貓插圖之外，也都有各種性格與個性的表現～可以感受到製作上的用心～光是看這些卡片就有種心靈被療癒的感覺～情境卡的設計也是相當天馬行空，各種狀況都有，但其實只要玩家們有創意，情境是絕對用不完的，想要玩什麼情境就玩什麼情境～</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiiZm2v4xIwVkicS0r_91rZDuFCOduVNK-1F6EG0ZBpXizx8Q-gN6KT2AxXYUAlcZCp4I5tpMjY47ddzKKW9he38x4vF_beBSFmc2Czr0_CP8MLCvHV9NgVuSdxiPwMyZskVugO6RDUUUVJ5TbdJ5rE9V4suvpZdBNZt50_lSflyKd6hNQ8ldkl-Ik-YDY/w640-h200/dasd.png\"></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲這邊偷偷跟大家說，我的測試結果是INFJ性格，據說是最少見的人格類型～</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">想要知道自己是哪一種類型的性格，可以在<a href=\"https://www.16personalities.com/tw/%E6%80%A7%E6%A0%BC%E6%B8%AC%E8%A9%A6\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">這個網站</a>測試喔～</p><p><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjZBFIoiJZnju8NtuPTX6a2DqhcehIcfd4MS88D_Sh0nNowRpH2hv5YUv9_RMdYotoQrWWXKLaq4vhce3hH76GylXuZxCFqOOHFTtKEbm1GTB-xKnICh-AYGdyDFdKEorZb2PmebSPysjVexmmeRZqw-5-WHNdO9gHnL8EBTejOtr8SPSPil5OwFFzFBdQ/s3272/DSC05255.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjZBFIoiJZnju8NtuPTX6a2DqhcehIcfd4MS88D_Sh0nNowRpH2hv5YUv9_RMdYotoQrWWXKLaq4vhce3hH76GylXuZxCFqOOHFTtKEbm1GTB-xKnICh-AYGdyDFdKEorZb2PmebSPysjVexmmeRZqw-5-WHNdO9gHnL8EBTejOtr8SPSPil5OwFFzFBdQ/s600/DSC05255.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲這邊是一些INFJ的卡片，某些部分跟我真的很像～</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">（卡片內沒有I卡，因為都被歸類在Big 5的E裡面了）</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhlg1SSJB6xuHG1kR_GGes9_S45X6FScMazrzh1UMARdPKjZL-Tladqps8dULSOb_OFmea8S4qPMOtIdIh_rJY7KWnVWGO2vRFOht3xpE07ZHCsgWp-6JMRFzDqKDxBsjZt2mQ_lG07BSTxnEyhZ271QRNnu7B5cpFYbsDxpmVVoWazXG2PgMowK1hl8x4/s3240/DSC05257.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhlg1SSJB6xuHG1kR_GGes9_S45X6FScMazrzh1UMARdPKjZL-Tladqps8dULSOb_OFmea8S4qPMOtIdIh_rJY7KWnVWGO2vRFOht3xpE07ZHCsgWp-6JMRFzDqKDxBsjZt2mQ_lG07BSTxnEyhZ271QRNnu7B5cpFYbsDxpmVVoWazXG2PgMowK1hl8x4/s600/DSC05257.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲額外照一些Big-5的卡片給大家看，都很可愛</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiBZOzl5pY93KwufteMpTjabOUJXQYPhX1pDQkjff__6VreuvM7XcUZBvO_yE98YniS91R1XaDHvIWg1MfktO0XzWRQsGR3AapxPYWyYeLt3mXUpc3KqehXykkmpyk0cYtc_QsF0jrA574pBmnMF66nDB_6-fMvKtJHr47wntGR26rzFtFFDiQM9AskKDo/s5080/DSC05266.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiBZOzl5pY93KwufteMpTjabOUJXQYPhX1pDQkjff__6VreuvM7XcUZBvO_yE98YniS91R1XaDHvIWg1MfktO0XzWRQsGR3AapxPYWyYeLt3mXUpc3KqehXykkmpyk0cYtc_QsF0jrA574pBmnMF66nDB_6-fMvKtJHr47wntGR26rzFtFFDiQM9AskKDo/s600/DSC05266.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲遊戲收納照</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEj5cRdI1qvL3ow6pJLc3OWOdL9r67Id1FxmOQ_qUphEeVDGlpoajlkz6iCCOfEGApMF3fAMRmWc6aRSlRkoG-yVZJP7aG-Z9hYJLFYCJpkysgjhOAdXYY0gnFj1s9acDnX55MUTihSwFoB58uBknJ0pq3mQoUBeQYr50Ec0BevGdMmxWIxJQiyFJ5MRag0/s5472/DSC05258.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEj5cRdI1qvL3ow6pJLc3OWOdL9r67Id1FxmOQ_qUphEeVDGlpoajlkz6iCCOfEGApMF3fAMRmWc6aRSlRkoG-yVZJP7aG-Z9hYJLFYCJpkysgjhOAdXYY0gnFj1s9acDnX55MUTihSwFoB58uBknJ0pq3mQoUBeQYr50Ec0BevGdMmxWIxJQiyFJ5MRag0/s600/DSC05258.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲好奇心不會殺死貓，但會殺死芙莉蓮　ＸＤ</p><p>張貼者：&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.blogger.com/profile/09653142042534482709\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">小羊&nbsp;</a>於&nbsp;<a href=\"https://usnoopy.blogspot.com/2024/08/blog-post.html\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">上午10:37:00</a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.blogger.com/share-post.g?blogID=5459019143384602630&amp;postID=1804581207816010477&amp;target=email\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">以電子郵件傳送這篇文章</a></p><p><a href=\"https://www.blogger.com/share-post.g?blogID=5459019143384602630&amp;postID=1804581207816010477&amp;target=blog\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">BlogThis！</a></p><p><a href=\"https://www.blogger.com/share-post.g?blogID=5459019143384602630&amp;postID=1804581207816010477&amp;target=twitter\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">分享至 X</a></p><p><a href=\"https://www.blogger.com/share-post.g?blogID=5459019143384602630&amp;postID=1804581207816010477&amp;target=facebook\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">分享至 Facebook</a></p><p><a href=\"https://www.blogger.com/share-post.g?blogID=5459019143384602630&amp;postID=1804581207816010477&amp;target=pinterest\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">分享到 Pinterest</a></p><p><br></p>', '2024-11-18 09:43:38', '2024-11-18 09:45:49', 1, 'forum-1731894218045-534650039.jpg');
INSERT INTO `forum_posts` (`id`, `user_id`, `title`, `content`, `created_at`, `updated_at`, `status`, `cover_image`) VALUES
(10, 1, '【桌遊開箱報】 Open Season 獵頭季 簡中版 開箱+介紹', '<h3><br></h3><p><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiThA794l1Jkag10GqDtLxyXEw4naTJYw8vV0URj13aHPDe9YZnIX4fRUpjPJxdJjGW5zhDEgdAQSLi3EXVQvXWPdAlHUYfYiStbzT3TO6caPvWJoQXiHLkB0D0W4pOXGdY02n88NebySYth38NEONNbrUXUq-53qnAdof7NyBSlDc2kDZWO-rXg6EBlnk/s3364/DSC05100.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiThA794l1Jkag10GqDtLxyXEw4naTJYw8vV0URj13aHPDe9YZnIX4fRUpjPJxdJjGW5zhDEgdAQSLi3EXVQvXWPdAlHUYfYiStbzT3TO6caPvWJoQXiHLkB0D0W4pOXGdY02n88NebySYth38NEONNbrUXUq-53qnAdof7NyBSlDc2kDZWO-rXg6EBlnk/s600/DSC05100.JPG\"></a></p><p><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEhv2DiXmQzC9J3Fr9bACz2Zcw39buqwMoqeTvtk2F02DLUyoftW_hbKIj4qipKykCm3inKZ_0dE4MIEWjrmI1wxrBz5n_czLfcKo6WiTcN572F9C0zDBljpqMVr3jTZmTsmRL2T81fTlcLQqcZVy6qzpspnJkDfscqvL4wUuGcuVzIml2Qjfe2LosMgU0o\"></p><p><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">身為魔王的你，已經受夠了這些煩死人的矮人、精靈、半獸人、死靈法師。。。。他們總以為自己是勇者，打著正義的旗幟破壞你悠閒的退休生活～看著家中的牆壁，你突然有了一個念頭：『這面牆看起來空空蕩蕩的，不如我來做點手工藝增加些裝飾品～』於是，《獵頭季》就此展開，想打擾你清夢的人，一個也不會放過！</p><p><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEh4k4vF8_6OaIXoWDX2uMflZtcp1Csa4sdq7OZpqlgDr5WVvqtFif0jJrFDTPhAxUGJiFtOALCd7Ed-Y-XyW_b78vP582EJEfkzfPdALAqwoO-irtnm3ordBJXEFJW4ESvS1QFDuKVBebvAfzfIizrDOAqE4v_ELfIivvW9GclB53gx3JW6RGbVJMWxpb0\"></p><p><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiThA794l1Jkag10GqDtLxyXEw4naTJYw8vV0URj13aHPDe9YZnIX4fRUpjPJxdJjGW5zhDEgdAQSLi3EXVQvXWPdAlHUYfYiStbzT3TO6caPvWJoQXiHLkB0D0W4pOXGdY02n88NebySYth38NEONNbrUXUq-53qnAdof7NyBSlDc2kDZWO-rXg6EBlnk/s3364/DSC05100.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiThA794l1Jkag10GqDtLxyXEw4naTJYw8vV0URj13aHPDe9YZnIX4fRUpjPJxdJjGW5zhDEgdAQSLi3EXVQvXWPdAlHUYfYiStbzT3TO6caPvWJoQXiHLkB0D0W4pOXGdY02n88NebySYth38NEONNbrUXUq-53qnAdof7NyBSlDc2kDZWO-rXg6EBlnk/s600/DSC05100.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲封面就可以看到各種精美的『收藏』</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiBNB-B7sVRs-Iq8rG9xPC_dHin1H8w8_C-3vrDr70gb_0cbXTJGoB-y336m8k6pwbT5s4CK2hHRuQPSSYM-ExTnnbaYYDFnRPpdv5I3NRHmdx2sgNM2bdldNKbKzr_bgvEi1tGwMfCLkU6-ZEHWHz6D_5vidqWOIc1TmUcxJPQtQ9Hy4JYg7p9VjnCnEk/s3952/DSC05101.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiBNB-B7sVRs-Iq8rG9xPC_dHin1H8w8_C-3vrDr70gb_0cbXTJGoB-y336m8k6pwbT5s4CK2hHRuQPSSYM-ExTnnbaYYDFnRPpdv5I3NRHmdx2sgNM2bdldNKbKzr_bgvEi1tGwMfCLkU6-ZEHWHz6D_5vidqWOIc1TmUcxJPQtQ9Hy4JYg7p9VjnCnEk/s600/DSC05101.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲遊戲人數：2-4人　建議年齡：10+　遊戲時間：15mins/每人</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">（這個主題確定年齡設定１０＋ＯＫ嗎？）</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgs5ZmL7hVnv1NP9z5CaCfk7FN-_yDrdXelOpoK1kGuH1BRSicPFKqxH9Ihyey2AFc39F7EjUaFQKxPweCxs6NQDZq68DQnvChQpChs9CzGt4hnpWlUHwBU67ZNT8YamG8vjQ_c39BK0GwvJ4XB1W3KCGOJ54v2mcXwbyVdqSfmNHTZdLsdI757omIIFrQ/s3428/DSC05102.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgs5ZmL7hVnv1NP9z5CaCfk7FN-_yDrdXelOpoK1kGuH1BRSicPFKqxH9Ihyey2AFc39F7EjUaFQKxPweCxs6NQDZq68DQnvChQpChs9CzGt4hnpWlUHwBU67ZNT8YamG8vjQ_c39BK0GwvJ4XB1W3KCGOJ54v2mcXwbyVdqSfmNHTZdLsdI757omIIFrQ/s600/DSC05102.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲盒底有遊戲概況</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEh-o1ugCG7ZGirQQVaUgWgPWcXdbVrglr_C7wZX8EhkhdJXM6qQa5a3MaZ-UMycDJGd6vYztl0U80SzRIrMcKn-GznxlZZGy38lps-a3AKLLNQBPRdPi-5gC6E56KzZ6QMoY3iPvtK5cAwP2kQapTThbE426Mh1CYTWKuFa65r35yFzMaiGDeQQk85DWvE/s4924/DSC05103.JPG\" rel=\"noo