99oQUhfRIqO85VEsjwEJx2VKcM3eGzxeIzXEV1Raq3qOUim4iI917z_EM5R_lQiCuvFmM9yd46IXJPSGpMVDhT4V-dl5jYzSsIjTFUQNP9L1MyjkzCuMabiRPTUY9YeRiK68EhGT94k_87oWl9IO8aynm3G_Ip0tdSMLWXbSApUaE/s4688/DSC04867.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjg1RV4RWNikyEhR499oQUhfRIqO85VEsjwEJx2VKcM3eGzxeIzXEV1Raq3qOUim4iI917z_EM5R_lQiCuvFmM9yd46IXJPSGpMVDhT4V-dl5jYzSsIjTFUQNP9L1MyjkzCuMabiRPTUY9YeRiK68EhGT94k_87oWl9IO8aynm3G_Ip0tdSMLWXbSApUaE/s600/DSC04867.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲題目卡一大疊（而且題目卡本身也是一種樂器的樣貌，很可愛）</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEh7khaa2vSPXkvTe9SfouowddjCtYFhLSxwn-_1dvg7tJqC2K1S9tAkcpEeWjOR9ufSSr1sgKeioRuC8Rzk94mor1CGAqRlpj-c2gPVzYHbFA26ktfAXJZs6lT-q6eUxMSQmkYL9llZRKaj3iXINJDpujQo0fnkoYDsO80Q5EiK0Dwv4Va3iby4sUpFZS0\"></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhAd_K4DDzaBLmXiHttPcKQ8q1pPh1Wh_8jcoBAYkYn5bA2FE3AsyEP6-m5RhjJTeOzVYnrNFMq6TQN5Anpxn_qWfyj-I3ef95ZrQdEJYAfgOYWfNenx55zzDuJcdSLZWHRZMAyJZTYdlpwIIcaSbHs9DBZAo4aYD5RvVAlPbCYurzxl_k8S8Ez2RbFGq4/s5232/DSC04868.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhAd_K4DDzaBLmXiHttPcKQ8q1pPh1Wh_8jcoBAYkYn5bA2FE3AsyEP6-m5RhjJTeOzVYnrNFMq6TQN5Anpxn_qWfyj-I3ef95ZrQdEJYAfgOYWfNenx55zzDuJcdSLZWHRZMAyJZTYdlpwIIcaSbHs9DBZAo4aYD5RvVAlPbCYurzxl_k8S8Ez2RbFGq4/s600/DSC04868.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲遊戲開始，會隨機抽出８張題目卡，洗好之後形成牌庫～</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">每位玩家拿一個樂器轉盤～</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiRLzTvcaqRB4PTIreAyETjZjnMeqPM0zKeLdvseYKKIn6k0-0gBPQrrtt6ImkruoRZBG98SMSf6xTG9JiuGK5EgITzDo_NQev4WwAHanB65QUhbxCwuXQVn0s3lvICIPqIyEVmJ2FTYhdz0jP-w-K75KCx5sXj0dOVQSNLoQ-WAVNZbPIrl7q-PnblnXY/s4956/DSC04869.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiRLzTvcaqRB4PTIreAyETjZjnMeqPM0zKeLdvseYKKIn6k0-0gBPQrrtt6ImkruoRZBG98SMSf6xTG9JiuGK5EgITzDo_NQev4WwAHanB65QUhbxCwuXQVn0s3lvICIPqIyEVmJ2FTYhdz0jP-w-K75KCx5sXj0dOVQSNLoQ-WAVNZbPIrl7q-PnblnXY/s600/DSC04869.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲接著翻開第一張卡片，然後掃描牌庫頂那張卡片的QR code～</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">（翻開與掃描的卡片不同張）</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">▲這邊直接放音樂給大家試玩，聽完之後，你會覺得這首音樂比較符合哪個選項呢？（１）海、（２）太陽、（３）風、（４）陽傘、（５）海浪？用你的樂器轉盤秘密選下答案～</p><p><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiXMpGfLCLsiWjJTECzWjVlTrOBmDYlNvVtkf4naCvsxxiXOUK9ZymLQyf3WQWnch-9Zh9ahzDA6-8I51DUZqu2qVxczHKbnWvwdGpjvQr2m1lc0mkxj3EcHz_EKX9pkaSOhwD7TAzW9m1Hp0apL6mM72IjCjjuvQ93V2vHMWYWyycVUYzIlFWTJkGH-es/s5228/DSC04870.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiXMpGfLCLsiWjJTECzWjVlTrOBmDYlNvVtkf4naCvsxxiXOUK9ZymLQyf3WQWnch-9Zh9ahzDA6-8I51DUZqu2qVxczHKbnWvwdGpjvQr2m1lc0mkxj3EcHz_EKX9pkaSOhwD7TAzW9m1Hp0apL6mM72IjCjjuvQ93V2vHMWYWyycVUYzIlFWTJkGH-es/s600/DSC04870.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">▲接著所有人公開答案～如果所有人的選擇都一樣，我們會得１分～如果有人不同，那這題就沒有得分～接著繼續玩下一張～由於一共有８張卡片，所以共玩七次，看看最後我們可以得到幾分～</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjjCSrzG0R8I9Ky6RDj2yu7GB7lmGoNC5x-hGM66fPKSVz8GrVwcF3rClYzdT1WN5oQzu3kUjpx0e8HdkotpkODoelmsY8nsZFTtnB79k4TRYXNxp-HMRuGTvmKxYyVFfSUv7roCGi-VIvYy3k9d6BhH1UvCDxBu_uQVm61r97XkjC0ksADCq_CAG9Gso0/s4472/DSC04871.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjjCSrzG0R8I9Ky6RDj2yu7GB7lmGoNC5x-hGM66fPKSVz8GrVwcF3rClYzdT1WN5oQzu3kUjpx0e8HdkotpkODoelmsY8nsZFTtnB79k4TRYXNxp-HMRuGTvmKxYyVFfSUv7roCGi-VIvYy3k9d6BhH1UvCDxBu_uQVm61r97XkjC0ksADCq_CAG9Gso0/s600/DSC04871.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">▲此外遊戲中有靜音標記，如果你覺得某位玩家是老鼠屎，可以在開票前，用靜音標記無視他這次的答案。拿到靜音標記的玩家這次的答案會被忽略，但下一回合你可以把靜音標記丟給另一位玩家～大家可以隨意選擇要用幾個靜音標記，標準難度就是都不要用；用兩個靜音標記就是最簡單的難度～</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiRLzTvcaqRB4PTIreAyETjZjnMeqPM0zKeLdvseYKKIn6k0-0gBPQrrtt6ImkruoRZBG98SMSf6xTG9JiuGK5EgITzDo_NQev4WwAHanB65QUhbxCwuXQVn0s3lvICIPqIyEVmJ2FTYhdz0jP-w-K75KCx5sXj0dOVQSNLoQ-WAVNZbPIrl7q-PnblnXY/s600/DSC04869.JPG\"></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲根據遊玩人數的不同，使用的選項數量也不同～</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">２～４人，使用選項１～５</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">５人遊戲，使用選項１～４</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">６人遊戲，使用選項１～３</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgpSj4LhZT4XMygofqCx9Q-UpAjrMCy9IDSwwUOPvya5hA5B8w4XY_V0907JePnAO3h1dEGG5CxOuRDc20BMv35Dhf4yyuXR0HCy11eB887A9za80B0bnJDAYOi34lN59Nhk1i2y5Iw2xN-egDuUWmRvMgAi3iEIfn54Csvp3sMJ5zJoVNJxgKhWg-EZCU/s5440/DSC04872.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgpSj4LhZT4XMygofqCx9Q-UpAjrMCy9IDSwwUOPvya5hA5B8w4XY_V0907JePnAO3h1dEGG5CxOuRDc20BMv35Dhf4yyuXR0HCy11eB887A9za80B0bnJDAYOi34lN59Nhk1i2y5Iw2xN-egDuUWmRvMgAi3iEIfn54Csvp3sMJ5zJoVNJxgKhWg-EZCU/s600/DSC04872.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲遊戲盒子的設計很特別，展開會像這樣，合起來的時候會有磁吸～質感不錯～</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">（溫馨提醒，平時使用磁吸不會有問題，但如果要長距離攜帶還是建議固定一下）</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEiYbh5ZNhgL3QWxTiO9ZKf4jv95tgiXvjsaqGl30jCUqgwJyk5onnPX739IRgNXS69jmtVDTGwDWXaylhxyYz2shhCchboJrExzfnllNXFseSKo2uc14FU7HKZ3gx9uF0HoIQgkny2zOFODXOOC4lD2Wx7Fdlqg2SPdgwHqkSh97Sb61LhZFVTUuHq0aVI\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEiYbh5ZNhgL3QWxTiO9ZKf4jv95tgiXvjsaqGl30jCUqgwJyk5onnPX739IRgNXS69jmtVDTGwDWXaylhxyYz2shhCchboJrExzfnllNXFseSKo2uc14FU7HKZ3gx9uF0HoIQgkny2zOFODXOOC4lD2Wx7Fdlqg2SPdgwHqkSh97Sb61LhZFVTUuHq0aVI\"></a></p><p><strong>派對咖孔明！？</strong></p><p><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">超高質感的古典樂曲ＶＳ超鬧的派對遊戲！？到底是哪個人想到把這兩個結合在一起的？但莫名的其實還蠻搭的，加上超可愛的樂器轉盤，拿出配件的那一刻就可以成功吸睛～拿著這盒樣品到處推坑的這幾天，我剛好跟朋友們一起出了一趟遠門～原本隔壁一群在玩狼人殺的朋友，都被我們這一桌的古典樂與白痴笑聲吸引了過來～到後來甚至都跑來要求想要玩～</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">遊戲的本體概念很簡單，所以根本不用講規則就可以開始玩，連文字看不懂的孩子也可以參與（大人唸給他們聽），基本上門檻只要看得懂數字１～５就可以了～算是相當適合闔家歡樂的遊戲～由於題目的音樂跟可選的選項是隨機搭配的，因此有的題目會很鬧，有的則是會很簡單～</p><p><br></p><p>這款遊戲我會推薦給：喜歡古典樂的朋友、喜歡樂器的朋友、需要一款１５分鐘又支援到６人的快速破冰遊戲的朋友～最後當然是附上<a href=\"https://www.zeczec.com/projects/stereo_mind_classical\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">嘖嘖</a>的網址～</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhyHwwNiI4UxkQg26_tgOSv6rV0SXaCiSXMff-9-dq3mzJN0jvw2_Alt8lNGj2jd-qgwA-oxuE_74mLcllnXZaKmULSzGyDoBQLZQIJSEwcVXlseHQiIwW5n6qm-LygS_b1rFvcg2y9I9cBSmOZxPdWfI8wc-mcjC34NsIXJ7FXECnBbKjIQzV5N_b65eQ/s5172/DSC04874.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhyHwwNiI4UxkQg26_tgOSv6rV0SXaCiSXMff-9-dq3mzJN0jvw2_Alt8lNGj2jd-qgwA-oxuE_74mLcllnXZaKmULSzGyDoBQLZQIJSEwcVXlseHQiIwW5n6qm-LygS_b1rFvcg2y9I9cBSmOZxPdWfI8wc-mcjC34NsIXJ7FXECnBbKjIQzV5N_b65eQ/s600/DSC04874.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲遊戲收納照，上了牌套是可以收納的，建議像這樣把卡片分兩疊各塞一半，上面再放配件～</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhlyEoPys6MoRQ41exvUyIWNHh2IloZIkeXIATsZIdYpJgUhYUoW_Xt24umeH9NVBE4cuCC00Ouv1gFIS1KqVRk74S-x-CZeVeLSiYi0lJKinCrSl0IXBeu8gIB7brJcGOFoIetkUm5h7B8RiVG_VH0L7PfAQxnp3R4GfO9fog_OAKmfJR1HKEo2JWyGig/s5420/DSC04873.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhlyEoPys6MoRQ41exvUyIWNHh2IloZIkeXIATsZIdYpJgUhYUoW_Xt24umeH9NVBE4cuCC00Ouv1gFIS1KqVRk74S-x-CZeVeLSiYi0lJKinCrSl0IXBeu8gIB7brJcGOFoIetkUm5h7B8RiVG_VH0L7PfAQxnp3R4GfO9fog_OAKmfJR1HKEo2JWyGig/s600/DSC04873.JPG\"></a></p><p><br></p>', '2024-11-18 10:27:27', '2024-11-18 10:27:27', 1, 'forum-1731896847609-54089467.jpg');
INSERT INTO `forum_posts` (`id`, `user_id`, `title`, `content`, `created_at`, `updated_at`, `status`, `cover_image`) VALUES
(20, 1, '【桌遊開箱報】Sweet & Spicy 貓吃酸辣 開箱+介紹', '<h3><br></h3><p><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhNo9yaEyo9WDv9ui6q3pVvC5kCqTIEUpPkU-Acztj0axlf327SCV9ck-qU752V5js-I6h6f3subAgsdKq9zxhlSImaeEWpcu56yGLMAJSQH1_2QncIMvi3z-4CsmwXFCFoS6mbRzJvnsCp-ZgIeKfgkxRKohauRvpfqIXezmJqZ0QHgP5bmV_AZyC4YZc/s2516/DSC04646.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhNo9yaEyo9WDv9ui6q3pVvC5kCqTIEUpPkU-Acztj0axlf327SCV9ck-qU752V5js-I6h6f3subAgsdKq9zxhlSImaeEWpcu56yGLMAJSQH1_2QncIMvi3z-4CsmwXFCFoS6mbRzJvnsCp-ZgIeKfgkxRKohauRvpfqIXezmJqZ0QHgP5bmV_AZyC4YZc/w479-h640/DSC04646.JPG\"></a></p><p><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEgZeDgIghkA9z8B4IotNGfZTtT4MpzccsPH9IYcb5d1Fq_Yx_jpG1p0bTqKWIKYByV1DmB4OlI0hptmzsdelqYIno-8aDXcv1MP39exhmnNWz4C-Yb2NwQhdGLookCB_ARjNk7PooJi9VYFjZx1052T3Yc-ej9uzVtjaZY6LH25FCE1MoDW0bcGEdCt=w320-h136\"></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">Déjà vu，法文，意思就是『既視感』，指人在清醒的狀態下自認為是第一次見到某場景，卻瞬間感覺之前好像曾經經歷過，是被廣泛報導證實的一種常見的現象。也正是我第一次看到《Sweet &amp; Spicy 貓吃酸辣》時候的感受～是的，你想的沒有錯，這款跟《Spicy 貓吃3辣》是同設計師的姊妹作，兩款在規則上大概有８７％像，但美術風格差異很大！想知道這款新作有什麼不同之處，文章內都會跟大家說明喔～</p><p><br></p><p><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEgYU4HxY-Ij1lmyOq2eAeZykiHU9O76An9b_STPOjxOL_cHs0L2-3Ilt3oy2RNRTePJhm19WBjjLTb3BUkM1Twr6LTLkOY_4PlB77NOywNMd8pGAFlu-E_QMWZAWTiZkNi_VViuJ9bLTsrgj5EEmb75amn2pE7rpeCmJ87J9gSGTly1jnYSFlSPqyxz=w320-h136\"></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhNo9yaEyo9WDv9ui6q3pVvC5kCqTIEUpPkU-Acztj0axlf327SCV9ck-qU752V5js-I6h6f3subAgsdKq9zxhlSImaeEWpcu56yGLMAJSQH1_2QncIMvi3z-4CsmwXFCFoS6mbRzJvnsCp-ZgIeKfgkxRKohauRvpfqIXezmJqZ0QHgP5bmV_AZyC4YZc/s2516/DSC04646.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhNo9yaEyo9WDv9ui6q3pVvC5kCqTIEUpPkU-Acztj0axlf327SCV9ck-qU752V5js-I6h6f3subAgsdKq9zxhlSImaeEWpcu56yGLMAJSQH1_2QncIMvi3z-4CsmwXFCFoS6mbRzJvnsCp-ZgIeKfgkxRKohauRvpfqIXezmJqZ0QHgP5bmV_AZyC4YZc/s600/DSC04646.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲相較於前作金光閃閃又超級狂野的水墨風格，這次走的是萌萌路線</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjK0fQvvPacYiGhjIjNfczOOloRawEt-swm-A8tyBXudQTAvVYFZxc-knN6v-jByLGrQP2hHr5GM5Ht-JILkvSDxo7KZR4fwGHplq9qagLGDE7WVRSkWqy2eRg54xXXyEIeXiL3TgH1rQwwkPiOLDb05gP5rPeoLKZuFyNYuU76viUOaHlxyshOasXjtQk/s4048/DSC04647.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjK0fQvvPacYiGhjIjNfczOOloRawEt-swm-A8tyBXudQTAvVYFZxc-knN6v-jByLGrQP2hHr5GM5Ht-JILkvSDxo7KZR4fwGHplq9qagLGDE7WVRSkWqy2eRg54xXXyEIeXiL3TgH1rQwwkPiOLDb05gP5rPeoLKZuFyNYuU76viUOaHlxyshOasXjtQk/s600/DSC04647.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲遊戲人數：2-6人　遊戲時間：15 mins　建議年齡：8+</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjK_jme-tuUFBtrl6XyPQyrLz9dEj4FjZqzbshVEpTS70eUZJbAJFiQtAvalN_JjG6R3dsL5AiQaRTzijlIg2rS1yw8AS4VpG2T09FA2mcokiNQKD3SgX0WnlcLRIpsGS0fLEUDEwmKY8lATw-QUyrObU6NXxjFXYwgxCdsThgdqVyIdgcPimdck_xfUU8/s2972/DSC04648.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjK_jme-tuUFBtrl6XyPQyrLz9dEj4FjZqzbshVEpTS70eUZJbAJFiQtAvalN_JjG6R3dsL5AiQaRTzijlIg2rS1yw8AS4VpG2T09FA2mcokiNQKD3SgX0WnlcLRIpsGS0fLEUDEwmKY8lATw-QUyrObU6NXxjFXYwgxCdsThgdqVyIdgcPimdck_xfUU8/s600/DSC04648.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲盒底的說明圖也很可愛</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhnqOpZsMqeqWV8kZV6pvvqQoFi7-4CWPdBkray0Eku6zJuHGDcBeQE26-lGti-i2wAi-nfQCnxtNRKqqssN4FH9cwbilqEY2HFjqdtC0jIsQ6eKvtzsx2zaMhoGyQZg0Lmtgv-SDKotvjTmICzb7dt37zyZEupnLfEcdcbrr0XNxVEPH4U9OertVuA4B0/s4696/DSC04649.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhnqOpZsMqeqWV8kZV6pvvqQoFi7-4CWPdBkray0Eku6zJuHGDcBeQE26-lGti-i2wAi-nfQCnxtNRKqqssN4FH9cwbilqEY2HFjqdtC0jIsQ6eKvtzsx2zaMhoGyQZg0Lmtgv-SDKotvjTmICzb7dt37zyZEupnLfEcdcbrr0XNxVEPH4U9OertVuA4B0/s600/DSC04649.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲內容物一覽</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEg3sGAkl7_kANxbpibzoeheJFjyT0jUvCQC8670W5hx-YuWn0P7BYZaL1TjbiEpDxOB7qf2_0_1qTS8fyn1E1PkaxRYkc3VQG5MwE0gQ7hIZI7yLjpJc-y59fYE_wGtlf5NUGUi9RZHafUYeHSXR0Z1z4WXkOj3AEAOXWuiAt-KXgzWZ5c2WehP9MwYrCg/s4672/DSC04650.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEg3sGAkl7_kANxbpibzoeheJFjyT0jUvCQC8670W5hx-YuWn0P7BYZaL1TjbiEpDxOB7qf2_0_1qTS8fyn1E1PkaxRYkc3VQG5MwE0gQ7hIZI7yLjpJc-y59fYE_wGtlf5NUGUi9RZHafUYeHSXR0Z1z4WXkOj3AEAOXWuiAt-KXgzWZ5c2WehP9MwYrCg/s600/DSC04650.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲主要的配件就是卡片兩包</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEg6sYMVtdfz8qqmAbR_W8yNtxg1j64UT9E4EegavipOJsKfKYnGPDPUsmpLc3Ug8dS6k5uHDc8ydiPtOi2RZBgYL4_9Q30kL6KL16Hk3IO4RFpp-eSN2jeOakVYczsJPvJsvdOng_ht0FsS9NLKTgrXCi8joY-nzbYytQ6G8rZxknykY5BXpmEiuPLd-Bo/s4972/DSC04651.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEg6sYMVtdfz8qqmAbR_W8yNtxg1j64UT9E4EegavipOJsKfKYnGPDPUsmpLc3Ug8dS6k5uHDc8ydiPtOi2RZBgYL4_9Q30kL6KL16Hk3IO4RFpp-eSN2jeOakVYczsJPvJsvdOng_ht0FsS9NLKTgrXCi8joY-nzbYytQ6G8rZxknykY5BXpmEiuPLd-Bo/s600/DSC04651.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲卡片共有四種，由左而右分別是：酸辣牌、雙料萬用牌、戰利品牌、遊戲結束牌</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEh80zBwlJ6zgtm7UhZbYe17DL_nFCIADCK15GcIfJ81lcHwtF7joNc6Vim8H9k5jm-aDkvJy5yachR1z0AJosgF6T3DqxmI6yd_tz4DoYnOdWXymAFe2pTv29cyH06Jt7054t2BpGg0-33D3ko_UAvgllVlPB3G33iaO1uuncuNgFeoVdAxabcIGEIZA6w/s3684/DSC04652.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEh80zBwlJ6zgtm7UhZbYe17DL_nFCIADCK15GcIfJ81lcHwtF7joNc6Vim8H9k5jm-aDkvJy5yachR1z0AJosgF6T3DqxmI6yd_tz4DoYnOdWXymAFe2pTv29cyH06Jt7054t2BpGg0-33D3ko_UAvgllVlPB3G33iaO1uuncuNgFeoVdAxabcIGEIZA6w/s600/DSC04652.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲其中酸辣牌的組成就是紅藍綠三種顏色的酸辣卡１～１０各３組，兩種特殊卡各５張～</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">底下我們來看看三種顏色的酸辣牌～</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEh7UQC31dLF9zL3OjAXzb5B6rECGv00m4t5cu3AwDIFA9Ys8XxhHfCO-NQHMLa5HzzhJNSbav1nulGRtkjGf7sQvFPlHhfk-4r8DVmUV7n5KHtZASillsUpIZyCFYL1lRRDJu5gF8RInvOesz6a3G5iBxm6u3zMQhs6XO9EXARYx4fQkEBV3OIMU1gJ1Cg/s4356/DSC04653.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEh7UQC31dLF9zL3OjAXzb5B6rECGv00m4t5cu3AwDIFA9Ys8XxhHfCO-NQHMLa5HzzhJNSbav1nulGRtkjGf7sQvFPlHhfk-4r8DVmUV7n5KHtZASillsUpIZyCFYL1lRRDJu5gF8RInvOesz6a3G5iBxm6u3zMQhs6XO9EXARYx4fQkEBV3OIMU1gJ1Cg/s600/DSC04653.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲首先胡椒，由我們可愛的胖胖貓來示範吃胡椒</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEi-_a_Om87z2azyffXE8tJyDoeqLhfx6XazKS931onPSVRyEOjika2WNkjnsPbrov1w78EiZQNIkJHaTgERX2CjM_QWS4DvwgqNnRhsH8t2y6-RZvOhgd08WG4G_QHCKzyvS-dPqtBa_TsOCUV1rKaDpFZkogx-04UYDBGoZ-k0Dr8Z6nCXknkfdx0MOKg/s3936/DSC04654.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEi-_a_Om87z2azyffXE8tJyDoeqLhfx6XazKS931onPSVRyEOjika2WNkjnsPbrov1w78EiZQNIkJHaTgERX2CjM_QWS4DvwgqNnRhsH8t2y6-RZvOhgd08WG4G_QHCKzyvS-dPqtBa_TsOCUV1rKaDpFZkogx-04UYDBGoZ-k0Dr8Z6nCXknkfdx0MOKg/s600/DSC04654.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲接著是檸檬，由黑白貓來表演吃到檸檬的反應～</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEh00GJ_j5cAoxEQ6KX4S4cWb9k6cjC57vAqu0YNyzbbN3fxg8HYSyK56ZYdVVm198iC_qqrfvP_Z0tlvkItIFSjeUOO723bSa5eViDjU1L87IPECdr0sKmXXlVd9ViMdy6KxWlQp_aUeEX3g_73xmJCiHZ2uZEit-RALqaHkaj0_NFwWdXMn3uum-bU2mA/s4340/DSC04655.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEh00GJ_j5cAoxEQ6KX4S4cWb9k6cjC57vAqu0YNyzbbN3fxg8HYSyK56ZYdVVm198iC_qqrfvP_Z0tlvkItIFSjeUOO723bSa5eViDjU1L87IPECdr0sKmXXlVd9ViMdy6KxWlQp_aUeEX3g_73xmJCiHZ2uZEit-RALqaHkaj0_NFwWdXMn3uum-bU2mA/s600/DSC04655.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲最後是主角辣椒，當然也是由最萌的小橘貓來擔當演出，超可愛～</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiDkSp5T9vQjZ8MkhDQm8G5bCKmlWUsoxxyOXPCj1qaVxI0pDLlOWBPa196YDqdKo-Mcm5XQS2SeAXDao2o3XvbNKJ-bYpqMWMJO4vj_mdC2UX78qoLLr131jXo9tR9BN-viOc25KxM2PlfaXdqnrGA_j0Cdl04tyIB7hP7rX83QfO0InP-roEKWGviRNw/s4168/DSC04656.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiDkSp5T9vQjZ8MkhDQm8G5bCKmlWUsoxxyOXPCj1qaVxI0pDLlOWBPa196YDqdKo-Mcm5XQS2SeAXDao2o3XvbNKJ-bYpqMWMJO4vj_mdC2UX78qoLLr131jXo9tR9BN-viOc25KxM2PlfaXdqnrGA_j0Cdl04tyIB7hP7rX83QfO0InP-roEKWGviRNw/s600/DSC04656.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲雙料萬用牌是這次新增的卡片，它同時代表三種食材與十個數字</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEhB6le85ukWsQs_7rOcfbomUdQ3RFj3S8FvwQkvcQH0hxuiZVx-hK1iY_GobVzPlas-oamncFrlgQI8kYt-_tRTgYPF-yC544gtrcM3D-nBO5MUkIKF4bRH5x57AeJlUIH-P13wFC6g6kSwuVzRzmqi4J-eIcMkaTK7HyjQYM4TskMtmv5et5ATwVOs84k\"></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">規則其實就是《貓吃三辣》的規則，所以不教了，不教了～（才怪）</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhiGPhatIrVR9sVhyphenhyphencCnKKIz7SK1Ts8vM-g4JOkyGkPW5XNYpNsAlmany1hspOsSzXeIt36o9HtO2sUAuV9IZYJ_76yka96dCgcAN7jbp4F7gigfCVS2owDDCOdsdDnHFetjJFiSM2sJSCq0Huu48AKiXnkhbRVCYtPrC6Dg3Ih4q8qwamvdGHdtf5laic/s4904/DSC04659.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhiGPhatIrVR9sVhyphenhyphencCnKKIz7SK1Ts8vM-g4JOkyGkPW5XNYpNsAlmany1hspOsSzXeIt36o9HtO2sUAuV9IZYJ_76yka96dCgcAN7jbp4F7gigfCVS2owDDCOdsdDnHFetjJFiSM2sJSCq0Huu48AKiXnkhbRVCYtPrC6Dg3Ih4q8qwamvdGHdtf5laic/s600/DSC04659.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">▲遊戲設置如上，把所有的酸辣牌洗牌之後﹐每個人隨機發５張，雙料萬用牌每人１張，其餘的卡片各自分類之後形成中央牌庫區～</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiQ2x18ggE7i4CiQPVHAEIa2uDziVrrkSZi9pfjJQh0zdRZIP8mY8heWSDMFz1v8ikIgvbbyTL2Fj_cQZCuhSCjQOM0HVDNf0piyvqJuE75ZL9bFjgUyOdP6Ao5-C-KlTkd_q5WVl_94Sfyjal-xwL0DBd3jZHrBvFlgyusTNLxYhb0nQogrjeSoVYUyhU/s5288/DSC04660.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiQ2x18ggE7i4CiQPVHAEIa2uDziVrrkSZi9pfjJQh0zdRZIP8mY8heWSDMFz1v8ikIgvbbyTL2Fj_cQZCuhSCjQOM0HVDNf0piyvqJuE75ZL9bFjgUyOdP6Ao5-C-KlTkd_q5WVl_94Sfyjal-xwL0DBd3jZHrBvFlgyusTNLxYhb0nQogrjeSoVYUyhU/s600/DSC04660.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲遊戲結束牌會像這樣根據遊玩人數量完高度之後，插入酸辣牌的牌堆中。</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEifyuDM338jMqqQL7jSneq3trGa2TlZLUHrNMhs6kkd1Jzur829qSMBBJhx3hNd9aoo6Yhk5EYCIFEt1xgmYtfEM3HPVyJzEWhWlAzz0eVfJOnEn-KAlIu_7oNXl4Q9HCECzKmkA0Nwi5lGBD3jLLJWswxUgbjdSzqoGn0e23z5jlrakRKA2DC5eD0IY20/s3520/DSC04661.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEifyuDM338jMqqQL7jSneq3trGa2TlZLUHrNMhs6kkd1Jzur829qSMBBJhx3hNd9aoo6Yhk5EYCIFEt1xgmYtfEM3HPVyJzEWhWlAzz0eVfJOnEn-KAlIu_7oNXl4Q9HCECzKmkA0Nwi5lGBD3jLLJWswxUgbjdSzqoGn0e23z5jlrakRKA2DC5eD0IY20/s600/DSC04661.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">▲由最年輕的玩家開始出牌，出牌的人必須宣告自己這張牌是什麼食材＋數字，比方說辣椒２。第一個出牌的人數字只能喊１～３，下一個出牌的人必須跟著喊一樣的食材，但是數字一定要更大～但若數字到達１０之後，下一張就只能喊１～３～</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">輪到你的時候，除了跟著上一家出牌並喊出食材數字之外，你也可以選擇跳過並從牌庫抽１張牌～</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">最後，所有玩家在任何時候都可以進行【挑戰】（當然，不能挑戰自己），當你覺得有玩家出的牌跟他口頭所說的不同的時候，你就可以【挑戰】。你必須指出他的錯誤是『食材』或是『數字』，必須抓對才算【挑戰】成功。</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">實例：有一位玩家出牌，並喊出胡椒５，你覺得他出的不是胡椒，因此提出挑戰，並大聲說出：『不是胡椒！』然後翻開他出的卡片～假設他出的是胡椒４，雖然他數字跟自己聲稱的不同，但他出的的確是胡椒，因此算你挑戰失敗～</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">挑戰中的贏家（可能是提出挑戰的人，也可能是最後一個出牌的玩家），將目前場中央所有被打出的牌拿回自己面前，這些都是你的分數～輸家必須從牌庫抽２張牌到手牌，如果手中沒有雙料萬用卡，則必須加抽１張雙料萬用卡～</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEh3QuCECjy8nbLEe9xvKzs4L3433bQGIImkKQexvWdTec-fFLC2qwy87aQBvrYJAGkXfXYAXk9L9752oZB9pti5OtxIP4j7XKqdwSBxILJUi0QBV6krsGDesSsNvBugLYvDjuShbT8YzOqZ7Grt4NvgR83SM6-Y_mIIzhcRrHqosxGrsHqZK7FxuIxAO9Y/s600/DSC04663.JPG\"></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">▲雙料萬用卡是這次的特殊卡片，有專屬規則～簡單說，他就是一張人人都會有的萬用卡～打出它的時候，不管你說什麼都不會被抓～但它不能拿來幫你贏得戰利品，計分的時候，你贏得的每張雙料萬用牌價值５分～但是你手中沒有被用掉的雙料萬用牌會扣５分～是個雙面刃～</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEi5VqGAxj7rveM87naaBtZXwp3PW4xjX52z5lSFkzmbQ9xF3yI756R-MCT4wt2B3UkgZU5DobUHkfVuot8jor3SIbIozVvssRrBET7ooSv7HdEgIu3z46rW_R_vupxB2N-nTGgsf38RnHtwxy4OBl1JW7KC1t43SslJDcFxG6aoM_XnOArfuSSedGoDLe8/s4248/DSC04662.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEi5VqGAxj7rveM87naaBtZXwp3PW4xjX52z5lSFkzmbQ9xF3yI756R-MCT4wt2B3UkgZU5DobUHkfVuot8jor3SIbIozVvssRrBET7ooSv7HdEgIu3z46rW_R_vupxB2N-nTGgsf38RnHtwxy4OBl1JW7KC1t43SslJDcFxG6aoM_XnOArfuSSedGoDLe8/s600/DSC04662.JPG\"></a></p><p>▲如果你打出的是最後一張手牌，你必須大喊『脫手』～這之後如果：</p><p>１．沒人挑戰你！</p><p>２．有人挑戰你，但你獲勝了！</p><p>你就可以獲得一張戰利品牌～遊戲結束時價值１０分～</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiOC20MuK9ER5424Hx_ItudINBjsWIuXOeyQMcHETnIL4QL0E-aGmSVvAnQtwu1gM5GbQXzljbkvpJVUMk7wIZlRVijAtdigZr2E5wWAIU3rL5OrM8eLw9ZGKepE8bPFqLMNqKPH-WY7XzUY5DNXMyU3bLqRBPVsHg6S_-TNTiCqyWws3OuVY5YTeDcTkI/s5100/DSC04664.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiOC20MuK9ER5424Hx_ItudINBjsWIuXOeyQMcHETnIL4QL0E-aGmSVvAnQtwu1gM5GbQXzljbkvpJVUMk7wIZlRVijAtdigZr2E5wWAIU3rL5OrM8eLw9ZGKepE8bPFqLMNqKPH-WY7XzUY5DNXMyU3bLqRBPVsHg6S_-TNTiCqyWws3OuVY5YTeDcTkI/s600/DSC04664.JPG\"></a></p><p>▲遊戲會在下面三種狀況下結束：</p><p>１．當有玩家獲得２張戰利品牌時（該玩家直接獲勝，不用計分）</p><p>２．當戰利品牌被拿光時</p><p>３．當遊戲結束牌出現在牌庫頂時</p><p><br></p><p>計分：</p><p>上述情況１不用計分，其餘狀況：每張戰利品牌１０分，贏得的每張雙料萬用牌５分，贏來的每張酸辣牌１分，手中還沒用掉的雙料萬用牌扣５分，每張沒用掉的酸辣牌扣１分～</p><p><br></p><p><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEg6ACnWEyYvn1s2JybBzPXtC_VTn5GHEgrzzmPs5Zxc3CMQqr2vU53qil6A3LI67kdXVlXjlBYlNtgPvCm2T7N9AV2WcnpwZXHX9lwF1--IVjw7h7Hw3NNxQTdF1T3bHlpLSife85qufLQyxmZR-VMH7HCMiHsuSeEGBeD88llWPUofWcxWcn6-3mlSwMU\"></p><p><br></p><p><strong>可愛ＶＳ獨特</strong></p><p><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">幾年前那篇<a href=\"https://usnoopy.blogspot.com/2020/09/spicy-3.html\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">《貓吃３辣》</a>的文章還蠻熱門的，也有許多人對這款遊戲相當有興趣～加上相當有個性的插圖與很精緻的卡片，一下就吸引了很多注意～而這次的《Sweet &amp; Spicy 貓吃酸辣》很明顯就是來賣萌的，光是從英文標題的Sweet就開宗明義的告訴你，這就是一款超可愛遊戲～至於要怎麼選呢？不用上網找圖了，我都幫你們放好了～</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhbDCbSPeTUBnOBqKdhmKVk4I93ipNC13DRtr7A-i3xVB2NOWWq_8lub_fstfqwHnTF8NUA96hpW6YNURiablTm8958XHBjHxL_Nq0_gvEN9wRrMrkcb3JdjDvsBIpjUG3xeF1GrVAmGD1F_A_rwbh9vAgGdaBsu1pXYsAyis6rYnCsDJbEix53OjdrKiU/w640-h450/qqq.png\"></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲小孩子才做選擇，對吧！？</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">但認真比較的話，兩者的特性也因為彼此的特殊卡片而有所不同～《貓吃３辣》有６張『加辣牌』每次可以搭配隨機１～２張讓遊戲更有變化，所以我會覺得它在遊戲的重度上會稍微高一些些～而這次《Sweet &amp; Spicy 貓吃酸辣》特殊的雙料萬用牌則是讓人又害又恨～留在手中可以在必要的時候救你一把，打出去會讓吃到的人多拿分，留在手中沒有適時地打出去，又會害自己扣分～但不像《貓吃３辣》可以搭配出不同玩法組合，定位上我會覺得這次的新作會更偏家庭遊戲一點，在這一點上跟它的美術也相當吻合～</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgwbNCa7Sj8uXxdafTIJmfYZPO4QzV0M7Z0ClcmwcfUP7uJy2nRSSHKe8z7wBwjAhhmZFyKbz0pSPCn87Si4sYOJV_xMpC_dzX6wMQQIIxgiMyRNF0pzlJK9ZTP5AUjAyHIAi6InLtBKPdZ4_doy3gOgBrH6fWCBPOe1_-gs6EzhOwSECzZKDAkjw7uNkU/s4772/DSC04665.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgwbNCa7Sj8uXxdafTIJmfYZPO4QzV0M7Z0ClcmwcfUP7uJy2nRSSHKe8z7wBwjAhhmZFyKbz0pSPCn87Si4sYOJV_xMpC_dzX6wMQQIIxgiMyRNF0pzlJK9ZTP5AUjAyHIAi6InLtBKPdZ4_doy3gOgBrH6fWCBPOe1_-gs6EzhOwSECzZKDAkjw7uNkU/s600/DSC04665.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲遊戲收納照</p><p><br></p>', '2024-11-18 10:28:12', '2024-11-18 10:28:12', 1, 'forum-1731896892865-3810393.jpg'),
(21, 1, '【桌遊開箱報】The Grand Carnival 盛大的嘉年華 主遊戲+擴充 開箱+介紹', '<h3><br></h3><p><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEjoX-szjztgfycYvvi-grHQ_RdcKnOnukw6eaL9M_hI1XPCQ--0dNdUpwFn4LqqVjqPPxerL61dHtlMgInYaHNFV7dmK4OenMJiwqHZG3u7Znpi9eUxk8NIKIXJuLUgOzRx-re1GEv1FBnddLYekl1PLkkHZJpx2wFleehljEjSNm_wBOURVIDu1WgJUkA\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEjoX-szjztgfycYvvi-grHQ_RdcKnOnukw6eaL9M_hI1XPCQ--0dNdUpwFn4LqqVjqPPxerL61dHtlMgInYaHNFV7dmK4OenMJiwqHZG3u7Znpi9eUxk8NIKIXJuLUgOzRx-re1GEv1FBnddLYekl1PLkkHZJpx2wFleehljEjSNm_wBOURVIDu1WgJUkA=w640-h370\"></a></p><p><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEgZeDgIghkA9z8B4IotNGfZTtT4MpzccsPH9IYcb5d1Fq_Yx_jpG1p0bTqKWIKYByV1DmB4OlI0hptmzsdelqYIno-8aDXcv1MP39exhmnNWz4C-Yb2NwQhdGLookCB_ARjNk7PooJi9VYFjZx1052T3Yc-ej9uzVtjaZY6LH25FCE1MoDW0bcGEdCt=w320-h136\"></p><p><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">《The Grand Carnival 盛大的嘉年華》是香港朋友送我的禮物，真的很感謝他。更早之前的《坦帕妮樂園》也是因為他，才讓接觸到這麼可愛的遊戲，也才有參與製作後來中文版的機會～這次要開箱的不只是主遊戲，還有含最新的擴充，因此會把主要的版面用在擴充的介紹上，我覺得是相當有誠意的一款擴充。話不多說，就開始來介紹吧～</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEi4GQye8Vbp5EQd920T1TJitNjE3vl3HvqJfKUbJfr_aA8zYteOCoU0gNQUskR0kp6Ds0iQug_gdNpbnccv9zkz_qpD0rTZVV5faCCbNHk0C1SgwQ_HiDPpWIkPmhlsCNSRqG-K81vp4eBxF0yoT7hjC5qbHoGrNg1N5ajD2RRsRDTKjs5_mlT8-KzGMc8\"></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiukp1z_BEJG6GG38LbiiTVYSiR7kGff_DYuymlZg_fUMrQgV4Lzd0iQTDBG24_4YdaojM8byshfrniykgaTPpU-I5ZScktmaiEDRNuj5B57QIwpZY_7hDRUTsrEJRRfMvOMfFuqmXokN58y4D4VKeVJb-b9dFX2h6c3-O-JDTVRtKGOzljX0gqRfVBuo0/s4936/DSC04610.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiukp1z_BEJG6GG38LbiiTVYSiR7kGff_DYuymlZg_fUMrQgV4Lzd0iQTDBG24_4YdaojM8byshfrniykgaTPpU-I5ZScktmaiEDRNuj5B57QIwpZY_7hDRUTsrEJRRfMvOMfFuqmXokN58y4D4VKeVJb-b9dFX2h6c3-O-JDTVRtKGOzljX0gqRfVBuo0/s600/DSC04610.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">▲這遊戲很誇張的是，封套都還沒拆開，遊戲盒子就已經被撐成這樣，可以想見這內容物到底有多麼的豐富！</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEj49bNjoUqbfSEcKOWkNrop9vZezEw6xyjhbq7YOEKW2QmjCpU8R6D1q68FwWLU-9bAdbMPvGIbbEqA0Vz4vVkC-HUKZaMkYoiMYLOJR9FSrxfqcx8IQKgFIhwEt8IxxcuvJkr7RUP_oM_rrebxVJZLWzFi28S4EJifnWnQET7thQHMuT5f-12sarJQE-0/s2940/DSC04612.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEj49bNjoUqbfSEcKOWkNrop9vZezEw6xyjhbq7YOEKW2QmjCpU8R6D1q68FwWLU-9bAdbMPvGIbbEqA0Vz4vVkC-HUKZaMkYoiMYLOJR9FSrxfqcx8IQKgFIhwEt8IxxcuvJkr7RUP_oM_rrebxVJZLWzFi28S4EJifnWnQET7thQHMuT5f-12sarJQE-0/s600/DSC04612.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲封面很可愛，算是復古的美式風格～</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjPnNUjWZNI0TA5FihTB0rs4hPFJomfqlhzzY32u-c0MRY6vZz1zuW3NANHXR7bSsMNRvHagUk0mbQkuuIHqaZtsmlE7r4mnKTUe8K6NFiw_PHxnyP7xFC8vKR1Z6Dc3Mj6lnGSfUGgjy1yWFjys-lFqGFTvKBB8LfmTlnTX8U9p8r3hF5zlRrlZ2uiEoA/s3600/DSC04613.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjPnNUjWZNI0TA5FihTB0rs4hPFJomfqlhzzY32u-c0MRY6vZz1zuW3NANHXR7bSsMNRvHagUk0mbQkuuIHqaZtsmlE7r4mnKTUe8K6NFiw_PHxnyP7xFC8vKR1Z6Dc3Mj6lnGSfUGgjy1yWFjys-lFqGFTvKBB8LfmTlnTX8U9p8r3hF5zlRrlZ2uiEoA/s600/DSC04613.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲遊戲人數：1-4人　建議年齡：12+　遊戲時間：45-60 mins</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiqEa7DUv7_5uEl9SkGGnMSLxyMQaTsFkNkBfcPelGPQLcuSjx4_dsATzlLXPSQgSSD2dtFrepS_2fHoxjDXLRDrgHGvYkkyUUjQJKepEvf8mVLfu3ol8paWNfscHQOD7fTKz5qWSxCg4CwDijar_I6nF4eBI_Ayrs7COsUVZAAot6OS-elCVD3SuJi5b0/s3220/DSC04614.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiqEa7DUv7_5uEl9SkGGnMSLxyMQaTsFkNkBfcPelGPQLcuSjx4_dsATzlLXPSQgSSD2dtFrepS_2fHoxjDXLRDrgHGvYkkyUUjQJKepEvf8mVLfu3ol8paWNfscHQOD7fTKz5qWSxCg4CwDijar_I6nF4eBI_Ayrs7COsUVZAAot6OS-elCVD3SuJi5b0/s600/DSC04614.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲底部超簡潔～但缺點就是看不到遊戲的樣貌～</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgfaMKSNx0ityPwGjCy4KymJz-EQUuwpIBvh_boiGLqNSggtsMNGg8OgMUj4XK7qFJO_aN5fG2wAy5Z90-YsvF7PtNyuLv-w7JS-PMv7GRDHfukLH6-MMZyfoq9ZXeryLI1992mv8C3cbHTkwh26BKV3g8a5Uog7OKTkfQ2dTYTC7eAXEF2waCAk8E8X2U/s3440/DSC04615.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgfaMKSNx0ityPwGjCy4KymJz-EQUuwpIBvh_boiGLqNSggtsMNGg8OgMUj4XK7qFJO_aN5fG2wAy5Z90-YsvF7PtNyuLv-w7JS-PMv7GRDHfukLH6-MMZyfoq9ZXeryLI1992mv8C3cbHTkwh26BKV3g8a5Uog7OKTkfQ2dTYTC7eAXEF2waCAk8E8X2U/s600/DSC04615.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲內容物一覽</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjG55baTD24okqOstwthywxPht97JZWp4rDAtp7f6v_g3kOJaEMsQ_nVt1JquIrfXYLZCr_FgUJ5MH11-pMv3K7YwFPGf449p7NT_tIDatLQuQjZspv1pPv5naSOu83GVclk6Di1U0D4Y4Cj2M6I6Fh-Z4lLxWu-gf9VM6qEp9AHH218qBifJP8dk0_okg/s5024/DSC04616.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjG55baTD24okqOstwthywxPht97JZWp4rDAtp7f6v_g3kOJaEMsQ_nVt1JquIrfXYLZCr_FgUJ5MH11-pMv3K7YwFPGf449p7NT_tIDatLQuQjZspv1pPv5naSOu83GVclk6Di1U0D4Y4Cj2M6I6Fh-Z4lLxWu-gf9VM6qEp9AHH218qBifJP8dk0_okg/s600/DSC04616.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲由於是板塊遊戲，所以戳戳樂超多！</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiVT38gl2HAhuUefDNm_xp1CuyzHtzvwKwyxbBogbqDovZiRNykLt-y4_bImADuE2Urvrb0dwIjANseyJV-1inkYJeihMg_Hcd0un-FUZ4bG0swevgdca5AKkEdykBhCODHhO9V0GlvP2K_xV9n3SdzvqcRIrAXqRb4Y1xZq5w9W6iK2d_CgkWrP87ULvQ/s4976/DSC04617.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiVT38gl2HAhuUefDNm_xp1CuyzHtzvwKwyxbBogbqDovZiRNykLt-y4_bImADuE2Urvrb0dwIjANseyJV-1inkYJeihMg_Hcd0un-FUZ4bG0swevgdca5AKkEdykBhCODHhO9V0GlvP2K_xV9n3SdzvqcRIrAXqRb4Y1xZq5w9W6iK2d_CgkWrP87ULvQ/s600/DSC04617.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲遊戲內有附超棒的收納！</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjKXRTkiUwkc3K3nrgTaNhZlclK4VkMkHDLe2NZIVMC6ot3jkVxtcI4E08dbDI_nFZvrFphA0SE7gDV_DsW7sGp5yygPUvbmVSkga9tg8Wn4PXtQbZJJt9mgA6ry1uBLWnzsWZE_GEZTaTTQhLE0VrIoHdUfyho6KRClcYtjXblpN1UEIaZhGub5xFXRTY/s5472/DSC04618.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjKXRTkiUwkc3K3nrgTaNhZlclK4VkMkHDLe2NZIVMC6ot3jkVxtcI4E08dbDI_nFZvrFphA0SE7gDV_DsW7sGp5yygPUvbmVSkga9tg8Wn4PXtQbZJJt9mgA6ry1uBLWnzsWZE_GEZTaTTQhLE0VrIoHdUfyho6KRClcYtjXblpN1UEIaZhGub5xFXRTY/s600/DSC04618.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲這邊讓大家看看板塊的美術，真的很有嘉年華的感受～</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjZdlGl3MXfsrYDm1QsNXFhjnUcV9c413IFoTkb2OKI00kr4CUDEwGPU9sSWE9lsAqFEVOE316iEEY2fapDWzSfCMSxgKJ_DbobGjJDDuTTulJadciXmQ0A2f1s9slK4VJ9ReCabb-PqSLGWki3R0orB_z19wLbzHIY2kJfqs_GxVXdZGb6ISpaCNasV7A/s3088/DSC04619.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjZdlGl3MXfsrYDm1QsNXFhjnUcV9c413IFoTkb2OKI00kr4CUDEwGPU9sSWE9lsAqFEVOE316iEEY2fapDWzSfCMSxgKJ_DbobGjJDDuTTulJadciXmQ0A2f1s9slK4VJ9ReCabb-PqSLGWki3R0orB_z19wLbzHIY2kJfqs_GxVXdZGb6ISpaCNasV7A/s600/DSC04619.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲各種米寶都好可愛</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhRqec8KwqUXyeieWf7Py77r_mCeiNNN-ShKfVn8zRLIg3qkiSWzlerFQaGfCatXIrnWRdZso6FBcw49odj2OrZrqZr8ad15W-gVVykgEZSlnwCgrMtxwqa-HbG7LD4iGg4LeHw5-PrknddocJePGBXzwQjvBC81sTHGRPW59-Sr6Hjc_KljAjH7gfQDkQ/s4548/DSC04620.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhRqec8KwqUXyeieWf7Py77r_mCeiNNN-ShKfVn8zRLIg3qkiSWzlerFQaGfCatXIrnWRdZso6FBcw49odj2OrZrqZr8ad15W-gVVykgEZSlnwCgrMtxwqa-HbG7LD4iGg4LeHw5-PrknddocJePGBXzwQjvBC81sTHGRPW59-Sr6Hjc_KljAjH7gfQDkQ/s600/DSC04620.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲便當盒（咳～），是整理好之後的收納盤～</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhWXQuJTtJrhw9r8pyy3Pm9w6aJQnASm1ElrCpSGy22kC4lfL6si_YvV3G-FDpvZ1BEvOgqgL3H4J1wzCENIaRJlF4dfnvKnIXe4UGyqHIwWmeUWm6Mkr4kp-5BAs2BT-_ddfnGnQLzs_GGowYI6ZCeyGEHQJH6LSaAZyjX6PI_FhUqKuljCBQI-Fp3NfY/s4464/DSC04621.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhWXQuJTtJrhw9r8pyy3Pm9w6aJQnASm1ElrCpSGy22kC4lfL6si_YvV3G-FDpvZ1BEvOgqgL3H4J1wzCENIaRJlF4dfnvKnIXe4UGyqHIwWmeUWm6Mkr4kp-5BAs2BT-_ddfnGnQLzs_GGowYI6ZCeyGEHQJH6LSaAZyjX6PI_FhUqKuljCBQI-Fp3NfY/s600/DSC04621.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲四張很大張的個人圖板</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgIVQANLkkVoAjP0jz7CJEyOndQMWDlNyLC4EOGtRwSGWUJygcxjPvAIOyuaXc7G1noo5xjslD5shMCZYq_Dn7Ylqw-Uqgs_g0PC-NsS3a8WzMMzzki34q4GtnI7jCK6aTSwLMEQDMUanD4Qg0et2WcVaPgd5-H1LGjB0KWgZHrlBh8ji7hakaomPbDy2g/s4188/DSC04622.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgIVQANLkkVoAjP0jz7CJEyOndQMWDlNyLC4EOGtRwSGWUJygcxjPvAIOyuaXc7G1noo5xjslD5shMCZYq_Dn7Ylqw-Uqgs_g0PC-NsS3a8WzMMzzki34q4GtnI7jCK6aTSwLMEQDMUanD4Qg0et2WcVaPgd5-H1LGjB0KWgZHrlBh8ji7hakaomPbDy2g/s600/DSC04622.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲打開之後不只顏色，連美術都有不同</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjcRP4SoxFzNuXv-Y1lVlMxP7V6DUWLtUs3NmL0SzUnbDvz5sZTlVyBVqSpMsJSh-OX5QCWh0xRc6oEvowe73gb3cinoQ0LfzPtMsOiRMLlw0H2o565OVELBi5IG4PEK25YQp5a7A1P-LWPC_rWaR9m6MIoen0n-Gn4x1kYZ0Wnvb-7rggrQ5DOtmgjoXk/s4828/DSC04623.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjcRP4SoxFzNuXv-Y1lVlMxP7V6DUWLtUs3NmL0SzUnbDvz5sZTlVyBVqSpMsJSh-OX5QCWh0xRc6oEvowe73gb3cinoQ0LfzPtMsOiRMLlw0H2o565OVELBi5IG4PEK25YQp5a7A1P-LWPC_rWaR9m6MIoen0n-Gn4x1kYZ0Wnvb-7rggrQ5DOtmgjoXk/s600/DSC04623.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲一張鐵路圖板</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiMnArLSSYHT7D19jM6MYYlSpuxAgt-TlUzGca34nrFP0EyseytToFozpNcY7viUy5igmAePElo0tXs00iOPtY2RFSE227D5hPpMnI5tpCuxSMF5Ec-9oQyHDWGCbi-XqEorOirC8Gay3oJyk7b1CKPhHVKLmKhLdtGzP_YQAK4a-itMfPmcX47CmkWNMA/s3180/DSC04624.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiMnArLSSYHT7D19jM6MYYlSpuxAgt-TlUzGca34nrFP0EyseytToFozpNcY7viUy5igmAePElo0tXs00iOPtY2RFSE227D5hPpMnI5tpCuxSMF5Ec-9oQyHDWGCbi-XqEorOirC8Gay3oJyk7b1CKPhHVKLmKhLdtGzP_YQAK4a-itMfPmcX47CmkWNMA/s600/DSC04624.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲卡片一包</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEib3Oys30uyVSZmi01gZj73UrfrdVJuHtqPM7GP10K9TAyaKkw-cpGLDL0TnbuwPf7K7DLwpmn9rtY2wnHLktPZci5BDHtPLhn4a55OiK1MpeMhei7VOQTmUDP_LXF4O1Y_cdacWv9s3C7li2HciD0NI79tipsByU0H01hLwY1lz5j1PwJRHr4DrmzR5kw/s4764/DSC04625.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEib3Oys30uyVSZmi01gZj73UrfrdVJuHtqPM7GP10K9TAyaKkw-cpGLDL0TnbuwPf7K7DLwpmn9rtY2wnHLktPZci5BDHtPLhn4a55OiK1MpeMhei7VOQTmUDP_LXF4O1Y_cdacWv9s3C7li2HciD0NI79tipsByU0H01hLwY1lz5j1PwJRHr4DrmzR5kw/s600/DSC04625.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲這些是特權卡，也就是公共目標，遊戲當中有達成的話，可以獲得特殊能力</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEi4GQye8Vbp5EQd920T1TJitNjE3vl3HvqJfKUbJfr_aA8zYteOCoU0gNQUskR0kp6Ds0iQug_gdNpbnccv9zkz_qpD0rTZVV5faCCbNHk0C1SgwQ_HiDPpWIkPmhlsCNSRqG-K81vp4eBxF0yoT7hjC5qbHoGrNg1N5ajD2RRsRDTKjs5_mlT8-KzGMc8\"></p><p>接著我們來看擴充的開箱：</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiAaLh0B6e70rYovfBC2D9Cq3_TylfV7iIk5felo3W9GzZFizVLBBIU7AugU6lYq-AqYJ1H0yN0FqSfEdjrIvBbGOnsbd2vkHemGWWjnImpnsWLeZZEZ4ipUm07_yZaaeR0K870CnROp2HNyE1RfeiapahVyCvmA9hXh9Tgo1gNjuG4QV3hykBV2-V8W-I/s3776/DSC04626.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiAaLh0B6e70rYovfBC2D9Cq3_TylfV7iIk5felo3W9GzZFizVLBBIU7AugU6lYq-AqYJ1H0yN0FqSfEdjrIvBbGOnsbd2vkHemGWWjnImpnsWLeZZEZ4ipUm07_yZaaeR0K870CnROp2HNyE1RfeiapahVyCvmA9hXh9Tgo1gNjuG4QV3hykBV2-V8W-I/s600/DSC04626.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲首先是封面，對映著副標題【On the road】，美術真的很有巡迴感～</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">（而且有恐龍！有恐龍！）</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhKFYDDDdbkrqoZlAFUPmbh7ocoS_CCG59QChg2dqqx1LyKCL3GA1ufWaCAtXaUAE8awa1Te3nA5sOb2W46xt1udMg5GFjqhcDb4m4XcOW0I6-G9y_Kqz6kf-JXRdulQtvkqMX2vstVPvczjM6BfXoil76on3w8n9z86mMBqVPNTpr0wv_B-qNvgJ9AduM/s4576/DSC04627.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhKFYDDDdbkrqoZlAFUPmbh7ocoS_CCG59QChg2dqqx1LyKCL3GA1ufWaCAtXaUAE8awa1Te3nA5sOb2W46xt1udMg5GFjqhcDb4m4XcOW0I6-G9y_Kqz6kf-JXRdulQtvkqMX2vstVPvczjM6BfXoil76on3w8n9z86mMBqVPNTpr0wv_B-qNvgJ9AduM/s600/DSC04627.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲盒子薄薄一個</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiqYeMnXP8YfKK_1rQJh4gxQgZXyb6tXWn5jN02pf_VOVRrDILBESo1f3wJtm5YGqzDdE0GaFFk2-YRviB1O_RZWXQnfs4XuTQgUyZk77s14z3raLzEkbewC1aLaxKW5oWwJZUyxnfmfyJK-RmCIe8S8k5IUTGrPUe_rwGo4yRPFu-QyprAx6PVkHb_FwI/s4176/DSC04628.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiqYeMnXP8YfKK_1rQJh4gxQgZXyb6tXWn5jN02pf_VOVRrDILBESo1f3wJtm5YGqzDdE0GaFFk2-YRviB1O_RZWXQnfs4XuTQgUyZk77s14z3raLzEkbewC1aLaxKW5oWwJZUyxnfmfyJK-RmCIe8S8k5IUTGrPUe_rwGo4yRPFu-QyprAx6PVkHb_FwI/s600/DSC04628.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲盒底依然是這種清淡風格，光看圖片，玩家完全看不出有什麼內容，真的很吃虧～</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhHMA3RDBx5FxIIv-k7s4TEwdTjxhAI8H2ZwNcEjXbAyKEnHGM8KMCjwLg9IWjQCW2YGey01S6-CqYViYVAoWG2A6w1r6tct6Bo7Y9qMTBKfYTWP7DYl5JuUCsozSxw2zCjrTT4zNkzGjfj7k4BWLAQxF1t92RbaRBOGIhIqxU6rLKtleMC_M21341t2X4/s5108/DSC04629.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhHMA3RDBx5FxIIv-k7s4TEwdTjxhAI8H2ZwNcEjXbAyKEnHGM8KMCjwLg9IWjQCW2YGey01S6-CqYViYVAoWG2A6w1r6tct6Bo7Y9qMTBKfYTWP7DYl5JuUCsozSxw2zCjrTT4zNkzGjfj7k4BWLAQxF1t92RbaRBOGIhIqxU6rLKtleMC_M21341t2X4/s600/DSC04629.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲內容物一覽，裡面其實是好多個擴充的模組，接著我們一個一個來介紹</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhoAtT_JGhSJpIh3ZqVoPQ7et-hvf2kcqHhbNCsbqyzROw6OaQH_ISr_hIOjxZNqT2CFPK5VBE-Pi-V8h6-uQwvxFQF68T_OXBg2tUtyzzfzQogW_oiMiTIjda2mxidPs_piJRhBlVBtDvGnwiDriTvK1Zov2mGQK0Kewwi6NNMoRwJdz0LedquQJC5QD4/s4740/DSC04636.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhoAtT_JGhSJpIh3ZqVoPQ7et-hvf2kcqHhbNCsbqyzROw6OaQH_ISr_hIOjxZNqT2CFPK5VBE-Pi-V8h6-uQwvxFQF68T_OXBg2tUtyzzfzQogW_oiMiTIjda2mxidPs_piJRhBlVBtDvGnwiDriTvK1Zov2mGQK0Kewwi6NNMoRwJdz0LedquQJC5QD4/s600/DSC04636.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">▲模組一，小丑：共有２０隻小丑米寶，當玩家建設嘉年華設施時，可以額外支付行動點數來得到小丑（比方說使用行動點５來建設３格的設施，就可以拿到２隻小丑）。將小丑放到該設施中的格子，每個設施可以容納的小丑數量上限＝格子數。小丑不會影響你的門票收入，遊戲結束時，小丑旁邊每有１個遊客就可以得２分（每個遊客只能讓１個小丑得分）～</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEii_8wa6nZhCjshPtz9Gyk8xYLGzT14W8fVmX0fyUD_QlkwP65YecCJU6nAECsg4AXB1fly63Y0-omi2dFXIxDbYq7sbdOSva56S0n6EAOsNDW5EzN_VN0mXbuChr5X-RpJLrcnYaUY7B3yoUMjC0gebRc486YKI0V4Vi-cBSBrkvrhQJZ-ULn8vRGVEPM/s600/DSC04632.JPG\"></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">▲模組二，雙倍地基：有５片雙倍地基板塊，遊戲設置時，會隨機發給每位玩家１片。大家就各自把這片雙倍地基放到自己的嘉年華中。由於雙倍地基上面的槌子有畫３６０度旋轉，所以這片板塊可以轉成任意方向放置。</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhpMZPEL9IoToa3PVjIlCVvV9n-ULTFhpaE69j5axVrXDCXhvCHJLlRSW4yi33YvskNeXMglUwpq5nzwj823Rz2rZT2f3U2-tIUPITWgBkk9CWrj9xECgVaTuYud5iEozT50L5odMES5XK-P9Lz2iwoRbC-qiiq8HlLRsbJbTumFyQJGKda2u8aEow7BRg/s600/DSC04635.JPG\"></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">▲模組三，花生：共有２０個花生指示物。每當有客人移動後停留在餐車（尺寸１的設施）旁，就可以得到１個花生。之後花生可以用來增加你的行動能力，比方說你可以踩在行動１的格子中，並花費２個花生來執行行動３的行動。每次使用的花生數量沒有限制。</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">模組四，黃金票：共有４０個黃金票指示物。每當你的客人移動之後同時停留在攬客員與設施旁時，可以將１張黃金票放到設施中～黃金票與普通票在其他規則上沒有不同，但遊戲結束時，每張黃金票價值２分。</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgVKpW0NMTNm4VD2EWIltMG5x9AM3n6v_irF6I3cAeXeNBKsWoJHiaznuj7Xo6eLrJqS_b3Z7ATBHQ34CDX_Roi8aFm-JLXpKkCCYwCgQ790RVaHGiEurHxFzfIK1SxLB4nB4jDdo5HIpCE1FETXmUXtYaM__ZSWh0YFRnPJhCY-vP6kbpWcBTDocL2ZA0/s4476/DSC04631.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgVKpW0NMTNm4VD2EWIltMG5x9AM3n6v_irF6I3cAeXeNBKsWoJHiaznuj7Xo6eLrJqS_b3Z7ATBHQ34CDX_Roi8aFm-JLXpKkCCYwCgQ790RVaHGiEurHxFzfIK1SxLB4nB4jDdo5HIpCE1FETXmUXtYaM__ZSWh0YFRnPJhCY-vP6kbpWcBTDocL2ZA0/s600/DSC04631.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">▲模組五，六格設施：遊戲設置時，隨機使用人數＋１的六格設施。想要建造六格設施，就一定要加入【花生模組】，才能夠讓自己的行動力增加到６點。遊戲結束時，擁有５種不同尺寸的設施一樣可以得２２分，但六種不同尺寸的設施不另外加分～此外，當算某種設施是否有３棟時，六格設施可以當作任意格數的建築來用～</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhDOKZEL0cy6U3N95SmRm84dfT6nqmaEN3DK5E648mNMXsEIgvWXtNmqLXE8mwmhS6aC8CqeqDG4fqvOQbWf6urMKEv_SBnEq9MymnLaDYp7PbyZ1Rljhffxl4sL-zbBhmKItit4HnYNqgfY7CgrdsTJULumnNEwYiHdDTH_3tVhui7VFMYwK09Tv4Vjak/s600/DSC04638.JPG\"></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">▲模組六，加分卡：共１３張加分卡～每次會隨機開出等同玩家人數的加分卡（但有些是特定模組專用可以先挑掉）。當你的回合結束時，如果有符合某張加分卡，就可以獲得該卡，遊戲結束時價值８分，但每位玩家最多只能獲得１張加分卡～</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgXful0dOX5czD0DYMRxKmSlPEn6VBsXN1vVcQFeSgw0CshA84nFc2F4uMVEHfpn-V0HJpzFQiPkSvjIKqRVS-FDRjtPLYAHYMZJtIllihXRRxRU8st5Nbarxlz7FK6in1qyPGRCyWI-7imfhp9myJvcWwXxbFyDhHQzSyJ6Yg9GVFSsrLE7dR4bNa5ENs/s4872/DSC04634.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgXful0dOX5czD0DYMRxKmSlPEn6VBsXN1vVcQFeSgw0CshA84nFc2F4uMVEHfpn-V0HJpzFQiPkSvjIKqRVS-FDRjtPLYAHYMZJtIllihXRRxRU8st5Nbarxlz7FK6in1qyPGRCyWI-7imfhp9myJvcWwXxbFyDhHQzSyJ6Yg9GVFSsrLE7dR4bNa5ENs/s600/DSC04634.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">▲模組七，小地基板塊：１２張雙面的小板塊（一面是槌子，一面是草地），當你使用行動力５去蓋地基時，除了可以任意選擇一片地基之外，同時也能獲得１張小地基板塊～這張小地基板塊不用馬上使用，之後可以隨意蓋在你任何一片地基上，讓你更容易建造出設施，或是道路～（這模組感覺超好用）</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjpRPqweAWcHAiI74VllrUWwNfbX9Vs1JHyegN7as9iprGq8iJ-hHOPOtvEgNhsorNvs99J3Y6Mjhktw3TcQRUSp-uAcO57oAXauue08zYXkZIBFD4eHabNGHJE9-VwQaGUA1_vIS1_7SAQQoMLHA8CczLJiW3aMS69lMO3rTFFRYjxooCTPhUrWgXNWc8/s3736/DSC04639.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjpRPqweAWcHAiI74VllrUWwNfbX9Vs1JHyegN7as9iprGq8iJ-hHOPOtvEgNhsorNvs99J3Y6Mjhktw3TcQRUSp-uAcO57oAXauue08zYXkZIBFD4eHabNGHJE9-VwQaGUA1_vIS1_7SAQQoMLHA8CczLJiW3aMS69lMO3rTFFRYjxooCTPhUrWgXNWc8/s600/DSC04639.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">▲模組八，更多特權卡：擴充新增了針對各種模組的特權卡～讓遊戲有更多的變化～</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjH7lqyOMveCsRQozk8f4n9F2TMmB7qxczk_42O6xncGoSV9qx_FxmjmOl5ja8LZAFv3SbUm-qrQE6va-Ohu2yscREtg4yBuCM_FCj4In9hyphenhyphen2Es5e0IBrLTSLZsZqn_cLIXXtMTEznxglDoGFvqdKsdrwXXyfnBttyMJ5Khb19619VAqzRmYWKkDWZJj1Q/s5472/DSC04637.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjH7lqyOMveCsRQozk8f4n9F2TMmB7qxczk_42O6xncGoSV9qx_FxmjmOl5ja8LZAFv3SbUm-qrQE6va-Ohu2yscREtg4yBuCM_FCj4In9hyphenhyphen2Es5e0IBrLTSLZsZqn_cLIXXtMTEznxglDoGFvqdKsdrwXXyfnBttyMJ5Khb19619VAqzRmYWKkDWZJj1Q/s600/DSC04637.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲以上提到的八個模組新增小配件，都可以收在收納盤中，所以一切都幫你規劃好惹～</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">你以為擴充就只有這八個模組嗎？錯！下面這件事設計師做得更用力！</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjo3gllHp8A1n4waAhLCKQXrW4aiqGVCij1EO89eayUjhuL2TKQqx7uQKwjm_Gd7sgtZnqcJMwZB2PEYI7671LubwUq4dz1I1Qqxn05jusnLoi2C1g1EHkEEgxVrBJy7BuRxenjY9WpQoufs6cFWO-5UnNKQihWyCUM1unk8oJ9Vg_C4bPJP-IWMCifPD4/s4896/DSC04640.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjo3gllHp8A1n4waAhLCKQXrW4aiqGVCij1EO89eayUjhuL2TKQqx7uQKwjm_Gd7sgtZnqcJMwZB2PEYI7671LubwUq4dz1I1Qqxn05jusnLoi2C1g1EHkEEgxVrBJy7BuRxenjY9WpQoufs6cFWO-5UnNKQihWyCUM1unk8oJ9Vg_C4bPJP-IWMCifPD4/s600/DSC04640.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲還記得擴充的副標題嗎？【On the road】，於是，設計師真的要帶我們巡迴演出啦！</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiPSSSaPF7Hglg9YAQ4qQUXqKBR9ojnjLMlDRvt-yNt81IdCas-AMXVbHgz_4WFvpTQC71_JCkoEHLKyjVUQNrpbn2DGnr6kCi6335PQU6lUfrAllYfr-JstEx17zFDeUzVvcRdwa8mL36Nvs-oUf2t0AuRIlVcbyiiPDKnBmTvPUkNRXO-iCocEi0BKyE/s3440/DSC04641.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiPSSSaPF7Hglg9YAQ4qQUXqKBR9ojnjLMlDRvt-yNt81IdCas-AMXVbHgz_4WFvpTQC71_JCkoEHLKyjVUQNrpbn2DGnr6kCi6335PQU6lUfrAllYfr-JstEx17zFDeUzVvcRdwa8mL36Nvs-oUf2t0AuRIlVcbyiiPDKnBmTvPUkNRXO-iCocEi0BKyE/s600/DSC04641.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">▲我們一共會經過１０個城市，從塔爾薩（Tulas）到德梅因（des moines iowa），每個城市會加入不同的模組，不同的計分方式，讓玩家們更深入體會這款遊戲！最讓人感動的是！！！美個城市的玩家幫助卡的牌背，都做成各地嘉年華門票的樣子！！！這美術真的是感動到爆炸！！！</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEimQGaQ9XeB8ZYeHEdR6kT1fs39zFg784Z_oQFBs6K8Jn-N5S5qW3BlGRzYNbfOnQct-th4IsyPY8qKYZ2j6j9cLlrB1WiZQ6kw-YwOhp4wwzhQfGhVSN9p6oPxgl0VDfWcTl-YsHySjDqNNnEc3sSSqOd5oFBfIncBokOkAEnY8AzBBQB8KyTtBwFMyoQ/s4948/DSC04642.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEimQGaQ9XeB8ZYeHEdR6kT1fs39zFg784Z_oQFBs6K8Jn-N5S5qW3BlGRzYNbfOnQct-th4IsyPY8qKYZ2j6j9cLlrB1WiZQ6kw-YwOhp4wwzhQfGhVSN9p6oPxgl0VDfWcTl-YsHySjDqNNnEc3sSSqOd5oFBfIncBokOkAEnY8AzBBQB8KyTtBwFMyoQ/s600/DSC04642.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲最後不得不說遊戲的收納真的很用心～</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgkyp-MvqaYoNBx-O0gzDT0uaRci5iTPtDLTRR-kO_kZ7WGuNWrfIwH5niH7RQud5yHL92B-M2hArpy-HgHTYFdreKgqpcCgYO7RBB1ksrn7e0_OzrjGRZJJHlZ0W-5cUv2vD94GSNKp4x6Ec4iCanOih3vPLFl46a32LNABBzM5feJ3dnskBzB0EvlLm4/s4584/DSC04643.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgkyp-MvqaYoNBx-O0gzDT0uaRci5iTPtDLTRR-kO_kZ7WGuNWrfIwH5niH7RQud5yHL92B-M2hArpy-HgHTYFdreKgqpcCgYO7RBB1ksrn7e0_OzrjGRZJJHlZ0W-5cUv2vD94GSNKp4x6Ec4iCanOih3vPLFl46a32LNABBzM5feJ3dnskBzB0EvlLm4/s600/DSC04643.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲板塊都有剛剛好的位置可以放</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEh1nqT10LOU_5sBS66HuBs4Yh1LKtKufI9nsUrfPzyCVnXuJNSyyJJHcBHKnMi4Y2wM_THoIUagB-WXzTm5eWYxBm0maii5sUsFdN-KTzFf4HfPm1KzM0BXszh55OzqGHzEy8WMdzh8r6o21N4DktiSekB6djm3cI_qz22GwVr6lrG8auJy_QHtUdLNWf8/s4256/DSC04645.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEh1nqT10LOU_5sBS66HuBs4Yh1LKtKufI9nsUrfPzyCVnXuJNSyyJJHcBHKnMi4Y2wM_THoIUagB-WXzTm5eWYxBm0maii5sUsFdN-KTzFf4HfPm1KzM0BXszh55OzqGHzEy8WMdzh8r6o21N4DktiSekB6djm3cI_qz22GwVr6lrG8auJy_QHtUdLNWf8/s600/DSC04645.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲全部收好之後放上便當盒＋個人圖板～完美！</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEjyONKw_n9uY_YyHgdaoFdHMu-qENL9w6Vjtgom7KU6z7ngUI4Pa4wiDYz2EjLfgChHmCyel9xPCwrxfS5mmUmydM23uXYZZ4JAfrg-E4howDQgDnvxMlQQriG4fIvh3lbGwQwl3E7CVCxYNcAOKHDSjaQIs6LKj5ZZ54BrIBexJnGAgXEvXI_9w3Vx4Hg\"></p><p><strong>我給９０分！</strong></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">這篇文章由於篇幅的關係，我就不著墨在主遊戲的規則了，有興趣的朋友推薦可以看<a href=\"https://boardgame-record.blogspot.com/2022/01/the-grand-carnival.html\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">小柴這篇超詳細的文章</a>。至於擴充的規則我也有把所有模組的規則都寫在上面了，讓大家可以查詢參考～所以我們就直接進心得的部分吧～</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">長期有看我文章的朋友應該會知道，遊樂園＋板拼我真的很難抗拒～《盛大的嘉年華》這款遊戲在先天上就已經踩住我的點，再加上用數字來行動這個機制真的很對味，也因此這款遊戲玩起來我算是相當的喜歡。雖然美術風格沒有到超愛，但配合這個主題也還算加分！</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">擴充的部分更是讓我驚豔，原本以為小小一盒應該還好，但裡面除了提供八個可以任意組合遊玩的模組之外，居然還提供了巡迴規則！真的是讓大家玩好玩滿～這次配合擴充出的新版，也在收納的部份下足了功夫，整體收納起來相當舒服～美術超級用心，尤其是那十種巡迴卡片真的必須一提再提～我完全被感動到～</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">會給９０分是因為也不是完全沒有缺點。主遊戲的部分，由於板塊都不能隨意翻轉，所以建造起來的自由度不高，大家剛開始玩都會覺得很苦～好不容易打起來的地基，結果那個形狀的設施只有一個，被蓋掉之後好幾家慘叫。得分的方式也讓大家的路線很相似，比方說屋頂的遊客得分最高就是４位遊客，再多就沒有了～由於門檻沒有很高，結束的時候大家幾乎都有達成，變成一個有點雞肋的得分方式～這點在加入擴充的加分卡之後會比較改善，大家可以往不同的路線去發展～</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">另外還有一個缺點出在看起來很完美的收納，雖然板塊跟米寶做了有蓋子的收納盒，但是其實直放還是會有點散開，底部的地基板塊也是～但頂多算是小亂，不會到很可怕，我還是很感激官方提供了收納，不敢想像沒有收納會有多麻煩～</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">以上便是這次的介紹，希望有讓大家多認識這款遊戲～</p><p><br></p>', '2024-11-18 10:28:59', '2024-11-18 10:28:59', 1, 'forum-1731896939335-945278285.jpg');
INSERT INTO `forum_posts` (`id`, `user_id`, `title`, `content`, `created_at`, `updated_at`, `status`, `cover_image`) VALUES
(22, 1, '【桌遊開箱報】Mino Dice 米諾骰 開箱+介紹', '<h3><br></h3><p><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjIP3GW5LDV6BGnv3US4ETcEfGAVJMqVSYQqF7Vqll9DZv3DteaE7mYdeBMa9wXe0sJkhwazyvf1kyD6TR5V6A2txTWKIWMVtSzcDmkXZUVTLBtwhZmLP-3vwK37mop06GhqvBbKue2jUmhVu939lX10HuQaxfga8pK6R3-Zag2jewzw1DQwJ46_Lkqyfk/s2128/DSC04702.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjIP3GW5LDV6BGnv3US4ETcEfGAVJMqVSYQqF7Vqll9DZv3DteaE7mYdeBMa9wXe0sJkhwazyvf1kyD6TR5V6A2txTWKIWMVtSzcDmkXZUVTLBtwhZmLP-3vwK37mop06GhqvBbKue2jUmhVu939lX10HuQaxfga8pK6R3-Zag2jewzw1DQwJ46_Lkqyfk/s600/DSC04702.JPG\"></a></p><p><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEgZeDgIghkA9z8B4IotNGfZTtT4MpzccsPH9IYcb5d1Fq_Yx_jpG1p0bTqKWIKYByV1DmB4OlI0hptmzsdelqYIno-8aDXcv1MP39exhmnNWz4C-Yb2NwQhdGLookCB_ARjNk7PooJi9VYFjZx1052T3Yc-ej9uzVtjaZY6LH25FCE1MoDW0bcGEdCt=w320-h136\"></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">吃墩遊戲有玩過，派對遊戲有玩過，但如果兩種類型摻在一起做成撒尿牛丸，有玩過嗎！？米諾陶洛斯在迷宮中閒得發慌，玩起了骰子，因此誕生出了這款派對型的吃墩遊戲《Mino Dice 米諾骰》！想不出這兩種組合會迸出什麼新滋味？那就來看看這次的文章介紹吧～</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEi4GQye8Vbp5EQd920T1TJitNjE3vl3HvqJfKUbJfr_aA8zYteOCoU0gNQUskR0kp6Ds0iQug_gdNpbnccv9zkz_qpD0rTZVV5faCCbNHk0C1SgwQ_HiDPpWIkPmhlsCNSRqG-K81vp4eBxF0yoT7hjC5qbHoGrNg1N5ajD2RRsRDTKjs5_mlT8-KzGMc8\"></p><p><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjIP3GW5LDV6BGnv3US4ETcEfGAVJMqVSYQqF7Vqll9DZv3DteaE7mYdeBMa9wXe0sJkhwazyvf1kyD6TR5V6A2txTWKIWMVtSzcDmkXZUVTLBtwhZmLP-3vwK37mop06GhqvBbKue2jUmhVu939lX10HuQaxfga8pK6R3-Zag2jewzw1DQwJ46_Lkqyfk/s2128/DSC04702.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjIP3GW5LDV6BGnv3US4ETcEfGAVJMqVSYQqF7Vqll9DZv3DteaE7mYdeBMa9wXe0sJkhwazyvf1kyD6TR5V6A2txTWKIWMVtSzcDmkXZUVTLBtwhZmLP-3vwK37mop06GhqvBbKue2jUmhVu939lX10HuQaxfga8pK6R3-Zag2jewzw1DQwJ46_Lkqyfk/s600/DSC04702.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲封面很可愛，可以看到好多隻怪物～</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjzXazGe_eF0I08KhfTdc1ZSKrZbtsX6K9BtTn3B6dUxKiHMxZwv6oc87FFkeqzP306mYBTgODftmamI-3kZWKoPm2J6V5JFHo2l7KQZw_aC1RxrL9SybrzEsQRiH05w8IEB8De8IJ3eGgc-yuLh1cjeB4inAUi4x0nox-dxXXPOX8-QTwx9POEXC_228s/s3748/DSC04703.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjzXazGe_eF0I08KhfTdc1ZSKrZbtsX6K9BtTn3B6dUxKiHMxZwv6oc87FFkeqzP306mYBTgODftmamI-3kZWKoPm2J6V5JFHo2l7KQZw_aC1RxrL9SybrzEsQRiH05w8IEB8De8IJ3eGgc-yuLh1cjeB4inAUi4x0nox-dxXXPOX8-QTwx9POEXC_228s/s600/DSC04703.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲遊戲人數：3-6人　建議年齡：14+　遊戲時間：30 mins</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgx6HLVHufQLgGyZpvbsQFXvyxNdDJhth73e3953wxP57F2v2eXPhlGFAtdEPSFlkrEZuEvUoAV828QW9vNW3a7u4wBX7OcdJ6lOm8fx9v6i3gYQJH-0qNt0aPyvl3OyGzOs3jFSDxarVgZxzWxk9NJTe9vljpLiDAiLIr3B8NL6mh1xmMRs9CHc7CdJck/s2072/DSC04704.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgx6HLVHufQLgGyZpvbsQFXvyxNdDJhth73e3953wxP57F2v2eXPhlGFAtdEPSFlkrEZuEvUoAV828QW9vNW3a7u4wBX7OcdJ6lOm8fx9v6i3gYQJH-0qNt0aPyvl3OyGzOs3jFSDxarVgZxzWxk9NJTe9vljpLiDAiLIr3B8NL6mh1xmMRs9CHc7CdJck/s600/DSC04704.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲盒底有遊戲概況，可以看到用到許多骰子～</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjC33bSSttHbfemfV4kKFhbFVcDQKmYB2-aIZMUEoIiaNaRrL2NezmnntcYze1xdAe8z8y5g7EkWYWgHzBTFvP1H1UQY3mVqt_CEg25NlnROWWznFjUQpTk-N3MqXFfjIYv2UXQClq82XQxGdJSmwKIWwp3vVB87JAfp93t5nuBKO9Px9weoTDa31vCeBk/s3664/DSC04705.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjC33bSSttHbfemfV4kKFhbFVcDQKmYB2-aIZMUEoIiaNaRrL2NezmnntcYze1xdAe8z8y5g7EkWYWgHzBTFvP1H1UQY3mVqt_CEg25NlnROWWznFjUQpTk-N3MqXFfjIYv2UXQClq82XQxGdJSmwKIWwp3vVB87JAfp93t5nuBKO9Px9weoTDa31vCeBk/s600/DSC04705.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲內容物一覽</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhMRNlMXbmRGd4OaWEJc-wpekA2hnoOT7qKk6eoOlI622bI4AU4A4klTkPPgDp0ZOY3uXGjIBQ5NPVBg6Bj8okuGR9B5Ybv6376af3uEg6jmUB95iLQ2hA0J6M6XGJ0uCfIiQoFhHPiBWW8mX1-h5E7Q4yZbGrqgkwU2K6jsDMsTqOHUPvGX5-2lsNWzok/s5160/DSC04706.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhMRNlMXbmRGd4OaWEJc-wpekA2hnoOT7qKk6eoOlI622bI4AU4A4klTkPPgDp0ZOY3uXGjIBQ5NPVBg6Bj8okuGR9B5Ybv6376af3uEg6jmUB95iLQ2hA0J6M6XGJ0uCfIiQoFhHPiBWW8mX1-h5E7Q4yZbGrqgkwU2K6jsDMsTqOHUPvGX5-2lsNWzok/s600/DSC04706.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲超多骰子～</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjDU8MayGveaPQyJZG2v0ZzspW2UuAIEzLWGOtij4H9ycpw9X4CXwYASQTfdpmIGkDL6nyXyTt733P3VXxY1QvVDXGzMgLRe31gvu9JAbF8x6-MYFkI1lEK1Lwjq9QvmiRZWd862SiPnFwVjChgQkDHJ9G_iHvg_YIw6OBrWAIjF_O6-0oYtvzPAKAw9iw/s5176/DSC04707.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjDU8MayGveaPQyJZG2v0ZzspW2UuAIEzLWGOtij4H9ycpw9X4CXwYASQTfdpmIGkDL6nyXyTt733P3VXxY1QvVDXGzMgLRe31gvu9JAbF8x6-MYFkI1lEK1Lwjq9QvmiRZWd862SiPnFwVjChgQkDHJ9G_iHvg_YIw6OBrWAIjF_O6-0oYtvzPAKAw9iw/s600/DSC04707.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲都是六面骰，而且圖樣都是特殊骰～比較可惜是平面印刷，怕用久了會有磨損的可能～</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEi3rNG1Qa07yGgq3GTbJnYiqhKwJBEos3A7HokdiUQbYLFYEhH6nk1AYd-lvL7lJ31sCeuOoHaLsl6RsvwAZvq9WyTXwAFo4Ttr6B-Tno1dad4k8vlGPLXh2fzUCciqo5M38Gcm3fTX8D6FZnQ7ixRv8GY80w_QHUsO17lcqgW9CU6wwMNmKhbc1BfS3xc/s4800/DSC04708.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEi3rNG1Qa07yGgq3GTbJnYiqhKwJBEos3A7HokdiUQbYLFYEhH6nk1AYd-lvL7lJ31sCeuOoHaLsl6RsvwAZvq9WyTXwAFo4Ttr6B-Tno1dad4k8vlGPLXh2fzUCciqo5M38Gcm3fTX8D6FZnQ7ixRv8GY80w_QHUsO17lcqgW9CU6wwMNmKhbc1BfS3xc/s600/DSC04708.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲抽袋一個</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjNmRo93udtdDUlpwFL2Hmg0HLYEqw28RH0PtLJDXdoHw7dWLL2LHoYpVtVImC_OGMbgWiYx9nZylHe8jAp-FxtDAyW6ToOBFHQB7s7NrEfQk9K17Pr8SG8PJGyXl4We-0RB4WIBLdZO1Si1RTgtr1j_02fJDgJD1Y6nVduVUCy_jKBE_ck2JfEBxOtP9s/s3304/DSC04709.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjNmRo93udtdDUlpwFL2Hmg0HLYEqw28RH0PtLJDXdoHw7dWLL2LHoYpVtVImC_OGMbgWiYx9nZylHe8jAp-FxtDAyW6ToOBFHQB7s7NrEfQk9K17Pr8SG8PJGyXl4We-0RB4WIBLdZO1Si1RTgtr1j_02fJDgJD1Y6nVduVUCy_jKBE_ck2JfEBxOtP9s/s600/DSC04709.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲擋板一包</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiYsuYQv2ddSZu0iMnuU6rMLmXATLDLWtTK1dopRZyxrpoFi2VnlNyw0FL9TwROGIL2BpWhQ9_w8s72Yw6enQRivt80aq6OyvM2TRr_95VIeWG7vVthwarhsCQ5Ub0ZiWo4CduBTWSquduWjtR4v7YtpDanazPDBQzaI0ZO1Qaps6FsdhSpv6LNSP2W7Bg/s5092/DSC04710.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiYsuYQv2ddSZu0iMnuU6rMLmXATLDLWtTK1dopRZyxrpoFi2VnlNyw0FL9TwROGIL2BpWhQ9_w8s72Yw6enQRivt80aq6OyvM2TRr_95VIeWG7vVthwarhsCQ5Ub0ZiWo4CduBTWSquduWjtR4v7YtpDanazPDBQzaI0ZO1Qaps6FsdhSpv6LNSP2W7Bg/s600/DSC04710.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲擋板本身也是玩家幫助卡～</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEg4TSX3Jkhyhrqv4ORhP9sjD6WpuzE7OQNHowQaMzxCaPPUopmXAnEfKhUbS8MH4dODN1BIF2cgipQSFsETKDKpyKWzjaHEEs59jNcrSZKW6Kl3-dNg2w6mBNEgFeN-P11rTfyvKhBgBPbPzyUWGFA06oJqTpHno5K1rkXA6o_7DZYSY5Hm-B-MQl30Brw/s5472/DSC04711.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEg4TSX3Jkhyhrqv4ORhP9sjD6WpuzE7OQNHowQaMzxCaPPUopmXAnEfKhUbS8MH4dODN1BIF2cgipQSFsETKDKpyKWzjaHEEs59jNcrSZKW6Kl3-dNg2w6mBNEgFeN-P11rTfyvKhBgBPbPzyUWGFA06oJqTpHno5K1rkXA6o_7DZYSY5Hm-B-MQl30Brw/s600/DSC04711.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲圖案非常的可愛，除了有米諾陶洛斯之外，還有人魚、獅鷲、木乃伊、南瓜人等等～</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEjj1Z_QZcKu3-HRfraEZrRtZYwrZ07_emSbvTaVIDieRBnUj_7ydTuWfDQidAA-x--AVsxpFbf3ky0dOyus2iMI-k_4Vt2vs-VcFTJ_o-Wu9t_FPBNR2ndlHzskP4oe2UCTt7PjQ7pUOsR9xdFgEVAhT7UqvKA7B4JBQOyxERUORhvXVFSOx3MZyyRQLAg\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEjj1Z_QZcKu3-HRfraEZrRtZYwrZ07_emSbvTaVIDieRBnUj_7ydTuWfDQidAA-x--AVsxpFbf3ky0dOyus2iMI-k_4Vt2vs-VcFTJ_o-Wu9t_FPBNR2ndlHzskP4oe2UCTt7PjQ7pUOsR9xdFgEVAhT7UqvKA7B4JBQOyxERUORhvXVFSOx3MZyyRQLAg\"></a></p><p><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲先附上龍龍影片</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgmkzwrUCe7McD2v7GamYAXFes0Ck4wE2nOPcdHQHEFusBrNzDLtRERvUH3DCZwod7Ynz-n1fRKAf56cm1eIGq_MLRSPmokF2rEohJm-RYg2S1KXBb2FzWEN1MM938RUPlY-BcylmyPDlXegGb-mIhO06pNX3QaC8nW2MDHeFNNqGMyuGae9ekKk41gkR0/s600/DSC04713.JPG\"></p><p>▲遊戲會因為遊玩人數的不同，輪數不同～這一點不用記，因為計分紙上設計得很清楚～</p><p>３～４人遊戲就是８輪、５人遊戲７輪，６人遊戲６輪～</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjuNuvmCwb8tWpEXW7mXm6c4BshMiMjWI2bFbyLg7pvwy-JAc_8InHbOrym9ElscX72rjMjw18-1HM1z9HN7rY9XGber0m7L8OpL1C7bq3WHeEMuWlXoWfTiy_lFI9DpGypsblhNHT9jkhxDfvCB3Omr3l2vDX7SQS95zUFS2Q4AS6uB2Zd2lnxz6-j1t4/s600/DSC04715.JPG\"></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">▲知道輪數之後，我們來說遊戲怎麼進行～遊戲一開始會選一位起始玩家，然後把所有骰子丟進抽袋中～第Ｎ輪大家會各自抽Ｎ顆骰，放在自己的擋板背後～當所有人都看過自己的骰子之後，這時候要進行一個【同時喊墩】的步驟！建議大家用類似剪刀石頭布的方式，把你這回合預計要吃到的墩數，用手指頭比出來～（如果一隻手不夠，就用雙手）</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">接著由起始玩家開始，選擇１顆骰子並丟出～接著換順時鐘的下一位玩家～這個時候要遵循吃墩遊戲規則～大家如果手中有跟起始玩家相同顏色的骰子，則一定要丟出；如果沒有，則可以任選骰子丟出～</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">當所有人都丟出骰子之後，就是比大小的時間，結算後勝利的玩家吃得該墩，然後起始玩家繼續丟下一顆骰子～直到該輪的骰子都用完為止～接著計分，然後進行下一輪，把骰子全部放回袋子中，換順時鐘下一位玩家當起始玩家～</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEj-YkHYy_N_PkmiZ-Z2eUtyZi3NL6cInTV8SLyf3x9ypQ0dvU9XIWumaM1-JKqgBxs_CMvotzpWhR-ZT9EIFMiNDmh7jpiPhXQz2EykudRGJeOYyjGFxIFa-Xnx0_OzEPRGHtxZCvK0diHVn_kWKO3bEmLvTGjkRtrvBeUZlMCWPeHsHumAsO3GJ-NL0IM/s4184/DSC04712.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEj-YkHYy_N_PkmiZ-Z2eUtyZi3NL6cInTV8SLyf3x9ypQ0dvU9XIWumaM1-JKqgBxs_CMvotzpWhR-ZT9EIFMiNDmh7jpiPhXQz2EykudRGJeOYyjGFxIFa-Xnx0_OzEPRGHtxZCvK0diHVn_kWKO3bEmLvTGjkRtrvBeUZlMCWPeHsHumAsO3GJ-NL0IM/s600/DSC04712.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">▲玩家幫助卡上有所有骰子的骰面組成圖，此外也有每一種骰子的數量，讓你可以推算自己大概能吃到多少墩數～米諾陶洛斯的骰子很稀有，只有一顆～</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgF7h9uLGZ6YI5wJT0sC1_VkBIGrYzEtgvtAiBpLfd1JxcyVJvSAJvxa1qZ4OhY-qcO85ThE7hq8bz0V7dZSxXZWMv18jxaDs6ZoVV_hAgev_JbgAI9wAzrygJsiyfM3WRZWzKq7SahgjLhOVALC466ykeSvBsyBgJYOc1wl9CQ7bqoY9xkXLZSWhMqiyY/s2468/DSC04714.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgF7h9uLGZ6YI5wJT0sC1_VkBIGrYzEtgvtAiBpLfd1JxcyVJvSAJvxa1qZ4OhY-qcO85ThE7hq8bz0V7dZSxXZWMv18jxaDs6ZoVV_hAgev_JbgAI9wAzrygJsiyfM3WRZWzKq7SahgjLhOVALC466ykeSvBsyBgJYOc1wl9CQ7bqoY9xkXLZSWhMqiyY/s600/DSC04714.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">▲最後來看最重要的勝負判定～遊戲當中的前三種骰子稱為【怪物骰】只要出現怪物符號，就可以贏過所有的數字與旗子～同一種怪物，順位比較後面出現的玩家獲勝～此外三種怪物為相剋關係（如上圖），出現人魚（藍色）打敗米諾陶洛斯，或是米諾陶洛斯打敗獅鷲（綠色）的情況，都可以額外加分（如上圖）～如果同一墩當中，三種怪物符號都出現，那就由人魚獲勝～</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">如果場上所有人的骰子都是數字，不用管顏色，數字最大的玩家獲勝。如果最大數字中有出現相同數字，順位比較後面出現的玩家獲勝～</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">旗子是場上最小的符號，出現旗子的玩家無法戰勝其他任何符號～但是～如果這次場上所有的骰子結果都是旗子！那第一顆骰出旗子的玩家獲勝！（要注意三種怪物骰上面也都會有旗子）～</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiOkKPwTo3bmHZWbbYyrhZOvs9EA-FbKiF14NurulVB2x2MZ8jboPEbvyglRrPsZLDeTShKseXIVoV02ZkXuhFKNBSonxRiXqQ125o4z78C1P1iCAPksxn_jZ8-_5i8eetCHLnCFw5k-c7EvxusLqVVGyZS83LPVK6bv-8qZNQ3iai8cU471Gcfxe35OLg/w640-h502/DSC04713.png\"></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">＊藍色數字為預測墩數與加減分；紅色數字為實際吃到的墩數</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">▲最後來講每一輪結束算分，除了剛剛說的怪物互打會給特殊獎勵分數之外，每一輪的分數會有四種情況發生：</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">【情況一】預測墩數與所吃墩數相同（不是零）：看吃幾墩，每墩２０分～以上圖來說，就是肥龍的第一輪與洛克的第二輪，都是預測一墩吃到一墩，因此得２０分～</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">【情況二】預測墩數與所吃墩數不同（不是零）：每差一墩扣１０分～以上圖來說，就是小羊的第一輪，我預測會吃到一墩，結果什麼都沒吃到，扣１０分。</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">【情況三】預測零墩結果吃到零墩：得到分數＝輪數＊１０分～以上圖來說，就是洛克的第一輪，與小羊和吉姆的第二輪～雖然都是預測零吃到零～但是輪數越後面，這種情況得到的分數越高～</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">【情況四】預測零墩，結果不小心吃到墩：扣掉分數＝輪數＊１０分～以上圖來說，就是肥龍的第二輪，他預測自己會吃到零墩，結果吃到一墩，所以扣掉第二輪＊１０分＝２０分～</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">遊戲當然就是把所有輪數跑完，最後最高分的玩家獲勝！</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEg6ACnWEyYvn1s2JybBzPXtC_VTn5GHEgrzzmPs5Zxc3CMQqr2vU53qil6A3LI67kdXVlXjlBYlNtgPvCm2T7N9AV2WcnpwZXHX9lwF1--IVjw7h7Hw3NNxQTdF1T3bHlpLSife85qufLQyxmZR-VMH7HCMiHsuSeEGBeD88llWPUofWcxWcn6-3mlSwMU\"></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>迸出新滋味！</strong></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">對我來說，大部分的吃墩遊戲是需要動腦的！你可以觀察前幾家喊幾墩、可以洗王、可以故意把自己弄成缺門、可以．．．．有很多不同的策略跟細節要注意！但是！《Mino Dice 米諾骰》完全不管了！就算是你拿到本遊戲最強的唯一王者－米諾陶洛斯本牛，也不能保證他一定可以為你贏下一墩！（因為它會輸給人魚，也有可能會骰一骰變成一面旗子）</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">這種不確定性，也讓這款吃墩遊戲變得非常．．．．『不吃墩』！尤其是前幾回合骰子很少的時候，根本是只能把命託付給骰子了～總之，如果是本格派的吃墩玩家，可能會不喜歡，或是不習慣這款遊戲～但如果站在派對遊戲的立場來看就不同了，由於骰子真的很不受控～因此真的很鬧～很有可能全場都是怪物骰，但因為都骰到旗子，所以輸給了一顆數字１～</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">這款遊戲我會推薦給：喜歡派對遊戲的玩家，喜歡骰子遊戲的玩家，喜歡嘗試變種吃墩遊戲的玩家～</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjibcM0tXwNm77i4oZqhsU_88JpbfX23hFlaa5UMpDycjLzubF-QC6SeWVQ2YzoPOa5d0FgzTcqIh-rfLewKoQ0XTzgVbGvF_zz4juZGIH3dbftFZVmC0X91Q3Y_9pqisCkLrey2co4JsrylZfpOhc4s_7n7CYZ8IqTzxZ5AhM8-DAEfaHxGToPLE8iNWA/s4264/DSC04716.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjibcM0tXwNm77i4oZqhsU_88JpbfX23hFlaa5UMpDycjLzubF-QC6SeWVQ2YzoPOa5d0FgzTcqIh-rfLewKoQ0XTzgVbGvF_zz4juZGIH3dbftFZVmC0X91Q3Y_9pqisCkLrey2co4JsrylZfpOhc4s_7n7CYZ8IqTzxZ5AhM8-DAEfaHxGToPLE8iNWA/s600/DSC04716.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲遊戲收納照，小小一盒，玩起來相當歡樂～</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p><br></p>', '2024-11-18 10:29:51', '2024-11-18 10:29:51', 1, 'forum-1731896991489-300884930.jpg'),
(23, 1, '【桌遊開箱報】No context 迷因在說話 開箱+介紹', '<h3><br></h3><p><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiPwEw015-nV82JwIODV4nm7E_WK6ElwKCbeAhPKq0I23Cozv8TJJNoNxvVFA-HkoN4vHIY-U2eK5yNJIVvBI3tvAthY_d-uCbyKlygCZSqo29-F5-8_ZHFKHJKgX5kXYc0NHzA_XWL5dDpWeht5MSnG2YXLVbJtv4gLRYKejMkWaprBkWq1i4ZnRV_dsA/s3088/DSC04722.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiPwEw015-nV82JwIODV4nm7E_WK6ElwKCbeAhPKq0I23Cozv8TJJNoNxvVFA-HkoN4vHIY-U2eK5yNJIVvBI3tvAthY_d-uCbyKlygCZSqo29-F5-8_ZHFKHJKgX5kXYc0NHzA_XWL5dDpWeht5MSnG2YXLVbJtv4gLRYKejMkWaprBkWq1i4ZnRV_dsA/s600/DSC04722.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEhYA2__R2VKeItW-9wHBHpEjIUP_FfonBm1jhpdHsSLGXXo7vUONIMmmwQAx5I1xHadcUEI3i18zMS9Hep83xWAK1KVmsyuXTeKa-q15WN-oVLKRpDZlgxS1qZK4Pg2QZpwdTkRPa8lt3xSmPCY_dTJ6A5mV3fDW_l093Yq2Ag9Z7IQRyCQ_F3fUUC5WNs\"></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">Mr. Lovenstein是國外相當有名的圖片IP，老實說雖然有在網路上看過他的圖，但直到這款遊戲才真正知道它的正式名稱～也是在正式去搜尋之後才知道，原來繪師本人的名字是J.L. Westover而不是Lovenstein。到底這款遊戲會用Mr. Lovenstein這些可愛中又帶點嘲諷梗味十足的圖來變出什麼花樣呢？今天就來說給大家聽～</p><p><br></p><p><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEj-XYIv3kJn33d5J8DcqO7t5ugh1CgZvfoFqenPf-7dkWiNDG8k8z9s5O7g7YbfLHt67nVFSz7T2QUkwBO2BKM420AUnajlaxAl1DPPx1y3CZs0THGPLKXmB6PtX2UHZdWy2ZlV6qZEPfAKhJWKFf7hl3C-T81_nZhOJTcHIjyQq1jhgVp_l494SayY178\"></p><p><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiPwEw015-nV82JwIODV4nm7E_WK6ElwKCbeAhPKq0I23Cozv8TJJNoNxvVFA-HkoN4vHIY-U2eK5yNJIVvBI3tvAthY_d-uCbyKlygCZSqo29-F5-8_ZHFKHJKgX5kXYc0NHzA_XWL5dDpWeht5MSnG2YXLVbJtv4gLRYKejMkWaprBkWq1i4ZnRV_dsA/s3088/DSC04722.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiPwEw015-nV82JwIODV4nm7E_WK6ElwKCbeAhPKq0I23Cozv8TJJNoNxvVFA-HkoN4vHIY-U2eK5yNJIVvBI3tvAthY_d-uCbyKlygCZSqo29-F5-8_ZHFKHJKgX5kXYc0NHzA_XWL5dDpWeht5MSnG2YXLVbJtv4gLRYKejMkWaprBkWq1i4ZnRV_dsA/s600/DSC04722.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲封面就可以看到很多可愛的圖～</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjD4OxjjIjTewfVLowRCyQyydkx-hGon551etRZwS0sVHWUf-qCTsttPj6MfWx5znhFvFOJFJmYgzkwwNMcdv621gEAlOpVLKCME6mymmiPz4mwo_2dYJS8QO86JFI9kgMreBkfvN1nPdPJGtH_CIIqKo84Qr8GyVDT7reViR_a3f37-5AASNc-tr7y6qk/s3948/DSC04723.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjD4OxjjIjTewfVLowRCyQyydkx-hGon551etRZwS0sVHWUf-qCTsttPj6MfWx5znhFvFOJFJmYgzkwwNMcdv621gEAlOpVLKCME6mymmiPz4mwo_2dYJS8QO86JFI9kgMreBkfvN1nPdPJGtH_CIIqKo84Qr8GyVDT7reViR_a3f37-5AASNc-tr7y6qk/s600/DSC04723.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲遊戲人數：2-6人　建議年齡：13+　遊戲時間：20-30 mins</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEizHyfIwHldFZMaaH2Kg-QgaNl8_ZqJc0CSF0E4ZDmDn1nTboRJeT-gwJ-d1X0SxxNzS_gEyimC2Jajf0OHX1c7ziT8GVh8yBY9k_aGp3L0zSq4Dz07Yuy3OCH9Kp0lqjYrEozmCN8Z56IxKIxXZctza0ZIuqUxoRQPcb4UX64g1vOGdrdZNiEGMePLLbg/s3028/DSC04724.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEizHyfIwHldFZMaaH2Kg-QgaNl8_ZqJc0CSF0E4ZDmDn1nTboRJeT-gwJ-d1X0SxxNzS_gEyimC2Jajf0OHX1c7ziT8GVh8yBY9k_aGp3L0zSq4Dz07Yuy3OCH9Kp0lqjYrEozmCN8Z56IxKIxXZctza0ZIuqUxoRQPcb4UX64g1vOGdrdZNiEGMePLLbg/s600/DSC04724.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲封底有遊戲概況，還有一次試玩的機會～</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjI7BozAiJZ1t_oADP06dKVM6X2BghLs3I1eEWldFV3PPpCpNIYhqUDNZP94Y3h8kBz8AMYmlmuar2hSoAwDSh4FZQE0m71EMGXdsjqz1CHuCQkC2msCdQaQuZTnQuYbwYb1K1rwatccjubUOmLC76DFI4kZCcIve9LqL7ArKH_uQzd-j0YqtDilhX8Fik/s5104/DSC04725.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjI7BozAiJZ1t_oADP06dKVM6X2BghLs3I1eEWldFV3PPpCpNIYhqUDNZP94Y3h8kBz8AMYmlmuar2hSoAwDSh4FZQE0m71EMGXdsjqz1CHuCQkC2msCdQaQuZTnQuYbwYb1K1rwatccjubUOmLC76DFI4kZCcIve9LqL7ArKH_uQzd-j0YqtDilhX8Fik/s600/DSC04725.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲內容物一覽</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEieefECqv_t0tPyJDZw__RzIVmGhKUC6VWDkcGsM9mHvZUowlBhVhQhwREU9Dx3GWpejthPVJFUg4alHnjI86gPkrgwx7PspHPQabi3SyDCTFSns-NAuLhcbZT6wGeL5NxA6o-Qk1Xi4xxNkvrY-T2MhBNmCFTQK7aZQPZIZVwkpNUpDOAFAGML-ImxiTE/s5424/DSC04726.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEieefECqv_t0tPyJDZw__RzIVmGhKUC6VWDkcGsM9mHvZUowlBhVhQhwREU9Dx3GWpejthPVJFUg4alHnjI86gPkrgwx7PspHPQabi3SyDCTFSns-NAuLhcbZT6wGeL5NxA6o-Qk1Xi4xxNkvrY-T2MhBNmCFTQK7aZQPZIZVwkpNUpDOAFAGML-ImxiTE/s600/DSC04726.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲有超多的迷因圖片卡</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEilAsGTMw6iwtQUEQCYwVlLdaId_z0PNos3O1cxbUCmB96N_qufRhf8cQcLBu2uad6vIxCpo0P86TjSlt47zc5EcMzUaw2Mqzdon20cSfYCUQYnRYc-OKCaNHgPoBiOb8gugvKlseDR2DPyfbQYbqB-lQwPhOiSQkVS4abvYeEw1-LBz5Co9kiDnucA2oY/s5316/DSC04729.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEilAsGTMw6iwtQUEQCYwVlLdaId_z0PNos3O1cxbUCmB96N_qufRhf8cQcLBu2uad6vIxCpo0P86TjSlt47zc5EcMzUaw2Mqzdon20cSfYCUQYnRYc-OKCaNHgPoBiOb8gugvKlseDR2DPyfbQYbqB-lQwPhOiSQkVS4abvYeEw1-LBz5Co9kiDnucA2oY/s600/DSC04729.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲迷因卡都是雙面的，一面是綠色打勾，另一面是紅色打Ｘ</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">但是同一張卡兩面的主圖案是相同的（僅符號與邊框不同）</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgN_9pNjQntC4eLPxS_y8yWKARFIGIvueeIzzpT0zYD-bB3xre83LTTDSo0g1rTmfgyltIu-q-EQCB9tRbWiML2JPeC2ccz_eMgDQTtNcoT9WUsek8cgKzFufirr-IuShKWzYX8WBwxnodbaDCAwS8z2sqq0bcbzB3jXkgZNA9ryP5HuC2Znk0qRvezH6c/s4736/DSC04731.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgN_9pNjQntC4eLPxS_y8yWKARFIGIvueeIzzpT0zYD-bB3xre83LTTDSo0g1rTmfgyltIu-q-EQCB9tRbWiML2JPeC2ccz_eMgDQTtNcoT9WUsek8cgKzFufirr-IuShKWzYX8WBwxnodbaDCAwS8z2sqq0bcbzB3jXkgZNA9ryP5HuC2Znk0qRvezH6c/s600/DSC04731.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲此外還有七張【描述卡】，以及六套每位玩家各一種顏色的下標卡～</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhx2VN_crPIV7TB-ssiNJySHFDZzXQ6zNOCGdNaY6x_6ObAolAi9By9921FIw7iJLGMmzHLUJYieibYGGIE9JQD9IqAncOwiqylVr6EwMQDPEFJrHIta_uTwpPejFGHIZxlD7RF12X7Uxg-7_EvZX-GkfHlFgPsHu6RCry8-aU3xWQgcZ07LEIKzvcXay0/s3724/DSC04732.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhx2VN_crPIV7TB-ssiNJySHFDZzXQ6zNOCGdNaY6x_6ObAolAi9By9921FIw7iJLGMmzHLUJYieibYGGIE9JQD9IqAncOwiqylVr6EwMQDPEFJrHIta_uTwpPejFGHIZxlD7RF12X7Uxg-7_EvZX-GkfHlFgPsHu6RCry8-aU3xWQgcZ07LEIKzvcXay0/s600/DSC04732.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲遊戲主圖板一張</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjlNw2N9pxPjJcgOHRLjPm1vTMieAR5GYUDuTh6NGmGzSFdX-UVX5f_2RXZzOiNBAEGT0hAsVM8j3_IWHtYAix_V3KmcMHErRYHhmXpDDVUbIR2Z4nE2WZnLHX_W5OQXFGgAkZfvgQOaoWCBYkDoWyWX-zWxOlEjSOMQK0sYfvRtdP6O-YbneyLXZFtH7w/s4812/DSC04733.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjlNw2N9pxPjJcgOHRLjPm1vTMieAR5GYUDuTh6NGmGzSFdX-UVX5f_2RXZzOiNBAEGT0hAsVM8j3_IWHtYAix_V3KmcMHErRYHhmXpDDVUbIR2Z4nE2WZnLHX_W5OQXFGgAkZfvgQOaoWCBYkDoWyWX-zWxOlEjSOMQK0sYfvRtdP6O-YbneyLXZFtH7w/s600/DSC04733.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲圖板打開之後還蠻大張的</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEhI3V3B7VoTnRFeXoSBhQcuichvLccumitJ_oJtCTRz_sQG-I7JNr_3aWK-1__71Nz9iQfmzWz-hAH4_Ta6avQj2_T0T0XHxrOYIqENR_0Sp0JHcrNA5WBIM4J7mN2gTi9RXIHpehOd6rmvv7MKLfkX-bGWLmW9bRgBUMAezJZNbykLcWctVK6j4LPslTQ\"></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEh2dpb3m5PIdptGiCSe0xwJG0bvywBA9dA8aK797dVqoHLAmFDNfXb_RSwwA5d2Hk5GkewjWSP6QyjZfytQHeS8Mxh-Q3GiTaabiNZYmW669S5gaw0HYR_4t0CkBodmdB4mKCEFRotfbEVTlfFnvkZ6wycwybyOy_qLE9T8FmtPXL24XOqAyvvSjvxGHYQ/s4972/DSC04734.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEh2dpb3m5PIdptGiCSe0xwJG0bvywBA9dA8aK797dVqoHLAmFDNfXb_RSwwA5d2Hk5GkewjWSP6QyjZfytQHeS8Mxh-Q3GiTaabiNZYmW669S5gaw0HYR_4t0CkBodmdB4mKCEFRotfbEVTlfFnvkZ6wycwybyOy_qLE9T8FmtPXL24XOqAyvvSjvxGHYQ/s600/DSC04734.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">▲遊戲設置的方式如上，把圖板打開，根據遊戲人數在圖板上放與下方隨機放置迷因卡片～（３人遊戲，上下各５張；４人遊戲，上下各６張；５人遊戲，上下各７張）</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiTPvhH_Arw12wKYEUnuYyUgwFmEM00pZ8rTI7xlWbb5CLAo-T5OuBhhlOrWx8k7Nra99VsXBaEw7KKtOl2MOzdiHQUt9a_Z8SOg0jsVI6dtHwaaBgC7oGDfQSF5U4e4kRwzJapVrSom7Gu9YNM8K3yajTHAEwHQBav17EOTre8JuqVOWUE-ZpkaVDx0Dc/s4464/DSC04735.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiTPvhH_Arw12wKYEUnuYyUgwFmEM00pZ8rTI7xlWbb5CLAo-T5OuBhhlOrWx8k7Nra99VsXBaEw7KKtOl2MOzdiHQUt9a_Z8SOg0jsVI6dtHwaaBgC7oGDfQSF5U4e4kRwzJapVrSom7Gu9YNM8K3yajTHAEwHQBav17EOTre8JuqVOWUE-ZpkaVDx0Dc/s600/DSC04735.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">▲每位玩家隨機抽取一張目標牌（當然要符合這次的題目數量，比方說題目有５題，那就從１－５當中隨機抽１張）與同顏色的下注牌一組～</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiZWVggXuSAfLYS9UGE3IiQDaWCSetvyTLNuYiN3XLhK0ZhyphenhyphenJgOChTGlH4TS808a38HZBvfuDkWRXbRcLDfMZvOCgnizCrjnKlcD1iaItqSic_CAQ6LVq3hvoO0qEf_JPDejULqFnioZYjtah7LFazSGp-0xK1tK6z0MBXOEJ6Z2a2PbGDA-5LVOuV251Q/s5076/DSC04736.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiZWVggXuSAfLYS9UGE3IiQDaWCSetvyTLNuYiN3XLhK0ZhyphenhyphenJgOChTGlH4TS808a38HZBvfuDkWRXbRcLDfMZvOCgnizCrjnKlcD1iaItqSic_CAQ6LVq3hvoO0qEf_JPDejULqFnioZYjtah7LFazSGp-0xK1tK6z0MBXOEJ6Z2a2PbGDA-5LVOuV251Q/s600/DSC04736.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">▲抽完目標牌之後，你就會知道你這次的目標是哪一張卡片了～（當然，這是隱藏資訊，不能讓其他玩家知道）以上圖來說，我這次抽到２號，因此我的目標就會是『雙手點讚』這張圖～</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEh7UKF2HtFn2HwVLecjFpPfQLHmNA6CR252wLpExw32l3gVty9xzFnXuf6bie_2eXaXJEWmdWOuam7pJtTcgi2yGKHsGkKrFPhoqOuyvuU0LIoYFJkW9eqDv-gL3cp-udwg91gOAZwfd6SKXv7yVw5-_rTSuzt_TqtEFIwe7tobhyphenhyphenyN3s2ybltBxIFbA34/s5268/DSC04737.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEh7UKF2HtFn2HwVLecjFpPfQLHmNA6CR252wLpExw32l3gVty9xzFnXuf6bie_2eXaXJEWmdWOuam7pJtTcgi2yGKHsGkKrFPhoqOuyvuU0LIoYFJkW9eqDv-gL3cp-udwg91gOAZwfd6SKXv7yVw5-_rTSuzt_TqtEFIwe7tobhyphenhyphenyN3s2ybltBxIFbA34/s600/DSC04737.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">▲輪到我的時候，我要從下面的５張卡片選一張跟我的目標有關，或是跟我目標無關的卡片來使用～</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjOnzUL4xDe_DjFYX6jB2dvmTb6MdOwflWN-LQjEkfGlyAwj2epg9ymf3B1HOowO4CMQPO0RF0bFL3SROl6PyCPNMPQ9xFo1NrzOlQjbCKpQ_uQCAqIt4_SkJIPELq2SfxW5GodozKJS7mYjrrHjk2vbohDJky6SDduqiIjO1YBQ9WCNgqhWMtNf-uFrFk/s5276/DSC04738.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjOnzUL4xDe_DjFYX6jB2dvmTb6MdOwflWN-LQjEkfGlyAwj2epg9ymf3B1HOowO4CMQPO0RF0bFL3SROl6PyCPNMPQ9xFo1NrzOlQjbCKpQ_uQCAqIt4_SkJIPELq2SfxW5GodozKJS7mYjrrHjk2vbohDJky6SDduqiIjO1YBQ9WCNgqhWMtNf-uFrFk/s600/DSC04738.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">▲我選了這張咖啡被弄倒的『美好的一天』由於我覺得他跟我的『雙手點讚』相反，因此我把它翻到紅色的Ｘ面，然後放到我的區域中（由於我的下注牌是選淺藍色，我的區域也就是淺藍色）。</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjbwvzO0zBagLlB7OOJN-Rfv2b-w3Wg1zZ6EpGBZqIrwAZTlBfDp8wxsGQMPFp9XRfiM7XvkAGfH7AhQ6VZhyphenhyphenrcm7-7wAyGtTOtEhjx_hbCXD3PhyueQ6oY69TBX6j23M3BHI_Jbrq4eIq651TYR7Izgc1zOuHglKPqlsKlsWozNOqk31hLffhFM3Xf8U4/s5108/DSC04739.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjbwvzO0zBagLlB7OOJN-Rfv2b-w3Wg1zZ6EpGBZqIrwAZTlBfDp8wxsGQMPFp9XRfiM7XvkAGfH7AhQ6VZhyphenhyphenrcm7-7wAyGtTOtEhjx_hbCXD3PhyueQ6oY69TBX6j23M3BHI_Jbrq4eIq651TYR7Izgc1zOuHglKPqlsKlsWozNOqk31hLffhFM3Xf8U4/s600/DSC04739.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲這時候其他玩家就可以隨意下注，深藍色玩家覺得他很懂我，因此就放了一張下注卡～</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">接著就換順時鐘下一位玩家進行遊戲，會把下面可用來描述的卡片捕到對應人數的張數，遊戲就這樣持續進行．．．．</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjybR1gP10oE5z_BCSBR-DjAlLp2y_oWCW260SWcT88K1aurdu2sxWmI8SG1oRCKut-b3jqeP0pWoDowCHqxrZWaZmrxFgr6mVWq1Y-XUjcd7zcBNj5LM6gQXnryguUwrs-7GAZ6P0v7iULlNHyWR30wndP6LOntntTlGUqkarGoC_iuXB_FxCKO2XwgVQ/s5472/DSC04740.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjybR1gP10oE5z_BCSBR-DjAlLp2y_oWCW260SWcT88K1aurdu2sxWmI8SG1oRCKut-b3jqeP0pWoDowCHqxrZWaZmrxFgr6mVWq1Y-XUjcd7zcBNj5LM6gQXnryguUwrs-7GAZ6P0v7iULlNHyWR30wndP6LOntntTlGUqkarGoC_iuXB_FxCKO2XwgVQ/s600/DSC04740.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">▲隨著遊戲的進行，每個題目的題是會越來越多，最多會像這樣來到３個提示，玩家們也會陸陸續續繼續下注～當所有玩家都完成下注／每個區域的３張提示都放完，就會進行結算～</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">結算的方式也很簡單，只要有玩家答對你的區域，你就會獲得你那張目標卡片當作分數。第一個答對的玩家會獲得２張卡片當分數，第二位答對的玩家獲得１張，再後面的就沒了～遊戲沒有額外做分數指示物，用卡片來當計分方式。</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">以上這樣算是一輪，遊戲共進行三輪之後，最高分的玩家獲勝！</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEg6ACnWEyYvn1s2JybBzPXtC_VTn5GHEgrzzmPs5Zxc3CMQqr2vU53qil6A3LI67kdXVlXjlBYlNtgPvCm2T7N9AV2WcnpwZXHX9lwF1--IVjw7h7Hw3NNxQTdF1T3bHlpLSife85qufLQyxmZR-VMH7HCMiHsuSeEGBeD88llWPUofWcxWcn6-3mlSwMU\"></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>我要看到血流成河！</strong></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">這一類的遊戲其實不少，主要就是考驗玩家們的默契與思考方式～同樣的兩張卡片，很有可能有人會覺得它們完全無關，也有人會覺得它們非常相似～玩著玩著可以知道誰跟你的想法比較貼近，或是比較懂你的梗～某種意義上來說也算是聯誼神器～或是讓你更了解你的朋友或家人的遊戲～</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">跟其他同類遊戲比起來，《No context 迷因在說話》內含許多豐富的迷因圖就是它最大的特色～相信喜歡Mr. Lovenstein畫作的朋友對這款遊戲絕對是愛不釋手～但同時，這款遊戲對我們來說比較可惜的是，有一些梗我們可能沒有很流行或是不熟悉～如果都是我們熟悉的梗，那玩起來應該會更有樂趣～</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">這款遊戲我會推薦給：尋找適合六人以下派對遊戲的玩家、有聯誼需求的玩家、喜歡Mr. Lovenstein畫作！</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgndHlluXHy5F_ZQyKuVkyeFO8u0ts-oB6J1h1mwq70idPYaO4jGXRhOniCDdfgJoNrYL_WO5ai3CRkk8zKnhr30BuIdXBF1svDrCQc0XsBtLkHN3D3wLcfi2d1toKKc56ScfkON3i6sZGL867YFvzPeMw8Tcjhg0o1dBFET6yR6s6VXpPFOjv8OkvtBSA/s4792/DSC04727.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgndHlluXHy5F_ZQyKuVkyeFO8u0ts-oB6J1h1mwq70idPYaO4jGXRhOniCDdfgJoNrYL_WO5ai3CRkk8zKnhr30BuIdXBF1svDrCQc0XsBtLkHN3D3wLcfi2d1toKKc56ScfkON3i6sZGL867YFvzPeMw8Tcjhg0o1dBFET6yR6s6VXpPFOjv8OkvtBSA/s600/DSC04727.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲看到這張大家都很Ｈｉｇｈ！有熟悉的梗真的很幸福～</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEh2jAU5GNxARs86nxYldunxCUZMKvrw9pnBzoQxJRFfOry6mcc2zL4-hHnvJRdeSbn8NXI72cyG-1R0BrEc-RmufYFJPTRblJDP_C7rfLssSW11MwaaXuuFxYXtNhOfaLIcqdTpIG8sAJFLuO3OAOjtMBcxkP2qEMdE592mXtQVmIEoFA7N1hIbwiyrpLA/s4760/DSC04741.JPG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEh2jAU5GNxARs86nxYldunxCUZMKvrw9pnBzoQxJRFfOry6mcc2zL4-hHnvJRdeSbn8NXI72cyG-1R0BrEc-RmufYFJPTRblJDP_C7rfLssSW11MwaaXuuFxYXtNhOfaLIcqdTpIG8sAJFLuO3OAOjtMBcxkP2qEMdE592mXtQVmIEoFA7N1hIbwiyrpLA/s600/DSC04741.JPG\"></a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">▲遊戲收納照</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p><br></p>', '2024-11-18 10:30:22', '2024-11-18 10:30:22', 1, 'forum-1731897022064-409848074.jpg');
